After boiling the peas, put them in cold water along with the carrots and drain. Crush the garlic, finely chop the pickles and dice the cucumbers. Mix all the ingredients and rest. Chicken Salad with Yogurt is ready. Enjoy your meal!

For the Oatli Biscuit recipe; Take the oil, sugar, oil, egg in a bowl and mix. Then add the other ingredients: oat, raisins, dried apricots, chocolate chips and orange zest. In another bowl, mix the flour, baking powder, vanilla and add it to the hand and the mixture and knead until it does not stick to the hand. Take walnut-sized pieces from the dough and roll them in your palm and press them. Place on a greased baking tray. Bake in the oven at 170 degrees for 20 minutes. Oatli Biscuit is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Egg Salad recipe; Boil the eggs and slice the boiled eggs. Clean and finely chop the onion, parsley and green peppers. Add to the eggs. Add olive oil, salt, pepper and paprika to it. Egg Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For broad beans with olive oil, first extract the broad beans. After removing the ends, wash them and leave them for 15 minutes in the water you squeezed half a lemon. Then drain the water and chop it. Chop the onion into small pieces. Heat the olive oil in the pan and fry the onion. Take the broad beans in the pan, add flour, salt and sugar. After adding 1 glass of hot water on it, close the lid. Cook for half an hour on low heat. Serve the broad beans in olive oil with garlic yoghurt and dill. Enjoy your meal :)

For the red bean stew with olive oil, soak and wash the kidney beans the day before. Chop the onions into cubes and fry them with olive oil. Add the carrots, tomato paste and water. Meanwhile, boil the kidney beans in a separate pot. After the kidney beans are cooked, put them in the stewing sauce you prepared and boil them. Lastly, put the potatoes and cook. Your red bean stew with olive oil is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

To make peas with olive oil; In olive oil, sauté 2 diced onions and 2 peeled and diced carrots. Peel and dice the tomatoes, add them to the pot and fry them. Then add the peas and the chopped potatoes to the pot. Add enough water to cover the vegetables and cook on low heat until they are all soft. Add salt after cooking. Peas with olive oil are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the zucchini with olive oil; Add olive oil to the pot and chop the onions. Peel and dice the tomatoes. Slice the zucchini into long slices without peeling them. Finely chop the garlic. Drizzle olive oil on it. Cook in its own juice on low heat. Finally, add the dill. Zucchini dish with olive oil is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for Stuffed Celery with Olive Oil; Fry the shallots, garlic and carrots in olive oil for 5 minutes. Peel the celery and cut it in half. After carving the middle with a knife and making a hole, add it to the pot. Add the potatoes and lemon juice and mix 1-2 times, then pour boiling water up to the level of the celery. Cook until the celery is soft. Add salt and let it cool. When cool, stuff them with vegetables. Stuffed Celery with Olive Oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Soybean Stew with Olive Oil; Firstly, dice the onion. Peel and dice the potatoes, carrots and tomatoes. Heat the olive oil in a pan and fry the onion and carrot on low heat. Add the potatoes, tomatoes and soybeans and fry for another 3-4 minutes. Add salt and hot water and cook on low heat for 25 minutes. Soybean Rice with Olive Oil is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the meatballs recipe; Grate the onions, put the ground beef, thyme, pepper, egg, salt, oil and flour in a bowl and knead. Make walnut-sized meatballs when they don't stick to the hand. Put the square cut cheddar in the middle and close the mouth of the meatballs. Bake in the preheated oven until golden brown. Meatballs with cheddar are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the veggie pizza; Put the dry flour, flour, salt and water in a large bowl and yoghurt until it does not stick to the hand. Cover it and let it rest for an hour. Finely chop the mushrooms, put them in a pan and fry them with oil. Put the mushrooms on a plate and chop the zucchini and eggplant in the pan. Add the chopped green peppers and stir-fry them on high heat. Finely chop the roasted peppers and add them. Divide the dough into two and spread it on a round tray. Stir the sauce over it. Sprinkle some of the cheddar. Arrange the mushrooms, zucchini, eggplant and peppers in order. Chop the peeled tomatoes into rings and arrange them on top. Finally, sprinkle the remaining cheddar on top and let it rest for half an hour. And bake in the preheated oven for 20 minutes. Vegetable pizza is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal .

For the baked mucver recipe; Clean and grate the outside of the zucchini. Finely chop the greens and add to the zucchini. In a separate bowl, whisk the egg and oil and add the spices. .Then add the flour and whisk. Add the grated cheese to the zucchini mixture. Add the zucchini and cheese mixture to the egg mixture and blend. Pour into greased baking tray. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 45 minutes. Mücver is ready to be served in the oven. Enjoy your meal.

For lentils with noodles, first boil the lentils until soft. Chop the onion into cubes and fry it in oil. Add tomato paste and fry it, then add the lentils, 4 glasses of boiling water and black pepper, mix. After it starts to boil, add the noodle. Cook for 30 minutes on high heat. Lentils with noodles are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

To make eggplant paste; Bake the eggplant in the oven with baking paper until soft. Peel off the skin and leave it in the strainer for 1 hour for the bitter juice to come out. Fry the onion in olive oil. Chop the drained eggplant. Add the onion, finely chopped pepper, finely chopped parsley to the eggplant and strain the oil. Mix in the grated garlic, salt and pepper. Eggplant mash is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the shrimp salad recipe; Add 1 tablespoon of salt to the water and boil it. Add the cleaned shrimps and once the water starts to boil again, take the shrimps and place them in a bowl of cold water. After the prawns have cooled, cut them into several pieces. In a separate bowl, mix the mayonnaise, mustard, salt, lemon juice, garlic powder, black pepper and finely chop the dill. Chop the red onion finely. Grate the celery. Add the shrimps, red onion, and grated celery to the mustard mixture and mix. Shrimp Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To make broccoli hash, first separate the broccoli into florets and chop them. After boiling in a small amount of water for 5 minutes, drain the water and let it cool. Meanwhile, whisk the egg in a separate bowl. Mix the flour, grated parmesan, grated garlic, salt and pepper. Add the broccoli to the mixture and mash into a puree. Take 2 tablespoons of the mixture for each portion and fry in hot oil. After absorbing the oil, finally pour strained yogurt on it. Broccoli mucver is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal!

For the vegetable spring rolls, first finely chop the onion, garlic and all the remaining vegetables. Heat the oil and sauté the vegetables until they are slightly dead. Add 1 cup of soy sauce and cook on low heat until the water has evaporated. Spread the phyllo and divide it into 12 pieces. Wrap the yufka thickly with the vegetable stuffing. Crack the egg into a bowl and whisk it. Dip it in breadcrumbs. Fry both sides in hot oil. Vegetable Spring Rolls are ready to be served. Good luck :)

Boil the broccoli in salted water for 5 minutes and drain the water. Melt the butter on the other side. Add the flour and mix. Add the milk, salt, pepper and cream. Put the broccoli in the oven dish. Spread the sauce you have prepared on it. Add the cheddar cheese last. cook it.

For the light walnut gullaç recipe; boil the milk in a saucepan. Remove from fire when it boils. Add honey, mix well and let it cool. Pour the warm milk into a large tray and lay the gullaç leaves one by one on the tray. Take it out of the tray before it gets soft. Fold one of the leaves that you cut into two equal parts and cut in half. After putting some walnuts in the middle, wrap it in the form of a bundle. Do the same with the other Güllaç leaves. Arrange the bundle-shaped Güllaç leaves side by side on the serving plate with the folded side down. Pour the rose water and remaining milk on the Güllaç and let them rest for 30 minutes. Güllaç with light walnut is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For mixed vegetables in the oven; Wash 2 red peppers, 2 tomatoes, 2 zucchini, 1 red pepper and cut them into rings. Soak the eggplants in salted water for 10 minutes to remove their bitterness. Set it aside and set it aside. Then place the mixed vegetables in the baking dish. Put olive oil, thyme, red pepper flakes, black pepper and salt in a bowl, mix and pour over the vegetables. Sprinkle the chopped garlic. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven until the vegetables are tender. Serve garnished with thyme leaves. Mixed vegetables in the oven are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the cold buttermilk soup recipe; Soak the ashura wheat and chickpeas, which you will use in making the soup, in separate containers the night before. Take the swollen wheat in a deep pot. After adding 6 cups of drinking water to it, boil it over medium heat. Do not forget that we will use the boiling water of the wheat to make soup. Take the chickpea in a separate pot and boil it over medium heat with enough water to cover it. Mix the strained yoghurt, which will give the soup consistency and flavor, with the addition of salt, in a small bowl until it becomes smooth. After draining the boiled chickpeas, transfer them to the wheat pot and mix lightly. After checking whether the wheat is cooked or not, remove the soup pot from the stove and keep it aside to cool. Mix the cooled, boiled chickpea and wheat soup mixture by adding whipped strained yogurt and mint. To use in the service according to your desire; Finely chop the dill. Take the soup mix into serving bowls. Serve cold. Enjoy your meal :)

For the eggplant salad recipe with yogurt; Roast the eggplant and peppers and peel off their skins. Chop it into small pieces. Add lemon juice and oil to it and mix it lightly. In a separate bowl, mix the yogurt, salt and crushed garlic. Mix all the ingredients and let it rest a little in the fridge. Eggplant salad with yogurt is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Mushroom Salad recipe; Boil the mushrooms in lemon water until soft, drain them and cut into thin long slices. Boil the red peppers, cut them in half and chop finely. In a bowl, add the mushrooms, finely chopped dill, pickles, boiled corn, red peppers and mix. Whisk the olive oil, lemon juice and salt in a bowl and add them to the salad mix. Take the Mushroom Salad on a serving plate. Enjoy your meal.

For the homemade arara pide; Take 2 glasses of flour, yeast, salt in a bowl. Keep half a glass of flour aside. First add half of the water to the flour and knead. For a soft consistency, add flour and water if necessary. Then take the dough to the counter and continue kneading for 5-10 minutes. Sprinkle flour on the bottom of a bowl. Put the dough and put flour on it again. Put a damp cloth on it. Let it rest for 2 hours. Take the dough from the bowl and leave it on the counter for another 20 minutes. Give the dough a little more consistency by sprinkling flour on the counter. Shape it into a pita with your hands. Apply water, olive oil and sprinkle with black cumin. Cook until browned. Your homemade ramadan pide is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

To make coffee and cheese pudding; Whisk the milk, flour, sugar and egg thoroughly, put them in the saucepan and cook, stirring until thickened. Dissolve the coffee in hot water and add it to the pot and mix again. Add labneh, coconut and butter to the mixture and beat with a mixer for 3 minutes. Put it in serving bowls and put it in the refrigerator to cool after it comes to room temperature. Cheese pudding with coffee is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal!

For the lemon jelly gum custard; Mix the milk, granulated sugar and flour thoroughly. Once the sugar has melted, set aside 1 cup. Stir and cook the sugar-milk mixture. Add the separated egg milk to the pot by mixing it. Cook until it reaches a custard consistency. Add the mastic and butter and beat for 10 minutes. Pour into serving containers and cool. Mix lemon juice, water, lemon peel, sugar and starch. Cook until it reaches a custard consistency. Stir to cool and pour over the custard. Serve garnished with lemon slices. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Özlem salad, first of all, the barley vermicelli and salt are thrown into the boiling olive oil water and cooked until the water is absorbed. Yogurt is garlicky. Cucumbers are peeled and grated. All ingredients are mixed with each other. It is garnished with paprika and mint. Özlem Salad is ready to be served. Bon appetit :) NOTE : WHEN WEATHER STOP WEAKNESS, CONSUME 1 PORTION WITH CHICKEN VEGETABLES FOR 2 DAYS LUNCH/DINN. Garlic is a powerful antibiotic. It regulates blood circulation, lowers blood pressure, strengthens the immune system and protects against cancer. Prevents hair loss.

For the damson compote; Boil 6 cups of water with 1 cup of granulated sugar. Divide the plums from which you have removed the seeds, to the size you want. Add the plums and cinnamon to the boiling sugar water. You can add some cloves if you want. After adding the ingredients, boil for another 6-7 minutes. Remove from the heat before the plums fall apart. Leave to cool. Plums will give their color to water during cooling. After cooling at room temperature, keep them in the refrigerator. Your damson compote is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the curd cheese olmet; Beat eggs and milk, then add pepper and curd cheese to the mixture. Heat the oil in a wide pan and pour the mortar into the pan. Sprinkle finely chopped parsley on top. Fry the other side of the omelet with the help of the lid. Your curd cheese omelet is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Tomato Bulgur Pilaf recipe; Chop the onions. Add the onions and oil to the pan and cook a little. Finely chop the peppers, chop the tomatoes into cubes, add salt and cook a little more. Then add 1.5 cups of water to the mixture and boil it. Wash and mix the bulgur in boiling water. Cook the bulgur on low heat until the water is absorbed. Bulgur Pilaf with Tomatoes is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

For the veggie appetizer recipe, dice or julienne the vegetables. Add 1 tablespoon of oil and half a tea glass of water on the non-greasy paper, cover it with aluminum foil and bake in the oven at 200 degrees for about 1 hour in its own steam. When the vegetables have cooled, add yogurt to them. Vegetable appetizer is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For a lentil eggplant salad recipe with chickpeas, boil the lentils and chickpeas. Roast and chop the eggplants and red peppers and add to the lentils and chickpeas. Chop parsley, dill, green onion and dry onion on it. Finally, add 1 tablespoon of olive oil. Eggplant salad with chickpeas and lentils is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal

For the blueberry oat cookie recipe; Mix sugar, egg, yogurt, oil in a deep bowl. Add oat, flour, blueberry, baking powder, vanilla and mix some more. Then, with the help of two spoons, pour the mixture on wax paper at intervals. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees until golden brown. Blueberry oat cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For baby pudding, first mix rice flour in a glass of water. Stir until it boils. It will have a very thick consistency. After boiling for a few minutes, take it off the stove and add the butter. Once it's warm, add breast milk until it's the consistency your baby eats. Sweeten with molasses. Baby pudding should preferably be in the consistency of a dark boza and should be fed to the baby with a spoon, not with a bottle. It would be a healthier choice to use oat flour instead of rice flour. Your baby pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)
While preparing the mustard sauce, first add salt to the cream and boil it. Then add the mustard into the mixture. Your mustard sauce is ready. Enjoy your meal :)

For carrot screening, grate the carrots first. Heat the olive oil well. Fry the carrots in hot oil until soft and add salt. Store at room temperature and then in the refrigerator to cool. Prepare the garlic yogurt on a plate for an appetizer. Mix the cooled carrots with the garlic yogurt. Keep it in the refrigerator to cool down again and take the appetizer on a serving plate and prepare it for presentation. Enjoy your meal..

When making apple cookies, first peel and grate 4 apples. Add 4 tablespoons of granulated sugar and cook for 5 minutes on low heat in a saucepan. Add 1 teaspoon of cinnamon and 1 teaspoon of coarsely ground walnuts and leave to cool. For apple cookie dough, cool 125 grams of melted butter, add 1 tea glass of yogurt, 1 tea glass of sugar, 1 tea glass of oil, 1 egg, 1 packet of vanilla and 1 packet of baking powder to it and mix. Slowly add flour while continuing to mix. Knead the dough well until it is soft to the earlobe. After the dough is finished kneading, let it rest for 5 minutes and divide it into 3 parts. With the help of a rolling pin, roll out the dough in 30 cm diameter and divide it into 8 parts. Put 1 teaspoon of apple mortar on one edge of each of these pieces you cut and wrap them. Set your preheated oven to 170 degrees and bake for 20-25 minutes. Your apple cookie decorated with powdered sugar is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the walnut cookie recipe with powdered sugar; First deal with the flour and baking powder. In a separate bowl, mix the margarine, powdered sugar, walnut kernels and egg yolk softened at room temperature. Then add the flour and baking powder. Knead until it is as soft as an earlobe. Cut off walnut-sized pieces, roll them and place them on a greased tray. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven until lightly browned. Arrange the cookies on a plate and sprinkle powdered sugar on them. Walnut cookies with powdered sugar are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To make hazelnut cookies, first knead all the ingredients except hazelnuts in a large bowl. Continue kneading by adding flour until the dough has the consistency of earlobes. Add the hazelnuts to your dough and continue kneading. Break off small pieces and roll them. Dip the cookies you have prepared into coarsely pounded hazelnuts. Place the cookies you prepared on the baking tray. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven. Your cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the banana roll cake recipe; Crack the eggs into a deep bowl, add the sugar and whisk them in. Then add flour and baking powder to the mixture you prepared and continue whisking. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven for 6-7 minutes. Take it out of the tray, put it on the counter and spread the pastry cream on it. Cut the bananas in half, place them in the middle, roll them up and let them rest in the fridge for 1 hour. Slice evenly according to the number of people. Banana Roll Cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

To make zucchini tarator, grate the zucchini, then fry them in olive oil in a pan until they release their juice and absorb it again. Then put the zucchini in a deep bowl, wait for it to cool down and come to room temperature. Add the crushed garlic, ground walnuts, yoghurt, salt and finely chopped dill and mix well. Keep in the refrigerator to cool. Zucchini tarator is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal!

For the strawberry cake recipe; Add margarine, half of the granulated sugar, 1 whole of 3 eggs, only the yolk of 2 eggs and vanilla into a deep bowl and beat with a mixer. In the same bowl, add the flour, milk and baking powder and mix. Grease the cake tin and pour the mixture. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 40 minutes. Then boil the remaining granulated sugar with water until it dissolves. Add the coconut and lemon juice to the sugar water. After whisking the remaining 2 egg whites, add them to the coconut mixture and mix lightly. Cover the cake with this mixture. After placing the strawberries in the middle of the cake, the strawberry cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Pasta with Neapolitan Sauce; Cook the pasta in boiling water for 15-20 minutes. For the Pasta with Neapolitan Sauce, add olive oil to the pan, add the small chopped tomatoes and fry a little, then add the tomato paste and crushed garlic and fry some more. Then add salt and spices on it and fry for 1-2 more minutes. Add the sauce you prepared into the cooked pasta and mix well. Take it on the serving plate. Pasta with Neapolitan Sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pasta recipe with Bolognese sauce; Add water and salt to a deep pot. When the water boils, add the pasta and let it boil. For the sauce, grate the onion and tomato, beat the garlic. Put the olive oil in a pan and add the minced meat, grated onion, crushed garlic and tomato paste and sauté well. Add the grated tomatoes, salt and spices and continue sautéing. After the sauce is cooked, turn off the heat and strain the cooked pasta with the help of a strainer. Put the drained pasta in a hollow zucchini. Pour the sauce on it, mix it and divide it on plates for 6 people. Pasta with bolognese sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the lentil spinach recipe; In a saucepan, chop the onions into small pieces and fry them in oil until they turn pink. Add the tomato paste and garlic and fry some more. Wash the spinach in plenty of water and chop it for food. Add the pre-boiled lentils, chopped spinach and enough hot water to cover the ingredients in the pot. Add salt and spices and mix. Cook on low heat for 20-25 minutes. Before removing from the stove, add the lemon juice. Lentil Spinach is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the zucchini dish with dill, first cut the zucchini and tomatoes into cubes and put them in the pot. Add 5 cloves of garlic whole. Add salt, cumin and paprika as desired and let it cook with very little water. Before you take it off the stove, add half a bunch of chopped dill and 1 teaspoon of olive oil and leave it to infuse by closing the bottom. Zucchini with dill is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the chicken recipe with bechamel sauce; Spread the peas and carrots, which were boiled first, into a debt. Then chop the boiled chicken breast coarsely over the peas and carrots. For the bechamel sauce, melt the butter in a pan and fry the flour. After roasting, add two glasses of milk, spices and salt. Stir constantly until you get the consistency of a sauce so that there are no lumps in the flour. First, pour the boiled chicken and vegetables, then the béchamel sauce over the pyrex and grate the cheddar. Bake in the preheated oven for a while until the cheddar is melted and browned. Enjoy your meal.

For pasta soup, first boil the pasta. Put the olive oil in a pan, add the grated tomatoes and tomato paste and fry until it gets thick. Add water after frying. When the water boils, add the spices and pasta and mix. Then turn off the stove. Take this different taste among the pasta recipes on the presentation plate and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pasta recipe; First, boil the pasta. Fry the chopped onion in a pan with olive oil. After squeezing the juice of the grated zucchini, add it to the onions and mix. Add the minced garlic, spices and salt. Cook for another five minutes and turn off the stove. Mix the boiled pasta with the zucchini sauté thoroughly. Zucchini pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach pie recipe; After washing and draining the spinach, run the leaves through the robot. After whisking 3 eggs and 1 glass of sugar thoroughly in a separate bowl, add 3 glasses of flour, 1 tea glass of oil, 1 packet of vanilla and 1 packet of baking powder and whisk some more. Add the spinach to the mixture and mix well. Pour the spinach pastry dough into the baking dish and bake in a preheated 180-degree oven for 25 minutes. For the cream, mix 2 glasses of milk, 2 tablespoons of flour and 2 tablespoons of granulated sugar in a small saucepan and let it cool after cooking. In another place, mix 1 glass of milk and 1 pack of whipped cream thoroughly with the cream that you have left to cool after thoroughly whisking. Divide the baked cake in half horizontally with the help of a knife. Spread the cream you prepared for the cake between and on the cake. Spinach Pie is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the mosaic cake recipe; Melt the margarine in a pan and add the cocoa, milk and sugar. Cook the mixture by stirring and when it starts to boil, take it off the stove and let it cool. Break and mix the biscuits into the warm mixture without crumbling too much. Lay a stretch film on a tray and transfer your mixture to the stretch film you have laid and fold it in the form of a roll. Keep your mosaic cake roll in the freezer for 2-3 hours. After waiting the roll cake, slice it equally according to the number of people. Mosaic cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For an easy pudding cake recipe; Add the milk and pudding to a saucepan and stir until cooked. Process the biscuits and hazelnuts. Spread half of the cocoa pudding on a boron glass and add half of the hazelnut biscuit mixture on it. Do the same steps in the remaining pudding and hazelnut biscuit mix, respectively. Put my debt in the fridge. After the easy pudding cake has cooled, sprinkle coconut on it and slice it. Easy pudding cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Easy Orange Pie recipe; First, cut the oranges into large cubes. Cook the chopped oranges in a saucepan with sugar. When the orange juice is released, pass the mixture through the robot. Then put 750 ml of milk and packet pudding in another pot and mix until cooked. After laying the biscuits in a bowl and warming the remaining milk on the stove, sprinkle it on and spread the orange mixture. After laying another layer of biscuits on it, pour the pudding and spread it again. Put the Orange Easy Biscuit cake in the refrigerator to cool. Sprinkle coconut on the cooled cake and prepare to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken salad recipe; First, boil the chicken breast in water. While the chicken breast is boiling, wash the lettuce in plenty of water and chop the lettuce leaves thinly, the tomatoes into cubes, the cucumbers in rings and the carrots into tiny pieces. After the chicken breast is boiled, finely chop the chicken breasts in a deep bowl. Add the lettuce, tomatoes and cucumbers, carrots, corn and peas. Then add salt, pepper, lemon juice and olive oil and mix well. Chicken Salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For sauteed chicken with mushrooms, sauté the peppers and onions in olive oil for a few minutes in a saucepan. Add the diced chicken and continue sautéing. Continue adding the spices and crushed garlic. Then add the mushrooms on top of the mixture and after it releases its juice, add the diced tomatoes and tomato paste and mix. After the chickens are cooked, the sauteed chicken with mushrooms will be ready to serve. Enjoy the sauteed chicken with mushrooms, which is a good choice for chicken dishes.

For the Chicken Chickpea Meal recipe; Cook the chickpeas, which you soaked in hot water the night before, until they are soft. In a separate pot, fry the diced onions with olive oil. Add the diced chicken breast on it and fry it a little more until the water is gone. Then add the tomato paste, salt, crushed garlic, spices and chickpeas. Cook it with just enough hot water to cover it. Chicken chickpea dish is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

For chard with yogurt, wash the chard thoroughly and chop it not too finely. Fry the onions in olive oil in a pan until golden brown. After frying, add the tomato paste and water. After 3-4 minutes, add a clove of crushed garlic, salt and pepper and mix. Add the chard on it and fry it until it releases its water. After roasting, take the chard on a serving plate and pour the garlic yogurt on it. Chard with yogurt is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare your mixed pizza, first dissolve the yeast in warm water. Open the middle of the flour and add salt, sugar, olive oil and the yeast you have melted. Knead the dough to a non-sticky consistency and leave it to ferment. Flour the fermented dough and roll it into a round shape with the help of a rolling pin. Then, to prepare the sauce of your mixed pizza; Dissolve the tomato paste in half a glass of water, add the spices, olive oil and crushed garlic and mix. Spread the sauce you prepared on the dough with a brush. Chop the tomatoes into cubes, the peppers and sausage in rings. Sprinkle the ingredients you have prepared evenly all over the pizza. Sprinkle the grated cheddar cheese on the top and bake in a preheated 190-degree oven. Your mixed pizza is ready to serve. Bon appetit : )

For the recipe for Brussels Sprouts with Olive Oil; Fry the chopped onions in a pan until they turn pink. Then add chopped carrots and crushed garlic on it and fry some more. Add brussels sprouts and warm water with tomato paste and salt, slightly over the top. After a little cooking, add the lemon juice. Brussels sprouts will be ready to serve after cooking. Brussels Sprouts with Olive Oil are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

Before you start to prepare your raisin cake, first beat the sugar and egg in a bowl. Then add the oil and yogurt. Prepare the raisin cake dough by pouring flour, baking powder, vanilla on it and mixing for 2 minutes. Wash the raisins, sprinkle a small amount of flour on it and add it to the cake dough you have prepared and mix it. Bake at 150 degrees for 45 minutes. Your raisin cake is ready to serve :)

For the oat paste cookie recipe; First, beat the softened butter and sugar at room temperature with a mixer until it reaches a creamy consistency. Add the egg and continue beating. Mix the flour, oat, baking powder and cinnamon in a separate bowl and add them to the egg dough you have prepared. Add the hazelnuts to the dough you prepared for the last oat paste cookie and mix. Lay it on the greaseproof paper with the help of a spoon. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 15 minutes. oat butter cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

To make tarhana soup with milk, put the tarhana in a saucepan, add cold milk and water and stir until it boils. Add salt and boil for 2-3 more minutes. After heating the butter and roasting the chili pepper and mint, add it to the soup. Tarhana soup with milk is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal!

For the wholemeal pasta recipe with vegetables; Boil the pasta in salted water for 10 minutes. Chop the onions and tomatoes into cubes and cook them in a pan with just their juice, without oil. Add salt, pepper and thyme. Then extract the purslane, finely chop the dill and parsley and add to the pan. Cook for a few more minutes and turn off the heat. Strain and put the pasta water in a wide deep bowl. Pour the vegetable mixture you prepared on it. Chop the red peppers into rings and garnish with these peppers last. Whole wheat pasta with vegetables is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

When starting to make spaghetti with sardines, first wash the sardines, remove the salt and cut them into strips. Mince the onion and kill it in margarine. Add the diced tomatoes and let it simmer for 10 minutes. Then pass the finely chopped peeled garlic through the mixer along with the walnut kernels and sardines. Add the mixture you prepared and the chopped olives to the tomato sauce. Add the black pepper and cook on low heat for 10 minutes. After boiling the spaghetti in salted water until it does not lose its freshness, add the sauce you prepared. After sprinkling the grated Parmesan cheese on it, your spaghetti with sardines is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the sardine salad recipe; First of all, clean and wash the scales and inside of the sardines. After adding the knee and salt to the pot, cook for 15 minutes. Wash lettuce leaves in plenty of water and cut into finger-thick slices. Finely chop the peppers and onions. Divide the lettuce leaves, peppers and onions equally into two bowls. Spread the cooked sardines on the lettuce leaves in two bowls. Slice the tomato and garnish with the tomato slices. In a bowl, mix the olive oil, lemon juice, salt and mix. Drizzle the dressing you created from olive oil, lemon juice and salt over the salads. Sardine salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Persian Rice recipe; First boil and shred the chicken. Heat the butter and nut oil in a pan. Add the rice and pine nuts and fry them. Then add enough hot water to cover it and add salt and pepper. Add the shredded chicken and cook. Add chopped parsley and let it rest. On the other side, beat the eggs and make an omelet from each. When the omelets are ready, place them in the bowl. Put rice in the middle, gather the edges and turn it upside down and place it on the baking tray. Prepare the remaining omelets in this way. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 10 minutes and take it to a serving plate. Serve garnished with boiled peas, tomato and pepper slices. Your Persian Rice is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach egg recipe; First of all, wash and sort the spinach in plenty of water. Then dice the onion and fry it in oil by adding salt. Chop the spinach for food, then add it to the onion and cook for 10 minutes. After adding the black pepper, make as many holes as the number of eggs on it and break an egg into each well and cook. Spinach Egg is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the buckwheat salad recipe; First of all, to soften the buckwheat, add 3 cups of hot water and salt to a bowl and add the buckwheat into it. While the buckwheat is softening, finely chop the parsley, mint, dill and pickles and finely chop the tomatoes. Strain the boiled buckwheat and after it cools down, mix the buckwheat with the chopped ingredients. Add cumin and allspice, and finally olive oil, pomegranate syrup, salt and pepper, mix it a few more times and put it on the serving plate. Buckwheat salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the dark chocolate chip cookie recipe; Melt the bitter chocolate benmari style. In a bowl, mix butter, powdered sugar, salt and vanilla. Add the egg. Add the melted and warmed chocolate. Add the powdered almonds and flour and knead until they do not stick to the hand. Take walnut-sized pieces from the dough, roll them in your hands and place them on the tray. Bake in a preheated 170 degree oven for 15 minutes. Your dark chocolate chip cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

While making walnut bread, mix white flour and whole wheat flour, salt and dry yeast in a large bowl. Add room temperature water, butter and olive oil and knead the dough for 10 minutes. Leave the dough to rise for 1 hour in a warm place. Add the walnuts and knead for 3 more minutes to mix the ingredients well. Roll the dough by hand, place it on a floured baking tray and let it rise for 1 more hour. With a knife, draw a cross on the bread you have prepared. Bake in a preheated 220 degree oven for about 30 minutes. Walnut bread is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

When starting to prepare Sourdough Village Bread, use room temperature sourdough. Take the sourdough in a large bowl and add half a glass of flour and mix. Cover the container and let it sit at room temperature for 2 hours. At the end of this period, mix the sourdough, remaining flour, water and salt in a large bowl and knead for 10 minutes. Take your dough in a closed container and leave it at room temperature for 5 hours. Roll the dough on a floured counter, without over-kneading, and form it into a large meringue. Place on a floured baking tray and leave for another 1 hour for second proofing. With a sharp knife, make three parallel slits on the bread. Sprinkle flour on it and bake in a preheated 220 degree oven for about 30 minutes. Your sourdough village bread is ready to serve. Bon appetit :)

While preparing the green lentil pastry, first take the flour in a bowl and roll it out like a pool. Add the yoghurt, egg, baking powder and salt and knead. Then let the dough rest for half an hour. Saute the diced onion and minced meat in oil, add the boiled lentils and spices. Divide the prepared dough into meringues and fold it in half by putting the stuffing inside. Arrange on a greased tray, sprinkle egg yolk and black cumin seeds and bake at 170 degrees. Your green lentil pastry is ready to serve. Bon appetit :)

When starting to make the yoghurt egg salad, first of all boil the eggs to a solid consistency and peel them. After cooling, slice into circles. Arrange the egg slices on serving plates and sprinkle salt on them. Crush the garlic and mix it with the yogurt and brush it over the eggs. Drizzle with olive oil and sprinkle with paprika or black pepper. Finally, garnish by chopping the parsley finely. Your egg salad with yogurt is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal:)

While making dill cheese pastry, first take the flour in the dough mixing bowl and roll it out like a pool. Add dry yeast, milk, margarine, eggs, salt and sugar and knead it. Let it rest for 15 minutes to reach its consistency. In the meantime, take the curd cheese into the mixing bowl and add the finely chopped dill and green onion to it and mix. Divide the dough into 16 meringues and put the stuffing in the middle and close it. Arrange the prepared pastry on a greased tray and brush it with egg yolk. Sprinkle black cumin with honey upon request. Bake in a preheated 180-degree oven for 20 minutes. Your dill cheese pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal:)

For the Egg Toast recipe; First, fry the toast breads. Beat the eggs in a separate place. Melt the margarine in the pan and add the cheese and mix until it melts. When the cheese melts, add eggs and cook it. After the eggs are cooked, add the finely chopped parsley on them. Egg Toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

Before you start making Sivas Pastry with Pastrami, first sort and drain the spinach. Rub with salt. Fry the onions in olive oil, add the spinach and fry for another 5 minutes. Add black pepper and salt and mix. Finally, chop the bacon into pieces. Spread the pastrami you prepared in the middle of the ready dough. Make a square by folding the dough inward from all four sides. Cook on both sides in the pan. While your Pastrami Sivas Pastry is hot, spread butter on it. Cook all the phyllo in the same way. Your Pastrami Sivas Pastry is ready to serve. Bon appetit :)

Before starting the bean meal with bacon, first melt the margarine in the pan and add the bacon and saute it. Add the diced onion and fry for a few more minutes. Cook by adding the peeled and diced tomatoes and the green bell pepper cut into large cubes. Add the broth and bring to a boil. Sort and soak the dried beans the night before. The next day, add cold water to a pot and boil it for 30 minutes. After draining the dried beans, add the pastrami and tomato paste on it and cook until the beans are soft. Your baked beans with pastrami are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For herb and Bacon Egg recipe; First of all, chop the pastrami finely and add water and cook it until the water is absorbed. Then add butter on it, chop the spinach and finely chop the spring onions and fry for five minutes. Lastly, add the medium diced bacon and crack the eggs. Cook very little. Sprinkle salt and pepper on it. Herbed Bacon Egg is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the oven-baked spinach recipe; First of all, cut the onions into cubes and fry them in 2 tablespoons of oil with the peanuts in a saucepan. Wash the spinach in plenty of water, chop it up and add it to the pot and cook it. Then finely chop the mushrooms and add them to the pot. When the mushrooms are cooked, add salt and pepper and pour them into the baking dish. Arrange the bacon slices on it. Crack the eggs into a bowl and pour the beaten eggs over the bacon. Finally, sprinkle the cheese grater on top of the eggs. Bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees until golden brown. Spinach with bacon in the oven is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the fig jam recipe; First, peel the figs thickly and boil them in water. After boiling, divide into 4 parts. In a separate pot, boil the sugar and water until it thickens. Strain the boiled figs and put them in sherbet and cook on low heat. Cook until the juice of the fig jam thickens, then turn off the heat. After it cools, put it in jars and seal it. Fig jam is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal .

For the tangerine cake; Beat the granulated sugar, orange zest and eggs in a large bowl with a mixer at high speed. Continue whisking while slowly adding the liquid. Add the tangerine juice and mix. Add flour, baking powder and vanilla to the mixture and mix with a mixer at low speed. Add currants and walnuts and mix, then pour into a greased and lightly floured baking dish. Bake in a preheated oven at 170 degrees. Your tangerine cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

When starting to make the pear dessert with molasses, first peel the pears so that the stem remains on it and remove the seeds. With the help of a knife, make shallow horizontal scratches on the pears. Then put the molasses, water, bay leaf, cloves and cinnamon stick into the pot and cook on high heat. Close the lid of the pot and cook on low heat for 45 minutes, then set the pears aside. Simmer until the remaining liquid thickens to a sauce-like consistency. After placing the pears in the middle of the plate, pour the sauce over it and serve with cream or ice cream. Your pear dessert with molasses is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Wheat Flour Bluefish Grill recipe, first grease the grill wire with sunflower oil. Sift the flour and salt together. Squeeze 1m lemon and set aside 2 tablespoons of lemon juice, then pour the rest over the fish. Dip the fish in flour, shake off the excess flour. For the sauce, add half a glass of olive oil to the juice of 1 lemon. Place the fish on the grill and brush with the prepared sauce while the bluefish are cooking. Bake for 10 minutes side to side. After putting the bluefish on the serving plates, add the chopped parsley to the remaining lemon-olive oil sauce and pour over the grilled bluefish and serve. Enjoy your meal :)

Clean the sea breams and scratch them. After washing and drying the cleaned sea bream, apply olive oil on the inside and outside and sprinkle with salt and pepper. .After spreading half of the vegetables in the baking bag, place the sea bream on them. Arrange the remaining ingredients on the sea bream. Put them on a baking tray and bake in a preheated 200 degree oven. Your Grilled Sea Bream is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

To make diet cookies, combine all the ingredients and as much bran flour as you can and knead until you get a dough consistency. Then break off pieces of dough and form a round shape. Bake in the oven preheated to 180 degrees for 25 minutes. If you want it to be like a biscuit, you can bake it by giving it a thinner shape. Using baking paper will make it easier for you. You can store the cookies in the refrigerator for up to 1 week. Diet cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal!

For the recipe for meatballs with quail eggs; First of all, boil the quail eggs, peel them and keep them on a plate. To make meatballs, cut the ground beef, bread crumbs, and 1 egg into 10 equal parts. Open the middle of the dough and put the boiled quail eggs into the shape of meatballs. After laying them on a greased baking tray, pour the slightly heated butter on the meatballs one by one and bake them in a 200-degree oven until golden brown. Fry the flour with oil in a pan and add the grated tomatoes and chopped garlic on it. When the tomatoes are cooked, add salt, sugar and black pepper and bring to a boil. While serving the quail egg meatballs, pour the sauce over the meatballs. Meatballs with quail eggs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

To make molasses cake, whisk the egg and molasses in a bowl, then add sunflower oil and milk and continue whisking. Add the whole wheat flour, baking powder and finally the diced apricots that you dipped in the flour to the mixture. Bake in a greased cake tin and in a preheated oven at 160 C. Molasses cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal!

To make cauliflower pastry, first boil the cauliflower and let it cool after draining. Chop into small pieces when cool. Mix the eggs, oil, yogurt in a bowl and finely chop the parsley, dill and green onion and add them all to the cauliflower. After crushing the cheese and adding salt, pepper and 5 tablespoons of flour, add it to the mixture. Pour into a greased baking dish and bake in a preheated 180 degree oven. If you wish, you can sprinkle grated cheddar cheese on it and cook for 5 more minutes. Cauliflower pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal!

For the recipe of Yams with Olive Oil; First of all, peel the Jerusalem artichokes and keep them in water with lemon so that they do not darken. Cut the Jerusalem artichoke, carrot and potatoes into cubes and put them in a saucepan, add the onion and garlic. Cook by adding olive oil, salt, sugar, a tea glass of water and the juice of a lemon. After cooling, you can decorate with dill. Yams with Olive Oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

Before starting the leek pie, first wash the leeks and chop them finely. Cook the leeks with 2 tablespoons of oil, salt and tomato paste. Prepare the liquid mixture by whisking eggs, milk and oil. Then cut the dough in half, brush it with the liquid mixture and wrap it with the leek mortar. Grease your tray with oil and turn the dough around and place it on the tray. Arrange the other phyllo sheets around each other and bake them in a preheated 200 degree oven. Your leek pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

When starting to make Oven Mushrooms, cut off the stem in the middle of the cleaned mushrooms. Salt the mushrooms with salt and grate the cheddar cheese and place them in the pits in the middle of the mushrooms. Sprinkle with paprika and bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 15 minutes. Mushrooms in the oven are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the hazelnut tart, knead the flour, powdered sugar and oil in a bowl. To prepare the inside of the hazelnut tart, mix two egg whites, the zest of a lemon, hazelnuts and powdered sugar. Put the mortar you prepared on the tart dough. Bake in a preheated oven on a greased baking tray. Your hazelnut tart is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal:)

For the apple cake recipe, beat the eggs and granulated sugar until white. Then add the apple zest along with the other ingredients and beat for 3 minutes. Finally, add the flour and baking powder and whisk. Pour into greased cake tin. Bake in a preheated 170 degree oven. Apple Cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

To make oat paste cake, beat eggs and sugar. Repeat the whisking by adding milk, labneh and oil. Add the remaining ingredients and whisk one last time. Pour the mixture into the greased mold, bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 35 minutes. oat paste cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

You can use one of two options to make semolina dessert with milk. If you have 10 tablespoons of sugar or diabetes, you can use 1/2 Cup of Splenda. Put the semolina, vanilla and lemon zest in a saucepan, add milk and water and mix. Cook the mixture on low heat, stirring, until it reaches the consistency of custard. While still hot, add Splenda or sugar and mix well. After spreading on the wet glass tray, let it cool. After cooling, keep the dessert in the refrigerator for 1 day. You can sprinkle cinnamon and finely chopped walnuts on it. Milk semolina dessert is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal!

While making the fig cake, first beat the eggs and sugar until they turn white. Then add milk and oil. Sift the flour, baking powder and vanilla onto the mixture and continue mixing. Add the chopped figs that have been soaked in water and mix one last time. Pour the cake batter into the greased cake mold. Bake the cake at 180 degrees. Fig cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

While making fig cookies, first soften the figs by soaking them in hot water for 10 minutes and chop them into small pieces. Mix all the other ingredients and add the figs you cut last, and knead. When you get a soft dough, give it a round shape and arrange it on the tray and bake at 175 degrees for 30 minutes. Remove from the oven and decorate with powdered sugar when cool. Fig cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the apple pie recipe; First, mix the flour and baking powder in a bowl and add yoghurt, eggs, all kinds of oil and knead until it becomes a dough. Grate the apples. To prepare the filling for the apple pie, cook the apple zest, cinnamon, sugar and hazelnuts for 10 minutes and let it cool. While the stuffing is cooling, take small balls from the dough and open them with your hands and cut them into triangles. Put half a teaspoon of the mortar you prepared and cooled in the wide part of the triangle and roll it to the thin side. After doing the same for each triangle, put them on the tray. Bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees until golden brown. After removing from the oven, decorate with powdered sugar. Apple pie is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the dried apricot cookies, first mix the margarine, egg yolks and apricots. Then sift the powdered sugar, flour and baking powder into a dough. Take pieces from the dough and shape them into cookies. Dip the cookies in egg white and place them on a greased tray. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 30 minutes. Your dried apricot cookies are ready to serve. Bon appetit :)

For the wet cake, first beat the eggs and sugar. After adding cocoa, oil and milk, set aside a glass of water. After separating, add vanilla, baking powder and flour to the remaining mixture. Cook your oven at 170 degrees. When the wet cake is baked, pour a glass of the mixture you set aside on the cake. After the cake has cooled, garnish with nutmeg. Wet cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the pomegranate tart, first crush the biscuits until they become flour. Mix in melted margarine and cinnamon. Leave it for 5 minutes and knead it and spread it in the tart mold. For the custard, extract the pomegranates, crush them and extract their juice. Put 1 glass of water, starch, pomegranate juice and sugar in the pot and boil it. Spread the pudding on the tart. Garnish with pomegranates. Pomegranate tart is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

To make cauliflower patties, you must first separate the cauliflower from its leaves and cut it into sizes that can fit inside the pot. Next, boil the cauliflower until it is soft enough to mash. Take it out of the water and mash it well. Add the grated cheddar, flour, egg and spices. After kneading it well, shape it and fry it in a little oil. Cauliflower patties are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the pan pastry with minced meat, first peel and finely chop the onion, remove the parsley and chop it, heat the oil in the pan, fry the minced meat, add onion, salt, and black pepper and fry for a few more minutes, add the parsley, mix and remove from the heat, whisk the eggs in a deep bowl, add butter and Add milk and mix, grease the baking tray, spread the 3 phyllo dough on the tray by spreading the milk mixture between them, spread the mincemeat on it, spread the other phyllo dough on the tray by spreading the milk mixture between them. Bake in a preheated 160 degree oven for 45 minutes. Pie with minced meat is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

To make stinging nettle soup, you must first remove the stinging nettle with the help of gloves and discard the stems. Put the leaves in boiling salted water and boil for 10 minutes and then strain. After melting the butter in a soup pot, adding flour and cornmeal, fry it for 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly with a wooden spoon. On the other hand, mix the milk and broth in a deep bowl and add little by little to the flour you have roasted. Cook, stirring constantly, until it boils. After adding salt, pepper, granulated sugar and boiled stinging nettle, cook for at least 20 more minutes and take it off the stove. You can sprinkle red chili flakes on it before serving. If you wish, you can also puree the soup with the help of a hand blender. Stinging nettle soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For Ashura, first soak the wheat, beans and chickpeas in water the night before. While soaking the chickpeas, add hot water and salt. Wash the wheat we soaked thoroughly and extract the black water. Put it in a large pot and put it on the stove. Add enough water to cover it and boil it for 1 minute. Cover and rest for 10-15 minutes. Boil it again and let it rest again. If necessary, add a little more hot water. After boiling and resting for the last time, light the bottom of the stove again. While pouring the milk and continuing to mix, wash the rice and add. Pour hot water again. After boiling for a while, add the beans and chickpeas. Stir constantly. Wash and add the grapes. Increase the water as you add the material. Finely chop the peel of the orange. Boil in a separate pot. Dice the apples and add them to the soup. Add the boiled orange peels. Mix some more and add the sugar. After the sugar dissolves, add the chopped apricots that are kept in water. Pour rose water. You can add a little more hot water if needed. Stir constantly so that it does not stick to the bottom. Add the diced figs. Add some hot water. Cook a little more, stirring constantly, and turn off the heat. Divide into bowls. After it is cooled and jelled, garnish with pomegranate. Ashura is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For chicken rice, boil the chicken in a deep pot and leave it to cool after it is boiled well. When it's warm, shred it well. In another saucepan, melt the butter. Throw the rice you washed in water into the butter and fry it well. Poured hot water on it. If you wish, you can use half of the water from the water in which you boiled the chicken. After you add the salt, close the lid and let it cook on the lowest heat. After the rice is cooked, place the chickens on the bottom of a deep bowl. Put the rice on it. Carefully place the bowl upside down on the serving plate. Sprinkle black pepper. Chicken rice is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the linden tea recipe; Put the water, cloves and cinnamon stick in the teapot and boil for 5-6 minutes. After turning off the stove and waiting for 2 minutes, throw the linden herbs into it and wait for it to brew for 5-6 minutes. You can strain it into a cup and sweeten it with honey. Linden tea is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the carrot cake recipe; Beat the egg and sugar well until white. Then add oil, milk, flour, baking powder and vanilla and beat with a mixer. Add carrot grated and walnuts and mix. Pour it into a well-oiled cake mold and bake at 170 degrees. Your carrot cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

To make soup with chicken broth, first separate the skin of the chicken leg and boil it with the breast and 2 onions. Take the boiled meat out of the water and chop it into small pieces. In a separate pot, fry 2 tablespoons of flour and 2 tablespoons of butter until the smell of the flour is gone. Then add some boiled water to the chicken broth you have obtained and pour it little by little on the flour. After crushing the garlic, add it to the pot with the chopped chicken. Putting enough salt according to the water of the soup, cook for 10 minutes; but be careful to keep the lid of the pot open during this time. As the last step, sprinkle with ground black pepper. Chicken broth soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal!

For the cake recipe; First, mix the sugar and egg in a deep bowl until foamy. Then add the flour, vanilla, cocoa and baking powder and continue mixing. After oiling the cake mold, put the mixture in the oven set at 190 degrees and bake for 4-5 minutes. To make the cream of the wet cake, pour the chocolate cream into the bowl. Add milk to it and beat with a mixer. Prepare the chocolate sauce by whisking so that there are no lumps. Put the cream you made by cutting the cake cake in 3 equal ways and pour the ready-made chocolate chips on it. After pouring the cream on each layer and on the top, pour the chocolate sauce you prepared on the top. Grate chocolate over the sauce. Fresh cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the roll cake recipe; First, beat the eggs with sugar and add a glass of water to it. Add the baking soda and vanilla to the mixture. Pour the flour on it and mix it. Pour the mixture you prepared into the oiled tray. Bake for 10 minutes in a preheated oven at 200 degrees. Then, in another bowl, mix the whipped cream and milk. Spread jam on the cake you have prepared and spread half of the whipped cream you have prepared by spreading it well. Finally, pour the blueberries and roll the cake. Spread the remaining whipped cream on the cake. The roll cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled meatballs recipe with Breadcrumb Flour; First of all, finely chop the onion and garlic and put them in a bowl. Add mince to it. Finely chop the parsley. Add the finely chopped parsley, salt, pepper and cumin to the bowl. Then add the breadcrumbs and crack the egg. Knead until it does not fall apart. After kneading well, let it rest for a while. After resting for half an hour, give flat shapes. Put it in a Teflon pan that you heated and add a little oil and cook both sides of the meatballs. Grilled Meatballs with Breadcrumbs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Plateau Soup with Meat Juice; First, whisk the yogurt, flour and egg yolk. Add cold water to open the consistency and bring to a boil. Then add hot water and broth, stirring. Then wash and drain the rice and put it in the pot. Boil the rice and cook it by adding salt until the soup boils. After taking the highland soup into a serving bowl, melt the butter and add the mint. After pouring the sauce on the plateau soup, the service is ready. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Sausage Egg recipe; First, peel the sausage and then chop it to a thickness of no more than half an inch. Do not use a small pan and place the sausages in the pan first on low heat on a medium-sized stove. Add paprika, black pepper and salt if desired. In the meantime, use a lid to cook the sausages without drying them. After about 4 minutes, turn the sausages and cook for a few more minutes. When the sausages are browned like pomegranate, break the eggs. Continue without the lid until the egg whites are cooked. Make sure the egg is cooked by shaking the pan and remove it from the heat. Sausage Egg is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To make diet ashura; Cook the wheat in the pressure cooker for 20 minutes. Then add 7 glasses of water and cook the wheat until hellen. Add the chickpeas and beans that you soaked the night before to the pot. After cooking for another 20 minutes, remove from the fire. Add honey and dried fruits in it. Serve garnished with walnuts, pomegranate and cinnamon. Diet Ashura is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal:)

For the cabbage soup recipe, first chop the cabbage, tomatoes, onions and peppers into small pieces. Then add all the ingredients to the pot where you add the water. After it is well cooked, serve your cabbage soup by passing it through a blender. If you wish, you can flavor it with spices.

Before you start making the goulash soup recipe, first melt 1 tablespoon of butter. Then grate 1 onion and fry it in oil together with the meat. Cut the potato, celery and pepper into small pieces and add them to the pot. Finally, add 4 glasses of water and dilute the tomato paste slightly and add it to the pot. Cook until the vegetables are soft. Season with salt and white pepper, garnish with chopped dill and serve hot. Goulash soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the eggplant kebab recipe; Peel the eggplants, cut them into thick slices and soak them in salted water. After squeezing the eggplants, put them in the frying oil and fry them until they turn slightly pink. Peel the potatoes and cut them into thick cubes. Very little fry. After waiting for a while on a paper towel to absorb the oil, put the fried ingredients in a flat pan. After chopping and frying 1 tablespoon of onion, garlic and pepper in another pot, throw the meat and cook it until it is slightly soft. After the meat has evaporated, add the tomato, pepper paste, salt and pepper. Spread the cooked meat on the eggplants and add 2 glasses of water and cook until the eggplants and meat are cooked. Eggplant kebab is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the forest kebab recipe; First, put 2 tablespoons of oil and butter. When the oil is hot, add the onions. Fry until it turns pink. Add the meats. Keep frying until it releases the water and absorbs it again. Put the sauce. Mix all the ingredients. Add 2 glasses of water. Close the lid of the pot. Cook until vegetables and meat are tender. Add the peas. Put salt and thyme. Cook the dish for another 5 minutes. Forest kebab is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the chestnut orange cake recipe, add sugar to the eggs you cracked in a bowl and whisk well. Add the grated lemon peels to the mixture and mix well. Then add the orange juice you squeezed out. Add the flour to the cake mix and mix well. Finally, add chestnuts, grapes and walnuts to the mixture. Pour the mixture you prepared into the cake pan and bake in the oven that you previously heated at 170 degrees. Enjoy your chestnut orange cake.

To make celery soup, put olive oil in a large saucepan and heat it up a bit. Add the diced onions to the pot and fry them until they turn translucent. Then add cumin and bay leaves. After turning it a little, add the celery stalks that you cut into small pieces. Fry for a few more minutes and add the diced carrots, a little later the celery and potatoes cut into cubes, mix. Cover the pot and cook for 4-5 minutes, stirring occasionally. Then add boiling water into it and cook on very low heat until the vegetables are cooked. When it gets a little warm, puree it with a hand blender. Add salt and pepper last. You can also add lemon juice if you prefer. Celery soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal!

When starting to make a leek dish, chop the leeks and soak them in water for 5 minutes. Scrape and chop the outside of the carrots and put them in a bowl of water to prevent them from browning. Add the oil to the pan. Drain the carrots from the water and fry them in oil for 2-3 minutes over medium heat. Then drain the water from the leeks and add it to the pot. And right after that, add the tomato paste and red pepper powder. In this way, fry it on low heat until it releases its water and absorbs it. Meanwhile, sort and wash the rice and drain the water. When the leeks absorb the water they release, add the rice, salt and hot water and cook on low heat until the cooking water is absorbed. You can serve it hot with lemon. Your leek dish is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

To make homemade bagels, pour flour, salt, sugar and yeast into a bowl and add water little by little. Knead until it reaches the consistency of an earlobe (about 10-15 minutes) and then let it rest for half an hour. Then, dip the bagel rings, which you have shaped by tearing off pieces of dough, in water with molasses that you have boiled in one-to-one measure. After the water is drained, cover with sesame seeds, lay them on the tray and bake at 220 degrees for 25-30 minutes. Homemade bagel is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal!

For the potato dish, first chop the potato, tomato, onion and pepper and fry the onion in oil. Put the green pepper and garlic on it, then put the tomato paste, put the tomato on it, fry it a little, add potatoes, 3 glasses of hot water, black pepper, cumin and salt, adjust the salt, close the lid. Cook on high heat until the potatoes are soft. Your potato dish is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Caesar Salad recipe: First of all, cut the edges of the toast breads and chop them into cubes. Put two spoons of butter in a pan, add red pepper flakes, thyme, add cubes of bread and fry. Then, fry the chicken meat, cut long and thin, in two spoons of oil in the same pan, slightly pink. Divide the belly salad by washing the arugula in plenty of water and breaking it into a salad bowl by hand. Grate the old cheddar. Squeeze the lemon into a bowl. Spread the crusty bread and chicken pieces on top of the belly salads. Put the remaining olive oil, mayonnaise, mustard, crushed garlic salt and pepper into the bowl where you squeezed the lemon, mix and prepare the sauce. Pour the dressing over the salad and sprinkle with the grated cheese. Dice the tomatoes, chop the cucumbers into rounds and finally add them to the salad bowls. Caesar salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the crepe recipe; First, whisk the eggs and milk in a bowl. Then add the flour, baking powder, oil and salt and continue whisking. The consistency should not be too fluid or too solid. If it's too runny, you can add a little more flour to solidify it. For cooking, you can use a medium or large skillet as desired. Once the pan is hot, drop a drop of oil into it, then take a soup ladle of pancakes from the pan and spread them on the pan. Wait for it to cook very little on medium heat and turn it over with the help of tongs. To prevent it from sticking, put a drop of oil on the bottom of the pan, leaking it from the side of the pan. Use the drip method for all pancakes, otherwise the pancakes will stick to the pan. The crepe is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the cherry bread dessert, add the cherries, cherry juice, water and sugar in a saucepan and boil until the cherries crackle. Arrange the skirts in one layer on the bordeaux. Pour the cherries and half of the boiling water over the meats so that the meatballs are thoroughly wet. Then add another layer of meat and pour the remaining boiling water so that the meat is thoroughly wet. Let your cherry bread dessert cool. Enjoy your meal.

For the bread kadayif recipe, put the meat in two layers in a bowl. Boil water and sugar for syrup in a saucepan. After the syrup is warm, pour the syrup over the meats. Whisk the milk and whipped cream well in another bowl. Pour the whipped cream as desired on the cooled meats. You can serve the bread kadayif by garnishing it with walnuts. Enjoy your meal.

To start applying the cinnamon chocolate cake recipe, you can start adding other ingredients after you wait for the margarine to melt. After whisking the sugar with the margarine, add the 5 egg yolks one by one to the mixture. Add chocolate chips to the milk you have heated in a coffee pot and take it off the stove without allowing it to overheat. After adding the chocolate milk to the liquid mixture, add the flour you mixed in a different bowl (don't forget to sift it for airiness and better rise), lemon peel, baking powder, cinnamon mixture. Mix for a while with the help of a wooden spoon, without allowing the dough to become heavy. With the help of a clean mixer tip, start whisking the egg whites that you separated the yolks by adding the salt. After a while, you will see that it has a foamy consistency. Add it to the main mixture after whisking until you are sure that the whipped cream will not remain in liquid form at the bottom of the bowl. You can cause bubbles to form in the mixture by quickly turning the wooden spoon from the bottom up. In this way, the dough will rise well without getting heavy. After transferring the mixture to the bowl you have oiled, the cake mixture is ready to be placed in the preheated 180 degree oven. After 35 minutes, you can check if the cake is cooked by inserting a knife into the fluffiest part of the cake (the chocolate melted in milk will give you a slightly moist cake). Cinnamon Cocoa Cake is ready to serve! Enjoy your meal! Suggestion; You can adjust the cinnamon and lemon ratios according to your taste. While excess cinnamon leaves a bitter taste, it gives a wonderful aroma when lemon is in season. You can turn it into a simple walnut brownie by adding some walnuts to the cinnamon cocoa cake mix at the very end ;)

For tuna pasta, you can start by heating water for pasta. In the process of chopping the necessary materials for the sauce; Chop the onions into small cubes and add them to the oil you have heated in the pan. Before the onions get too brown, add the peeled tomatoes that you cut into small cubes. (By the way, don't forget to add the pasta after adding some oil and salt to the heated water). Once the tomatoes begin to cook, add the corn, tuna (strain excess oil), salt and pepper. After cooking for 5 minutes, take it off the stove. After adding the sauce to the pasta you have drained, mix it on the stove for a few minutes. Serve by adding parmesan, old cheddar, cheddar grated according to your taste. Tuna pasta is ready to serve, bon appetit! :) Suggestion: If you wish, you can get a slightly sour taste by adding one or more of the capers / corn / jalapeno pickles to the tuna pasta sauce after adding the tomato.

Before you start cooking okra with olive oil, first clean the stems of the okra. Then cut the onion into cubes and grate the tomatoes. After removing the garlic, transfer all the ingredients to a saucepan and add olive oil, juice of half a lemon, salt, sugar, and tomato paste. Finally, add hot water after frying for 10 minutes on low heat. After cooking on low heat for another 20 minutes, okra with olive oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the green lentil recipe; Boil the washed green lentils in a pot by adding water. Chop the onions into small pieces and put the oil and onions in another pot and fry them. After the onions turn pink, add flour and continue frying. After it is well roasted, add the tomato paste and then the boiled lentils to the pot with their water. Let the duckweeds pass by an inch. If it is less, add water. After adding the spices, cook until it boils. When the lentils are cooked, turn off the heat and let them rest for a few minutes. Lentil dish is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the falafel recipe; after boiling the chickpeas that you soaked the night before; pass the onion, garlic and parsley through the robot. Add other ingredients to the mixture and knead well. Give the mixture the shape of meatballs and fry in oil. Falafel is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal!

For the Halloumi Cheese Salad recipe; Wash the lettuce and tomatoes with plenty of water. Finely chop the lettuce and finely chop the tomatoes and put them in a bowl. Add soybean sprouts and corn to the salad ingredients. Add the walnuts and mix. Grill the halloumi. Then add it to the salad by scattering it. Halloumi cheese salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

In order to make an olive cake, first start whisking the eggs in a deep bowl. After the beaten eggs foam well, add the specified amount of water, milk, yoghurt, salt and oil to the mixture. Sift the flour and baking powder and add them to the mixture. Keep whisking until your olive cake batter has the right consistency. Fry the chopped onions in a separate pan. Add the roasted onions to your mixture with diced halloumi, pitted olives, finely chopped mint and dill. Mix until all ingredients are evenly distributed. When your dough has the right consistency, pour it into a greased tray or borehole and sprinkle your sesame seeds on it. Bake in a preheated oven at 175 degrees for 40-45 minutes. You can insert a toothpick into your olive cake to see if it is cooked or not. Enjoy your meal.

For stuffed chicken, let's first season the chicken with salt and pepper. Let's prepare breadcrumbs, flour and eggs in separate bowls. Melt the butter in a pan and fry the flour. When the smell of flour comes out, let's add cold milk. Let's add sliced mushrooms and cook until the sauce thickens. A little nutmeg can be added if desired. After turning it off, add the boiled corn and mix. Let's put the sauce we prepared into 1 finely beaten chicken, cover it with another slice of chicken and insert a toothpick. Add salt and black pepper to the flour and breadcrumbs. Let's dip the chickens in flour, egg and breadcrumbs respectively. If possible, fry it in a deep fryer. It can be served with french fries, rice and salad. Enjoy your meal:)

While making banana cookies; Banana Pudding, powdered sugar, butter, oil and vanilla are mixed until it reaches a creamy consistency. It is kneaded by adding starch, baking powder, flour, crushed hazelnuts or walnuts. Place in walnut-sized pieces in a tray on greaseproof paper. It is cooked for 20 minutes so that it is not very browned. It can be sprinkled with powdered sugar and served upon request. Enjoy your meal :)

Into our kneading bowl; Yoghurt, melted butter, salt, feta cheese, 1 whole egg+1 egg white is added and mixed, baking powder is kneaded by adding finely chopped dill and as much flour as it takes. From the dough we have kneaded, we take walnut-sized meringues, roll them and arrange them on the baking tray, brush with egg yolk and bake at 200 degrees. (20-25 minutes until browned).

For the Baked Spinach Pasta recipe; First, boil the pasta in salted water for 8-9 minutes. In the meantime, clean and finely chop the spinach, then cook it in a saucepan with the cream for 5 minutes. Add the spinach to the boiled pasta, add salt, pepper and garlic powder into it and mix. Put the mixture on the tray, add the grated cheddar cheese on it and finally, after sprinkling thyme, bake at 220 degrees for about 15 minutes until golden brown. Baked Spinach Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the beetroot cabbage salad recipe; First boil the beets. Peel and grate the boiled beets. Wash the cabbage in plenty of water and chop finely. Put the grated beets and cabbages in a bowl. Add the salt, crushed garlic, mayonnaise and yoghurt to the bowl with the beetroot and mix well. Take it on the serving plate. Cabbage Salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the raspberry muffin, first beat the eggs and sugar with a mixer until it reaches a creamy consistency. Add milk, oil, vanilla and coconut and mix. Mix and sift the flour and baking powder, add to the dough and beat for 1 more minute. Grease the muffin tins and divide the dough into them. Place the raspberries on the dough. Bake in the oven set at 180 C until golden brown. Raspberry muffin is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For eggplant slices with halloumi cheese, first wash the eggplants and slice them in 1 cm sizes without peeling them. Soak in salted water until baking. Peel the garlic, mash in a mortar and mix with olive oil. Set your oven to the highest setting and heat it up. Grease the baking tray on which you will cook the eggplants by applying the mixture you have prepared with the help of a brush. Place the eggplants on the tray and grease them with a brush, bake for 7–8 minutes (be careful not to dry out too much). Slice the tomatoes and halloumi cheese and arrange 1 slice of tomato and 1 thin slice of halloumi on each eggplant. Garnish with julienne slices of pepper and olives. Cook the halloumi cheeses until they are well browned, garnish with corn kernels if desired and serve. Enjoy your meal :)

When starting to make a parsley omelet, first sprinkle the eggs with salt and whisk them well. Add the chopped parsley, dill and garlic. Finally, add the flour and mix well. Heat the oil in the pan, pour the ingredients you prepared and cook. After browning on both sides, your parsley omelette is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

When starting to make apple pie, first of all, mix all the dough ingredients to get a soft dough. After dividing it into two parts, leave it in the refrigerator for a while. Meanwhile, grate the apples and mix with sugar and cinnamon. Roll out the dough that you previously reserved with the help of a rolling pin and place it on a greased round tray. After straining the juice of the apple mixture, add it. Finally, grate the dough you have kept in the refrigerator on the apple mixture. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven until golden brown. Your apple pie is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal  :)

For the Sausage Egg Potato recipe; First, peel and chop the boiled potatoes. Heat the oil in a wide and deep pan or saucepan, add the potatoes into cubes, quarter the sausage and fry them. Add desired salt and pepper. Turn down the heat when the potatoes turn slightly pink. In a separate bowl, whisk the eggs and spread over the potatoes. Shut the pan. When the eggs reach the desired consistency, turn off the stove and let them rest for 2-3 minutes with the mouth closed. Potato with Sausage and Egg is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the carrot soup recipe; After chopping all the ingredients, put them in a saucepan. Add water and cook until boiling. After cooking, pass it through a hand blender until it has a smooth consistency. Add the milk to the mixture and boil it for a few more minutes and finally add the oil you have heated to the soup. Carrot Soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal!

When starting to make the Kazandibi recipe, first mix the rice flour, flour and starch. Add 1 glass of milk and mix and boil the remaining milk by adding sugar and salt. Then, take a ladle of unboiled milk and add it to the starchy mixture, mix and add this mixture to the boiling pot. Pour the mixture you have prepared on the bottom of the tray after sprinkling powdered sugar. Take the tray you have prepared on the stove and cook by turning both sides. Then cool the cooked dessert tray in cold water. Your winner is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

When starting to make the chicken breast recipe, first boil and shred the chicken. Wash the chicken meat with cold water and leave it for 20 minutes. Then boil the milk and put the boiled milk and the squeezed breast meat and pass it through the hand blender 3 times. Stir and cook for 25 minutes. Mix 2,5 tea glasses of water, rice flour and starch in the bowl. After cooking on low heat for about 5 minutes, add 1 cup of granulated sugar and cook for 15 minutes until it gets a thick consistency like gum. After removing it from the stove, add the vanilla and mix it. After wetting the prepared bowl with water, pour the chicken breast. After it cools, put it in the refrigerator. Chicken breast is ready to serve after resting. You can serve it with a sprinkle of cinnamon on top. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe of Pastry with Olives; Before starting the preparation, first take the flour in the mixing bowl and add sugar and salt to it. After adding yeast to the middle of the flour, put oil and egg white on it. Add warm water to the yeast and after the yeast dissolves, mix the flour and knead the pastry dough. Divide the dough into 3 parts and roll it out with a rolling pin. Finally, add the pitted black olives and wrap the dough. Cut into two finger thicknesses and place on a baking tray. Brush it with egg yolk and bake it in a preheated 190 degree oven. Olive Pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
