When starting to prepare the Zucchini Gratin recipe, firstly chop the zucchini coarsely and boil them in salted water for 5 minutes. On the other hand, melt the butter in a saucepan, add the flour and fry it until it turns pink. Then slowly add the milk and add salt and pepper. After crushing the drained zucchini with a fork, place them in the bowl and pour the sauce you prepared on it. Sprinkle the grated cheddar cheese on it and bake in the preheated oven until golden brown. Zucchini gratin is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Quince Jam recipe; First, peel and grate the quinces. Add the grated quince and the seeds of the quince and boil it. After the quinces are cooked, add 2 kg of granulated sugar and continue cooking by adding 10 cloves. 10 minutes before the jam is cooked, add lemon juice and finally boil it. Your quince jam is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the künefe recipe; First of all, for the syrup, dissolve the sugar in water and add cinnamon and put it on the stove. While it starts to boil, cut a lemon into six, throw a piece into it and let it cool. Break the fresh kadayif ball by hand. Then grease the tray with butter and cut the remaining butter into small pieces and put it on the kadaif. Divide half of the kadayif evenly on 4 trays and grate and spread the cheese. Spread the remaining kadayif on top and leave in the refrigerator for half an hour. Bake in a preheated 270 degree oven for 15 minutes. After removing the trays from the oven, pour the cold syrup over them. Finally, serve with their own plates by putting cream and ground pistachios on top. Kunefe is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the gluten-free spinach cake recipe; Wash and boil the spinach leaves in plenty of water. boil the leaves. Pass the boiled spinach through the washer. Add eggs, sugar and vanilla to a bowl and beat with a mixer. Then add the spinach and oil and mix. Finally, add the gluten-free flour, baking powder and walnuts and mix. Pour into a glass container greased with margarine and bake in an oven preheated to 150 degrees. Gluten-free spinach cake is ready to serve after decorating it with coconut. Enjoy your meal.

When starting the gluten-free wet cake recipe, first beat the eggs and sugar until foamy. Then add water, oil, cocoa and vanilla and beat with a mixer. After separating half a glass of water from the mixture, add flour and baking powder to the remaining mixture and mix. Pour it into an oiled cake mold and bake in a preheated oven at 175 degrees. Finally, pour the previously prepared liquid mixture into the baked cake. Gluten free moist cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Buckwheat Rice recipe; Before starting the production, first wash the buckwheat and add 1 glass of warm water to it and wait for it to swell. Then, cut the onion into cubes, fry it with olive oil and cook it by adding the livers. Add the liver mixture, boiled corn, chopped dill and walnuts into the buckwheat that has not been cooled. Buckwheat Rice is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

When starting the leek bread recipe, firstly chop the leeks into small pieces, grate the potatoes and carrots finely and cook them in oil. Then, mix the cheese, yogurt, oil and eggs in a bowl. Finally, add corn flour, salt, parsley, cheese, baking powder and pour it on the tray where the greaseproof paper is laid. After applying egg yolk on it, bake in a preheated oven at 220 degrees. Your leek bread is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the saucy lentil soup; After washing and draining the green lentils, we boil the carrots, potatoes, onions and garlic that we cut into small pieces in 6 glasses of water in a saucepan until the potatoes are cooked, then we add the salt, black pepper and chili pepper and pass them through the blender. The naughty lentil soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe of Juicy Meatballs with Chickpeas; Add ground beef, salt and pepper and knead. Prepare some large meatballs from hazelnuts. Put the prepared meatballs on a floured tray. Let the meatballs be covered in flour by shaking them. Finely chop the onion. Put it in a saucepan with the oil and fry it on low heat until it turns pink. Add the tomato paste and continue to fry for 1-2 minutes on low heat. Add boiling water to it. Add the boiled chickpeas and salt. Boil the water for 2-3 minutes and add the meatballs. When the meatballs are cooked, add butter on them. Boil 1-2 times and turn off the heat. Juicy Meatballs with Chickpeas is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

When making raw meatballs with potatoes, first, to prepare ground beef with olive oil, mince and olive oil are put in a pan and roasted on low heat. Onion is chopped and added to it. The lid is closed, and it is cooked on low heat until the onion juice is released and absorbed. Add salt, black pepper, chili flakes and cook for 2-3 minutes. Add chopped parsley and mix. It is taken from the stove. Now that the ground beef is ready, we can move on to preparing the meatballs. Boiled potatoes are grated. Finely chop the onion, garlic and parsley. Meatballs are soaked with bulgur. Spices, half of the grated potato, tomato paste are put in a mixing bowl. First, onions, garlic, tomato paste and spices are mixed. Mix the bulgur with potatoes and start kneading. Added pomegranate molasses. It is kneaded like raw meatballs, but don't be intimidated. The remaining potato is finished by adding it as it dries (2-3 times). When the meatballs soften and get thick, add chopped parsley and olive oil. Mix well, serve. Let me explain for those who don't know. You may say, what does roasting meatballs and ground beef have to do with it? Our meatballs are eaten by dipping them in this olive oil minced meat. Potato Meatballs are indispensable in Hatay. Tip: Potatoes must be freshly boiled. The potato you boiled 1 day ago prevents the meatballs from getting consistency, and the taste will not be good. While soaking the bulgur, the water should be cold and kneaded without waiting for a long time. Raw meatballs with potatoes are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

To prepare the stuffing of kibbeh; Start frying the minced meat in a pan by adding salt. Add the finely chopped onions just after the ground beef leaves its juice and starts to shrink. Meanwhile, add 2 tablespoons of olive oil. After the onions and ground beef are roasted, add other spices and ground walnuts. The stuffing of the kibbeh is ready after this process. In the preparation phase of kibbeh; Soak the bulgur and semolina with 1.5-2 glasses of water for half an hour in a separate place. Then knead it well so that it becomes a dough. Cover the dough by putting 1 teaspoon of the inside of the dough you have prepared into the dough you have opened by shaping. Put the prepared kibbeh in boiling water and boil for 10-15 minutes. Serve after 2-3 minutes. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mushroom Tavern Rice recipe; Add the grated onions to the butter and oil you melted in the pan and fry them. After the onions are roasted, add the tomato paste and the chopped mushrooms and sauté. Add the thyme and mix the mixture. Add the washed bulgur and other spices. For Mushroom Tavern Rice, add water and let it cook. Enjoy your meal.

For the mince pies recipe, first chop the onions into cubes. Fry the chopped onions in a little oil. Add the ground beef to the onions and continue frying. Finally, add the spices to the inner mortar and mix. In another bowl, whisk together the milk, oil and 2 eggs and 1 egg white. Spread 1/4 of this mixture on the dough you have opened on a large surface. After laying the other phyllo on this yufka, spread 1/4 of the mixture more. Divide the phyllo into 8 parts with the help of a knife. Add the stuffing you prepared for your meat pie to the wide side of each triangle, wrap it like a spring roll and place it on the baking tray. Prepare the other two phyllo dough in the same way. Spread the egg yolk on the pastries and bake them in the oven at 200 degrees until they are browned. Enjoy your minced meat pie. :)

For the cinnamon cake; Put all the ingredients in a bowl and whisk until combined. Pour into the greased cake mold and bake at 150 degrees for 50 minutes. Cinnamon Cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

To make stuffed mussels, first scrape the shells of the mussels you bought and wash them thoroughly and remove the broken or dead mussels. Boil the mussels in this water by adding 1 teaspoon of salt to 1 liter of water. As soon as the mussels open, take them off the stove and put them in a bowl. If there are any mussels that haven't opened, separate them as well. Let the boiling water cool down. To prepare the stuffed pilaf, fry the finely chopped onions in olive oil. Add the grated garlic and peanuts and continue frying. Then add rice and other spices respectively. Take two glasses of the mussel boiling water that you have left to cool, add it to the mixture and cook it on low heat until it absorbs its water. At this stage, the rice will remain somewhat firm. Fill the mussels with the stuffed rice and put them in a deep pot vertically. Add the remaining 2 glasses of water from the boiling water and 2 extra glasses of water and cook for another 20 minutes on medium heat. You can serve it with lemons cut into circles. Stuffed mussels are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal! :)

When starting to make easy pastry, first the yolk of one of the eggs is separated to be spread on it. All ingredients (except cheddar and sausage) are mixed and kneaded. A dough that will not stick to the hand is obtained. Meringues about the size of a tangerine are cut from the dough and rolled out by hand, a mixture of cheddar and sausage (chopped sausages) is put in the middle and shaped like a half moon or round. Arrange on a paper-lined baking tray, brush with beaten egg yolk and sprinkle with black cumin seeds. Baked at 180 degrees for 30 minutes. Easy donut is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Shakshuka recipe; First, peel the eggplants as variegated and cut them into cubes. Finely chop the onions and peppers and fry them in oil until they turn pink. Fry the eggplants in another place and remove the oil thoroughly with a napkin. Add tomato paste to the peppers and onions first, then add the tomatoes and garlic that you cut into cubes and sauté well. After adding the spices, add the water. Finally, you can add the fried eggplants to the mixture and serve the şakşuka. Enjoy your meal :)

For the pumpkin dessert; After washing the pumpkin, which is about 1 kg, well, let's cut it into cubes and place it in our pot. After sprinkling sugar on it, add half a glass of water and boil on high; After boiling, let it cook for 30-40 minutes on low heat. When it softens, mash it into a puree and let it cool. In the meantime, let's crush the walnuts so that they are not too small. After the mashed pumpkin is cold, let's spread the puree in the thickness of 3 fingers on the cake mold in which we sprinkled the crumbled walnuts. Then, let's place baby biscuits vertically and optional cocoa or light biscuits at frequent intervals. Let's finish the rest with pumpkin puree. Let's put our dessert in the refrigerator, then turn it upside down and put it on a serving plate and serve it by slicing. Enjoy your meal! :)

Before starting to make the patetop, first of all, let's boil the potatoes, peel them and grate them. Chop the spring onions and onions very finely and fry them with 1 teaspoon of oil. In a separate bowl, mix lemon, olive oil, pomegranate syrup, vinegar, mint, chili pepper, sumac, isot, onions and salt. Knead it all well in a large bowl. Let's make balls the size of walnuts and place an olive on them. If desired, you can add parsley inside or on top. Bon appetit! :)

For the recipe for zucchini with spinach in the oven; First of all, wash the skins of the zucchini without peeling them and divide them into 4 parts. Carve without removing the bottom with the zucchini peeler. On the other side, chop the onion for food in a saucepan and sauté in 1 tablespoon of olive oil. Then, chop the mushrooms into small pieces, add them to the pot and fry them until their water is gone. Then add the washed and chopped spinach leaves, cook until the water evaporates. While the spinach is cooking, add the grated garlic, salt, black pepper and paprika. When the spinach is drained, mix it and let it cool. Fill the cooked spinach paste into the previously carved zucchini. Finally, sprinkle grated cheddar cheese on it and bake in the oven preheated to 180 degrees for 15-20 minutes. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the Parsley Fish Meatballs recipe; First, scrape the scales of the fish with a knife. Wash the fish that you have cleaned the scales thoroughly. Cut the cleaned fish into several pieces and put them in a saucepan. Add enough water to cover the fish. Add salt to it and wait until it boils. Take the pot off the heat 15 minutes after it starts to boil. Put the boiled fish in another pot with the help of a strainer. After cooling, separate the meat parts of the fish from the skin and bones. Cut the fish meat into small pieces with a fork or with your hand. Add the previously grated onions on the fish. Then add the bread crumb, egg, parsley and spices, and knead the mixture thoroughly. Serve the fish balls you have shaped by frying them in a little oil. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for green lentils with yogurt; Boil 2 glasses of green lentils in a saucepan with 3 glasses of water, add 1 teaspoon of salt. After straining the boiled lentils, mix them with 1 glass of yogurt. Add mint and paprika to it. Green lentils with yogurt are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the chicken barley noodle salad recipe; Put the chicken breast, 4 glasses of water, salt, pepper and 1 onion in a pot and boil the chicken meat. Shred the chicken meat after it is boiled. Then put the olive oil and butter in another pot, add the barley vermicelli and fry the vermicelli. Add 3 glasses of water from the water in which you boiled the chickens and cook. Keep adding water, checking the noodle's water absorption rate. Finely chop the parsley, green onions, red pepper and pickles. Strain the brewed vermicelli, put it in a serving bowl with the chicken meat and chopped vegetables and mix. Serve with lemon juice and optionally ground red pepper. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for sauteed meat with vegetables with soybean oil; Put the soybean oil in the pan and dice the meat and add it. Saute on high heat. Chop the onions for cooking, the tomatoes into cubes, the peppers and carrots into rings. Then continue sautéing by adding the onions, carrots, peppers and tomatoes in order. Add water and close the lid and cook until the water is absorbed. Sauteed meat with soybean oil and vegetables is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetable Chinese soup recipe; Wash the zucchini, leeks and carrots. Scrape the outside of the carrots and squash. Chop the zucchini, carrot and leek you scraped into the thickness of a matchstick. Put vegetable oil in a pan and add the chopped vegetables and sauté for 5 minutes. Sprinkle starch on top, add 6 glasses of water. Chop the chicken meat into cubes, add the meat and boil the soup for 20 minutes. Add the black pepper and ginger powder, mix a few more times and boil for another 10 minutes. If the soup becomes less watery, you can add water. Vegetable Chinese Soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled polenta recipe; First of all, clean and grate the skins of 1 kg of zucchini. Grate the Parmessan cheese and mix it with the grated zucchini. Mix the olive oil, dried thyme, salt, pepper and crushed garlic into the mixture you have prepared and knead. Spread the mixture you have prepared on a tray, flatten it and cut it squarely and cook it on an electric grill or in a pan. Then, cook the tomatoes, cut into rings, on both sides and place them on the zucchini slices and arrange them on the serving plates. Grilled polenta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Milan Style Rice Recipe; Heat 4 tablespoons of olive oil and fry the onion and bacon in olive oil until slightly soft. Then add the rice and stir fry for about 2 minutes. Add 3 glasses of chicken stock and 1 glass of water on top and boil on low heat. Once mixed, close the lid of the pot. Cook for an average of 20 minutes or until the rice is soft and drained. Add salt and pepper to taste, add half of the grated cheese to the rice and mix. Milan Style Rice is ready to serve. Spread the rest of the cheese on top of the serving, if desired. Enjoy your meal.

For the pumpkin yogurt recipe; Peel and thinly slice 4 zucchini. Get into a debt; Add oil and salt to them and mix well. Put them in the oven until they are browned. Then whisk 1.5 cups of yogurt, add salt and garlic. After you take the zucchini out of the oven, put them on the serving plate and pour the yogurt sauce you prepared on it. Then you can decorate the sauced zucchini with chili pepper and mint. Enjoy your meal :)

For Tomato Pepper Recipe; Scratch the peppers, remove the seeds and chop finely. Put a small amount of oil in a pan and add the peppers. Sprinkle salt on the peppers and fry. Peel and dice the tomatoes. Add the tomatoes to the roasted peppers and continue frying. When the tomatoes are soft, sprinkle thyme on top. Fry the tomatoes and peppers together with the cakes for an average of 2 more minutes, then transfer them to the serving plate and serve hot. Pepper with Tomato is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Butter Hummus recipe; Soak 500gr chickpeas overnight. Cook in a pressure cooker until well cooked. Drain the water completely. Then puree the chickpeas. Garlic is crushed. Mix the crushed garlic with the mashed chickpeas. Mix the tahini into the chickpeas and add salt. Spread the resulting mixture on a serving plate. You can add pine nuts to the butter melted in the pan, roast them and pour them over the hummus and serve hot. Butter hummus is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe of Cercerun; Chop the onions as piyaz. Heat oil in the pan. Then add chopped onions on it and kill it without frying. Meanwhile, mix the yogurt and salt. After the onions turn yellow, add 2 tablespoons of salted yoghurt and feed the onions and remove from the fire. It can be served by adding paprika on request. Cercerun is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For the Roast Zucchini recipe; Wash and peel the zucchini and cut them about 1 cm thick. Salt and wait before frying. Start frying by putting it in 2 glasses of olive oil that has been heated in a deep bowl. Fry until the top and bottom turn pink. After frying, you can take the zucchini, which you have drained completely, on a serving plate and serve with tomato sauce or yoghurt. Enjoy your meal.

For Chicken Burger Recipe; Grind 500 grams of chicken breast and 2 cloves of garlic in a robot. After putting this mixture in a large bowl, add the egg, onion and bread crumbs and mix. Add the red pepper and cumin to the mixture. Mix the mixture you have obtained thoroughly and turn it into a mortar. Cut pieces of the mortar according to the size of the hamburger and shape it. While shaping, you can oil your palm so that it does not stick to your hand. After the oil is hot in the pan, cook the meatballs by throwing them in the oil. Put the leaf lettuce in your hamburger bun and add your meatballs, tomato pickles, respectively. You can use ketchup and mayonnaise according to your wish. Enjoy your meal :)

For the homemade hamburger bun recipe; Mix 2.5 cups of flour, 1 teaspoon of salt, 2 teaspoons of sugar and 1 teaspoon of dry yeast in a deep bowl by kneading well with your hand. Add the olive oil, yogurt, egg and half a glass of water slowly and continue kneading the dough. Take the dough on the floured counter and continue kneading. Cover the dough with a container that will prevent air from getting into the dough and let the dough rest for 10 minutes. Divide the dough into 5 equal parts. Form an oval the size of a hamburger bun between your palm and the counter until the dough is smooth. Press the dough on top of it and place it on the tray on which you have greased paper. Wrap the bread with cling wrap and let it rest for 45 minutes. After waiting, remove the cling film and apply egg yolk on the bread and sprinkle sesame seeds. Then bake the tray in a preheated oven at 190 degrees for 20 minutes until golden brown. Homemade hamburger buns are ready to use. Enjoy your meal.

For Roasted Cheddar Toast Recipe; Sprinkle salt on top of your roasts. Spread margarine on and inside the bread. Crush the roasts and place them in your sandwich bread. Place the cheddar slices on your roasts and place your sandwiches in your toaster. You can decorate your toasts with tomatoes, peppers and parsley. Enjoy your meal :)

For the egg roll recipe; Add 4 eggs, 2 tablespoons of milk and salt to a deep bowl and whisk well with a fork. Find the egg sauce you have prepared on both sides of the breads. After heating 1 tea glass of oil in the pan, slowly put the breads in the pan. Toast the bread on both sides until golden brown. Egg Bread is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Yengen Toast Recipe; Cook the salami, sausage and bacon in the toaster for 30 seconds. Add 1 slice of cheddar, 1 slice of salami, 2 slices of sausage and pastrami on 1 slice of bread. Then add 1 slice of cheddar and 1 more slice of tomato, put the toasted bread and margarine it. Do the same with your other toast, place the toast in the machine and never press it. Cook until browned. Enjoy your meal :)

For the tahini oat rusk recipe; Mix all the tahini, oat and water in a bowl and make a dough. Spread the dough on wax paper by pressing it with your hand. Put another greaseproof paper on the dough and straighten the dough with a rolling pin so that it is approximately 0.5 cm thick. Take the wax paper on top. Divide the dough into equal square pieces with a knife and bake in the oven at 200 degrees for 10-15 minutes until it turns light brown. Enjoy your meal.

For the Ayvalık toast recipe; Finely chop the sausage, salami and sausages. Slice the cheddar cheese, pickles and tomatoes. Saute the sausage, salami and sausage in a pan. Warm the toasted bread in the toaster. Then put the cheddar cheese and then all the ingredients between two breads and reheat in the toaster. Enjoy your meal.

After the zucchini is grated, squeeze the juice well. Then chop the other ingredients into small pieces and mix all the ingredients. Bake the material you poured on the oiled paper in the oven at 200 degrees. Enjoy your meal.

For the bread; Flour, salt, yeast, sugar and water are put in a bowl and kneaded. Then it is left for 30-40 minutes and rolled into small pieces and placed on the tray. It is cooked at 180 degrees. Dove interior; Sausages, salami and sausages are sliced ​​and cooked in a toaster. The prepared bread is heated in the toaster. One side of Tulum cheese is fried. Ingredients are put into the bread. Served with ketchup and mayonnaise. Enjoy your meal.

For the granola recipe; Crack the almonds well and mix all the dry ingredients in a bowl. In a separate bowl, whisk together all the wet ingredients with a fork. Pour wet ingredients on top of dry ingredients and mix. Preheat the oven to 150C. Line two baking trays with parchment paper. Divide the mixture evenly into the baking trays and put them in the oven. Bake for about 40 minutes by changing the location of the trays every 10 minutes and mixing the ingredients. Thanks to this mixing process, the remaining pieces will also be crunchy. After cooking, leave the baking trays to cool at room temperature and keep stirring occasionally. Granola may have a soft consistency at first, but it will become crunchier as it cools. Once completely cooled, transfer to airtight containers and store in the refrigerator. Enjoy your meal

For the homemade lahmacun recipe; Put the flour in a bowl, add the yeast and salt and mix. Pour the olive oil into the flour along with the warm water and mix. Then flour the counter and your hands and knead the dough until it is elastic and soft. After oiling the bowl and putting the dough in it, let it rise for about 30-40 minutes until it doubles in size. While the dough is fermenting, put the finely chopped peppers, onions, parsley and tomatoes in a bowl. Add paprika, black pepper, cumin, ground beef and mix well. Put the mixture aside and flour the dough you have kept waiting and divide it into equal parts and roll each piece you cut out with a rolling pin so that it is thin but not torn. First, apply some tomato paste on the rolled dough and spread it with your hand. Then put the mortar and spread it with your hand. Heat the Teflon pan at maximum temperature in the grill section of the oven. After warming up, put the lahmacun you prepared in it and bake it in the oven until the underside is lightly browned. When the edges are crispy, take it out of the oven, fold it in half and cover it, and after waiting for a while, your lahmacun is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For diet apple dessert recipe; Mix water and lemon juice in a bowl. While mixing the sweetener and cinnamon in one of the other two bowls, melt the butter in the other bowl. Peel the apples, remove the cores and cut them in half. Soak in lemon water and rinse. Next, dip the bottom of the apple into the butter and then into the sweetener and cinnamon mixture. Set the oven to 190 degrees and place the apples on the baking tray with the sugary side up. Bake for about 40-50 minutes until the apples are soft. Wait for the baked apples to cool and after the apples are taken to another place, pour the remaining apple juice on the apples. Serve with a dollop of whipped cream or whipped cream and ground walnuts, if desired. Diet apple dessert is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

We mix eggs and sugar thoroughly. Then we pass milk, lemon and strawberry through a blender and add egg-sugar and olive oil on it and whisk. After mixing well, add the coarse flour, vanilla, baking powder and cinnamon. We wait for 15 minutes for the oat bran to absorb the mixture. We pour the mixture into muffin cups, put the fruits inside or outside, and put them in the oven preheated to 170 degrees. Your muffins are ready when the top turns a little pink and grabs! Enjoy your meal.

Break the egg on the flour, add salt and add water by kneading with your hand. Knead a bowl of ground beef, finely chopped onion and finely chopped parsley and mix them together. Afterwards, divide the dough you have rested into meringues with your hand and open each meringues with a rolling pin and cut into squares. Put the stuffing inside the squares and seal it. Boil water and olive oil in a saucepan. Throw meat or chicken bouillon on it according to your taste, then throw the ravioli in it and cook it. Your ravioli is ready! If desired, you can flavor your ravioli by pouring yogurt, boiled water with tomato paste and sumac on it. Enjoy your meal.

If we have grated carrot, finely chopped red pepper, 1-2 cloves of chopped garlic, finely chopped onion, red chili pepper, ground cumin and powdered turmeric and a handful of parsley, we can start our menemen. Add the onion and garlic to the pan with olive oil and fry for two minutes. Put the carrots and peppers in it and wait for it to soften by mixing. Add the well-drained tofu to the pan by crumbling the water and continue mixing. Add the remaining spices in the specified amount or according to your own taste and continue mixing for 1-2 minutes until all of them are well mixed. Finally, pour the lemon juice 1 minute before turning off the fire and mix it. Optionally, you can use parsley to decorate the menemen while serving. This menemen is a very suitable food for vegans, as it is high in tofu and does not contain eggs. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Meatballs with Mushroom Sauce with Beetroot; Put the minced meat, finely chopped onion, chopped garlic, dill, parsley, breadcrumbs, parsley and salt and pepper to your taste in a deep bowl and knead well. After kneading well, break off walnut-sized pieces and form into meatballs. Fry in a low-oil pan. For the mushroom sauce; In another pan, add 1 tablespoon of oil and fry 3 tablespoons of flour until lightly browned. then put the finely chopped mushrooms in it. After the mushrooms are sautéed, add 2 glasses of milk and stir until dark. After turning off the stove, add salt and pepper. For Beet Puree; After boiling the beets, puree them with the help of a blender. Add some water, salt and 1 tablespoon of butter into it and mix. After you put the cooked meatballs into the service, you can put the mushroom sauce on it and serve it with beet puree. Enjoy your meal.

For the Italian-style stewed veal recipe, boil the veal until it releases its own juices. Put the grated onions and butter in another pot and stir until they turn pink. Add boiled meat, tomato paste and potatoes and fry for 5 minutes. Finally, add the parsley and mix. Boiled beef with Italian style vegetables is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal..

For the artichoke lettuce salad recipe; Slice the red peppers in length and cook them in a pan with 1 teaspoon of olive oil and turn off the heat. Boil 2 artichokes in a little water and slice thinly. Wash the lettuce in plenty of water and chop it into medium thickness. Put the remaining olive oil and all the ingredients in the salad bowl and mix well. Transfer to a serving plate and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the homemade italian pasta recipe; Sift the flour and put it in a deep bowl. Add salt and beaten egg and knead until it becomes a hard dough. Divide the dough into 4 parts. Roll out the dough by thinning it with the help of a rolling pin. Flour both sides of the rolled dough. Roll it up tightly and then cut it with the help of a knife, leaving a few inches at a time. Boil the pasta you prepared in water and serve it with the sauce you want. Enjoy your meal.

Boil 500 g of sorted fresh red kidney beans in a separate pot (slightly soft consistency). Put olive oil in your medium-sized pan. Put 300 g of low-fat meat cut into cubes and let it sauté on low heat, stirring occasionally, until the water left by the meat is absorbed. Never add salt while sautéing. Add your diced onions, red peppers and diced carrots. Saute the onions together until they turn pink. Add 1 teaspoon of tomato paste and mix. Add your diced tomatoes. Add your red kidney beans that you boiled in a separate pot to the pot. About 5 minutes Cook together. Add 2-2.5 glasses of heated water in accordance with the amount of food, not too much, and cook on medium heat until the red kidney beans and carrots reach the consistency of cooking. Enjoy your meal.

For the cheddar toast recipe; First, warm the bread a little in the toaster. Then put the cheese on one slice and cover the other slice on it. Put in the toaster until the top is browned. Cheddar toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Creamy Tomato Ravioli recipe; Put water and some salt in a deep pot and boil the ravioles. Put olive oil in a separate pan, finely chop the spring onions, finely chop the garlic, and dice the tomatoes and fry them in oil. As it sautes, add lemon juice, cream, basil and parsley leaves and mix. Drain the ravioli and put on serving plates. Pour the creamy tomato sauce you prepared on the plates over the ravioli. Creamy Tomato Ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

While beating the egg whites with the mixer, add the corn flour and powdered sugar and continue beating. Then transfer the mixture to a saucepan and cook until it thickens. After cooking, leave to cool in the refrigerator. After it cools down, add mascarpone cheese and mix it. Pour the mixture into serving plates, garnish with raspberries and pistachios and leave to cool. Serve cold. Enjoy your meal.

Knead the crumbled biscuits with melted margarine and place in a clamped bowl. Put it in the refrigerator to cool. While they are cooling, beat the ricotta cheese, fruit sugar, lemon zest, lemon juice and egg yolks in the bowl with a mixer. Pour this mixture over the biscuit mixture you have cooled in the refrigerator. Bake in the preheated oven for half an hour. Leave the baked cake to cool in the refrigerator. For the sauce; Mix the strawberries you cut in half with strawberry jam. Take the cheesecake out of the refrigerator, put the strawberries on it and serve.

For the duck meat sauce pasta recipe; Boil the pasta in a saucepan with half of water in it. While the pasta is boiling, put the duck meat in a pot and boil it in 3 glasses of water until the water is gone. Add 3 tablespoons of oil to a pan and heat the oil on low heat. When the oil is hot, thinly slice the boiled duck meat and add it to a pan. Lightly fry the meat in oil. Grate the onion and carrot on it, finely chop the dill and add it with tomato paste, salt, pepper and thyme. Add 1 cup of water and continue cooking for 3-4 more minutes. Drain the boiled pasta and put it in a deep bowl. Pour the duck meat sauce you prepared on the pasta and mix it a few times. Serve evenly on plates. Enjoy your meal.

Fry the onions in a buttered pan. Add the sausages you cut into rings and add the cheeses by breaking the eggs on it. Add nutmeg, salt, sage leaves, mustard, milk, and crusty bread and mix. Put the mixture in the preheated oven with the help of a baking dish. Bake for 30-40 minutes and serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Pasta with Arugula Sauce recipe; Cook the pasta in water to which you add salt for 10 minutes, keeping it slightly firm. For Pasta Sauce; Put the arugula, walnuts, olive oil, tulum cheese and garlic in a blender. Add the sauce to the pasta you have drained and mix. Pasta with Arugula Sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the spicy chicken leg recipe; Chop the chicken coarsely and fry in hot oil. Throw all the ingredients except coconut milk over the chicken and cook for 10 minutes. Then pour the coconut milk over it and take it off the heat. Enjoy your meal.

For Biryani Rice recipe; Boil the water in a large pot. Add all the spices except mint and saffron to the water. Add the rice and cook until the rice is almost completely swollen. Drain the rice and return it to the pot. Sprinkle the mint and saffron over the rice. Cover the pot with aluminum foil. Rest for 15 minutes. Serve with fried onions if you wish. Enjoy your meal.

250 grams of lamb meat is sealed, then butter is added and water is added and the meat is boiled. After the onions are chopped, they are cooked in oil. The juice of the boiled meat is taken into a bowl. Meat is placed on the bottom of the Teflon pot. The meat is covered with caramelized onions. Add chickpeas on the onions and spread. Finally, rice is added, spices are added. Half and half water and broth are added by mixing. After the pilaf is cooked, it is turned upside down on the tray and steamed pilaf is served. Enjoy your meal..

For the Indian style lentil soup recipe; Cook the red lentils in water until soft. Cut the potatoes and eggplants into cubes. Add cubed potatoes and eggplants, powdered saffron, powdered ginger and crushed hot peppers or preferably cayenne pepper into the lentils and cook. In another pan, melt the butter and add the onion and mustard to the sauté and soup. Finally, add 4 more glasses of water and cook by mixing. Indian style lentil soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Atatif dessert; soften the yeast with a little warm water and sugar, let it rise for 10 minutes, mix the other ingredients and add the swelled yeast, knead the dough will be in the consistency of dark yogurt, lightly fluid, cover its mouth for at least half an hour and leaven. Brush the Teflon pan with a little oil, pour 1 tablespoon of the dough, lightly fry one side, whether the size of the spread is palm-sized or smaller. Do not fry the other side. Do not fry the other side, cook in this way until the dough is gone. Heat the cream, do not boil it, melt the starch in a little water and add it to the cream, whisk it quickly, add sugar, remove it from the stove, mix it occasionally and cool it. Put a teaspoon of quashta in each dough, squeeze one end, stick it, dip pistachios, hazelnuts, etc. and serve. Enjoy your meal.:)

For the Chickpea Ravioli recipe; Drain the chickpeas soaked the day before. Add enough water to cover two fingers and boil it. Drain the water again and fry the chopped onion in olive oil in a saucepan. Add the vegetable seasoning and salt to it and mix. Turn off the stove and cool. Put the chickpeas on a serving plate. Drizzle the yogurt over the chickpeas. Garnish with pine nuts and cumin when serving. Chickpea Ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

Curtained Uzbek Pilaf recipe; For the filling of the pilaf, melt half the butter in a saucepan and add the finely chopped onions. Fry until it turns pink. Add the meat and fry for another 5 minutes. Add diced carrots, green beans and skinless and seedless tomatoes. Roast a little more and add peanuts, pepper paste, cinnamon, saffron salt, black pepper, grapes and boiling broth. Turn off the fire. Put the remaining butter in another saucepan and add the washed and drained rice soaked in salted water for half an hour. Roast for 8-10 minutes. Add the meat paste to the rice. Boil once and infuse for 15 minutes over low heat. Empty the tray. Fold in the finely chopped parsley. Put it on hold. Meanwhile, cut 1 cm wide strips of puff pastry dough and place them in the bottom of a 8-10 cm high heat-resistant round bowl with a flat bottom. Bring the remaining puff pastry dough side by side, stick it with a rolling pin and roll it out wide. Lay the dough out on a rough, with the edges hanging out. Fill it with rice. Cover the overflowing dough over the rice by pulling it lightly. Rub the egg yolk. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 20 minutes. Take it upside down on a serving plate, slice and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Honey Lemon Mint Sorbet recipe; Remove the peel of the lemon and extract the juice. Cover the shells with granulated sugar and leave in the refrigerator overnight. Boil in a saucepan until the mint color begins to turn. Filter your water. Put the mint juice, lemon peel, lemon juice, honey, ginger and black pepper in the pot and stir until the sugar dissolves. Pass the mixture through cheesecloth and pour into a glass jug with a lid. Place the warm syrup in the refrigerator and let it cool. Garnish with mint and lemon slices, if desired, and serve cold. Enjoy your meal.

For the Balkan meatball recipe; Mix the ground beef well with salt. After resting for half an hour, add onion, black pepper and chili pepper and continue to knead for 15 minutes. After letting the minced meat rest for 1 hour, cut it into egg-sized pieces. Cut each piece in half again. Press one of the pieces you cut into two with your hand and give it the shape of a hamburger patty. Put 1 teaspoon of grated cheddar cheese and 1 teaspoon of chopped dried meat on it, cover the other piece and press it. Prepare the other meatballs in the same way. Fry both sides in hot oil, put 1 teaspoon of cream on it and serve hot. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the chicken wrap recipe, cut the chicken breasts in half. In a bowl, mix the minced garlic, dill, butter and grated cheddar cheese. Put my wife on top of thin chicken slices and wrap. Then dip them in flour, scrambled eggs and breadcrumbs respectively and bake. Serve hot. If you wish, you can decorate the plate with dill basil-style herbs. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Aleppo rice pudding; Cook the rice, milk, crushed mastic, cardamom and ginger in a saucepan until the rice is tender. Add granulated sugar, grated peel of 1 orange and rose water and continue mixing. Divide into bowls. Aleppo rice pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

Mix the flour, warm milk, yoghurt, egg white, sugar and salt in a bowl. Add yeast and mix. Form a dough that will become soft and add butter or margarine to it. Let rest for 1 hour at room temperature. Break off egg-sized balls from the dough and give them the shape you want with your hands. Place them on a baking tray and brush with beaten egg yolk. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven for 15-20 minutes. Serve warm or cold.

For the asek recipe: Rub the chopped onion with 1 teaspoon of salt. Then, prepare the stuffing by blending the chopped spinach and spring onions. Then knead flour, egg, water and 1 teaspoon of salt to form a soft dough. Break off egg-sized balls and open them in a round shape. Put a teaspoon of mortar in each and close them in a half-moon shape. Cook in boiling water for about 5 minutes. Then cook the grated tomatoes and olive oil for 10 minutes and leave to cool. Pour yoghurt and tomato sauce on the aşek. Asek is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the dough of Uzbek manti; knead the flour, eggs, water and salt into a dough. For the mortar; Mix the onion, water, salt and pepper in the blender. Take lemon-sized pieces from the rested dough and roll them thinly with the help of a rolling pin. Cut into large squares and set aside. Repeat the process until the meringue is gone. Place mortar the size of a cherry tomato in the center of each square. Glue the ends of the diagonal corners by pressing them with your hand. When the steamer's water boils, place the ravioli in a greased sieve. Steam for 20 minutes and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Uzbek Pilaf recipe; Wet the rice and set aside. Cook the meat in vegetable oil on high heat until the water is absorbed. Then cook on low heat for another 40 minutes. Add the carrots after julienne and cook for another 20 minutes. Pour the rice into the pot and open the middle. Place the meat in the center of the rice and cover it with rice. After adding salt and pepper to the hot water that is half an inch above the rice, put it on the stove and let it cook. When the rice water is absorbed, take it off the stove and let it rest for 5-10 minutes. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the dough: 250 grams of flour 1 tablespoon of yogurt 1 glass of water 1/4 teaspoon of baking powder 125 grams of butter Half a teaspoon of salt For the dough, knead the flour, yogurt, water, baking powder and salt to obtain a soft dough. Open it thin. Spread melted butter on it and roll it into a roll. Cut it two finger widths, press it with your hand so that the middle of each piece is cambered, then thin it out with a rolling pin. For the mortar, mix the ground beef, onion, water, pepper and salt in a blender. Turn the doughs upside down and put the minced meat in the middle. Shape it into a bundle and close it. Place them on a greased baking tray and brush with beaten egg yolk. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven for 20 minutes.

Chop veal or preferably lamb as cubes. Chop the onions and fry them in oil. Add the meat and fry. Add tomato, tomato paste, wheat and 5 glasses of hot water and cook for 50 minutes. In a separate bowl, boil the mung beans in little water for 20 minutes. Boil the black-eyed peas and add the mung beans and black-eyed peas when the soup is ready. Add diced potatoes, carrots and the remaining 5 glasses of hot water and cook for 10-15 minutes on low heat.

Slice the zucchini into rounds. Finely chop the onion. After frying the onions in butter until they turn pink, add the zucchini and continue sautéing. Add 1 cup of water and cook with the lid closed until the zucchini is soft. Sprinkle with salt, pepper and dill if desired. Whisk the yogurt, egg and grated lemon peel in a bowl, add to the zucchini and mix. Line a round baking tin with parchment paper. Pour and spread the mixture you prepared. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 20 minutes. When it cools down, you can garnish it with mint and serve.

for herb soup recipe; grate the tomatoes. Put the grated tomatoes, oat paste and oil in the pot. Cook, stirring slowly. Add water to it and boil it. Sprinkle the dried basil before removing the pan from the heat. herb soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the almond chicken soup recipe; Add the saffron to the vinegar and leave it overnight. Put the chicken in the pot, add water and salt and boil it. Take it out of the water and separate the meat from the bones. Shred the meat with your hands and set aside. Put the chicken broth back on the stove, add the rice and let it cook. On the other hand, put the almonds in boiling water, remove them after 5 minutes, peel them, then dry them and grind them into flour. Melt the butter and lightly toast the cracked almonds. Whisk the egg yolk with the starch in a bowl. Add lemon juice and saffron vinegar on it. Add half a soup ladle of the chicken broth on the stove and warm it up, and then add it to the pot, stirring constantly. Add the shredded chicken to the pot. Bring to a boil and remove from the stove. Let it rest for 15 minutes and serve with roasted almonds on it. Almond chicken soup is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the spicy and goat cheese chicken wrap recipe; Cut three quarters of the breast horizontally by placing parchment paper on top of the chicken breasts. Kind of like an open book. Finely chop the basil, parsley and thyme. Mash the goat cheese in a bowl with a fork. Add the seasonings and lemon juice to the cheese. Remove the wax paper from the breasts, spread the cheese mixture evenly and roll it. Curl the ends of the breasts inward to prevent the material from spilling out. Wrap the rolls you prepared in aluminum foil and pack them tightly. Fill the pot halfway with water and bring it to a boil. Put the rolls in water and cook for 15 minutes and turn off the fire. Leave them in the water so that they do not cool. Fry the diced shallots and garlic in a pan with olive oil. Grate the tomato and throw it in. Sprinkle with salt and pepper. Cut the chicken into 1 cm slices and serve with tomato sauce.

For the Apple Turkey recipe; Peel and dice the onions and apples. Fry the apples and onions in a tablespoon of oil. Add salt and pepper according to your hand setting. Remove the parsley and add it to the mince and apple mixture. Spread the apple mixture over the meat. Then fold the meat in half and fasten the edges with toothpicks. (The turkeys should be in the form of thin steaks) Heat the oil in a pan, fry the meat on both sides for 5 minutes. Cook for 5 minutes on low heat with the addition of a little hot water. Boil the peas in boiling salted water for 15 minutes and drain. On the serving plate, place the turkey meat, boiled peas garnish with salt, pepper and a little olive oil added. Garnish with finely chopped parsley and serve hot. Turkey with Apple is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the rice chicken salad recipe; Boil the chicken breast and 1 cup of rice. Boil the mushrooms in water with lemon and leave to cool. Finely chop the spring onions. Cut the chicken breast into small pieces. Put the rice, chicken breast, mushrooms and spring onions on a serving plate and mix. Add 1 teaspoon of lemon juice. Chicken Salad with Rice is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the sea cowpea salad recipe; Cut off the muddy stems of the sea cowpeas. Wash the remaining thoroughly in plenty of water. Put the boiling water in the pot and add the black-eyed peas. Boil for 10-15 minutes, until the beans are soft. Also, be careful not to overcook it. After boiling, run them under very cold water so that they both cool down and do not lose their green color. Since cowpea has hard branches in it, you need to separate these hard branches for eating. Separate the hard parts from the twigs and put the remaining edible parts in a bowl. In a separate bowl, mix the olive oil, lemon and crushed garlic, add it to the black-eyed peas and mix. Sea cowpea salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the dry bean paste recipe; Add enough water to cover the dried beans that you soaked in water overnight and boil them. After peeling the shells of the boiled beans, put them in a bowl. Blend until smooth with a hand blender. Finely chop the garlic. Spread the smoothed beans on a serving plate. Add finely chopped garlic, olive oil and salt and mix. Sprinkle paprika on the last. Dry bean paste is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the diet eggplant pastry recipe; Roast the eggplants and peel them. Spread on a baking tray. In a separate bowl, mix diet yogurt, curd cheese, salt and red pepper. Pour the mixture over the roasted eggplants. Add a small amount of water to the tray and cook in the oven until the top turns pink. Diet eggplant pastry is ready to serve. Good luck.

For the recipe of Types of Legumes; Boil beans, chickpeas, black-eyed peas and green lentils separately. Chop the onion and fry in olive oil until golden brown. Add the grated tomatoes, garlic and tomato paste and cook on high heat for a few minutes. Add boiled lentils, black-eyed peas, chickpeas and beans and cook for 2 minutes. Add salt, pepper and enough hot water to cover. Bake for 25-30 minutes and transfer to a serving plate. Serve hot or warm, garnished with parsley.

Place the apples in the pot, add water and boil until soft. When the apples are soft, mash them into a puree and divide into casserole dishes. Whisk 6 egg whites and sugar in a bowl and whisk until smooth. Spread this mixture you have prepared so that it covers the purees. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven until golden brown. Serve with cinnamon if you wish.

For the vegetable meat pasta recipe; Soak the mushrooms in water for 15 minutes. After washing the spinach in plenty of water, boil it in a saucepan. After the mushrooms have rested, finely chop the mushrooms, meat and onions, dice the peppers, beat the garlic and mix it all with soy sauce, granulated sugar, 1 teaspoon sesame oil. Add 2 tablespoons of vegetable oil to a frying pan, heat it and add the meat mixture you have prepared and cook. In a separate bowl, mix the boiled spinach with the remaining 1 teaspoon of sesame oil and salt. Boil the pasta in boiling water for 8-10 minutes and drain the pasta when it swells. Chop the carrots into rounds, add the spinach and pasta that you mixed with salt to the cooked meat and continue cooking. Add black pepper and salt to your taste. Meat pasta with vegetables is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

Beat the egg thoroughly with a blender or whisk. Add the other ingredients and mix with the mixer for 10 minutes. Rest for 20 minutes in a warm environment. Cook one ladle of the mixture you have prepared in a waffle maker or a non-stick frying pan so that both sides are browned. Serve garnished with raspberry and chocolate sauce. If desired, sprinkle some powdered sugar on top.

Chop the chicken pieces into cubes and sprinkle with ginger. In a separate bowl, blend the onion, lemongrass, paprika and garlic together in a blender. Take the oil in a deep saucepan and heat it. Add the onion mixture to it. Add the chicken and fry. Add the coconut milk and basil. In a non-stick skillet, sauté the chopped zucchini, carrot and soybean sprouts and add to the chicken mixture. Remove from the stove and serve hot.

For the English Cream Fruit Salad recipe; Add salt and vanilla to the milk and bring to a boil over medium heat. When it starts to boil, reduce the heat and boil for another 1-2 minutes. Beat the egg yolks well in a bowl. Add the powdered sugar and continue beating. Stir the hot milk little by little into the egg. In the meantime, keep whisking fast. When the milk is completely drained, put the container on the stove in another bowl of water. Cook, stirring with a wooden spoon, until it forms a thin layer on top of the spoon. Let it cool. Squeeze the juice of one of the pomegranates well. Extract the seeds of the other pomegranate. Peel and slice the oranges and bananas. Put the pomegranate seeds, orange and banana slices in a bowl. Mix the pomegranate juice, orange liqueur and lemon juice in a glass. Divide the fruits into bowls and pour the mixture you prepared on it. Add the English cream that you left to cool on it by dividing it. Refrigerate for 1 hour and chill. English cream fruit salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

Powder the hazelnuts, almonds and pistachios separately. Take the butter and granulated sugar in a bowl and beat with a mixer. Add egg yolk to it. Add salt, powdered nuts and flour and knead well. Spread the dough you prepared into the tart mold. Slice the apples thinly and add cinnamon and raisins and mix. Place it neatly on the dough and bake in a preheated 180-degree oven for 40 minutes. When ready, serve with pistachios and almonds sprinkled on or around the edges.

Take cream cheese, yoghurt and a tablespoon of granulated sugar in a bowl and mix. Puree the figs and add them to the mixture with the egg. In another bowl, whisk the egg whites and froth well. Add half a glass of granulated sugar and whisk again to form a foam. Feed the cornstarch into the foam. Add the two mixtures together and mix well. Add the lemon juice, vanilla and grated lemon peel. Pour the mixture into a lightly oiled mold. Place on a baking tray filled with hot water. Bake in a preheated 150 degree oven for 120 minutes.

Beat the egg yolks in a deep bowl. Add other ingredients and mix. For the caramel, put the sugar, butter and water in a pan. Simmer until the sugar caramelizes. When caramelizing is finished, divide into hot baking dishes. . Divide the mixture you prepared earlier into the baking dishes. Pour hot water into a deep and wide baking tray and place the molds in it. Bake in the oven at 170 degrees for 40-45 minutes. Serve chilled with slices of fruit.

Season the beef tenderloin with salt and pepper according to your taste, and then fry it in a pan. Bake for another 10-15 minutes in a preheated 180 degree oven. Saute all the vegetables in a pan. Arrange the tenderloins at intervals on the serving plate. Serve with vegetables and rice.

For the pancakes, beat the egg whites with a mixer for 3 minutes. When it becomes a white foam, add all the other ingredients and mix. Heat a medium skillet and cook the pancakes, one ladle at a time. For the sweet sauce, whisk the egg yolks and sugar well. Melt the oil in a saucepan. Slowly add the egg yolks and sugar to the oil. After adding the lemon peel and cream, mix and cook until it thickens. Put the sweet sauce inside the pancakes and seal the edges as an envelope. Garnish with raspberries and serve.

Mix the oil and chicken for a few minutes and add all the other ingredients. After two minutes, add the chicken broth and continue to boil. Stir in the cornmeal so that the juice is thick. In the meantime, prepare the boiled and lightly cooked rice. Place the rice and chicken on a serving plate and serve hot.

Take oil in a saucepan and heat it. Add the chopped 1/2 onion, garlic and meat and turn several times. Add the carrot that you cut into cubes, all the spices, salt and pepper and continue the roasting process for 2 more minutes. Then add 2 glasses of water and boil it on a slow fire until the meat is cooked. Add the chickpeas close to the cooking of the meat and mix. Serve with boiled and sautéed couscous. For Harissa sauce, puree the garlic, red pepper, olive oil and walnuts in a blender. You can serve Harissa sauce with your meals.

Finely dice the pumpkins. Mix it with 10 tablespoons of granulated sugar (you can increase the amount of sugar if it still feels tasteless) Add 1 glass of milk and 2 glasses of coconut milk on top. After boiling, add 1 teaspoon of salt and 2 tablespoons of corn kernels. Cool and serve in a bowl with ice on top.

Goulash Soup with Noodles; Chop the tomatoes, carrots and peppers into cubes. Finely chop the celery and onion and sauté them in an oiled pan. Chop the meat into cubes and add to the celery and onions. Add cumin, salt and garlic. Cook until the meat is cooked. Add half of the broth and let the meat cook halfway. Add the remaining broth, red pepper, potato and carrot and wait for it to cook. At the end of the cooking process, add the tomatoes and peppers and boil for 5 more minutes. Goulash soup with noodles is ready. Enjoy your meal.

Put the coconut milk and green curry in the saucepan. When it boils, add the chicken, sugar, salt and kaffir lime (a spice that tastes like lemon juice). In another bowl, cook the coconut milk until creamy (6-7 minutes). Pour over the chicken and serve.

Chop the onion small. Fry in a pan with oil. Add the bell pepper and broth and mix. Finely dice the tomatoes. Cut the chickens in half. Put the chicken and tomatoes in the pan. Add salt and garlic and sauté on medium heat. Meanwhile, to prepare the sauce, mix the cream and flour on low heat until it thickens. Take the chickens that you have removed the bones on the serving plate. Pour the sauce over the chicken and serve hot.

For the Eggplant Ravioli recipe; Roast the eggplant first. While the eggplant is roasting, put the flour, semolina and salt in a large bowl and mix. Add 1 beaten egg and as much water as it takes and knead. Cover the dough you kneaded with a cloth and let it rest. Meanwhile, to prepare the filling for the ravioli, chop the roasted eggplants into small pieces. Put 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a pan and sauté the onions, garlic, and chopped Italian salami in this oil, respectively. After turning off the stove, add the roasted aubergines, chili pepper and salt and mix. Roll the dough out thinly with a rolling pin. Make circles from the dough with a ravioli mold. Put the filling material into this circle dough you have removed and fold it in a semi-circle. Cook the prepared ravioli by throwing them in boiling water. For the tomato sauce; Put a tablespoon of olive oil in the pan and sauté the garlic and tomatoes respectively. Add salt, pepper and granulated sugar, add water and cook for 10 minutes. Pour this sauce over the ravioli and serve. Eggplant ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

First of all, put 1 glass of flour, 1 egg and salt in a deep bowl. Add as much water as it takes and knead well. When the dough is ready, cover it and let it rest. To prepare the stuffing, put vegetable oil in a pan and sauté the onions in this oil. Add the garlic powder, chopped carrots, rosemary, basil, thyme. On the boiled beef, add this mixture and the peas, grated mozzarella cheese and mix. Place the dough that you kneaded beforehand so that it covers the bottom and sides of a baking dish. Put the stuffing inside the dough. Cover with the remaining dough. Bake in the preheated oven for 35 minutes. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the oven spaghetti recipe; Boil in a pot with 5 glasses of water and salt and 1 tablespoon of olive oil in it. When the water boils, drop the spaghetti into the water and boil them until they are slightly soft. Finely chop the onions. Crush the garlic. Chop the peppers and tomatoes as well. Put the remaining olive oil in a separate pan and sauté the onions, minced meat, garlic, peppers and tomatoes in this oil respectively. Add salt, pepper, chili pepper, parsley leaves, granulated sugar and bay leaf to the sautéed ingredients and mix. When the pasta is cooked, drain and spread in a baking dish. Pour the sauce you prepared on it. Sprinkle the last grated cheddar cheese on it. Bake in the preheated oven for 20-25 minutes. Spaghetti in the oven is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

Finely chop the green hot peppers and crush the garlic. Finely chop the lamb and mix it with ginger, garlic and green hot peppers. Add cumin, salt, egg, garam masala and fresh coriander and knead. Squeeze the mixture you prepared into the skewers by squeezing it with your palm. Cook on the barbecue. Chop the onions into rings and lay them out on the serving plate. Place the cooked meat on the onions and serve.

For the recipe for vegetables in the oven; Wash the eggplants, tomatoes, peppers, zucchini and potatoes with plenty of water. Cut the eggplants into strips, clean the zucchini from the outside and cut into rings, peel the potatoes and cut the peppers and tomatoes into 4 pieces. Add spices and oil, mix, pour on a baking tray, spread on oiled paper and bake in the oven at 180 C. Baked vegetables are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the pan mushroom recipe; Separate the mushrooms from their stems and wash them. Put the oil in a wide pan and arrange the mushrooms with the hollows facing up. Throw the stems on the sides, sprinkle with salt and cook on half fire until the mushrooms are cooked, with the lid of the pan closed. Mushrooms in the Pan is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Milky Zucchini recipe; peel and slice the zucchini. Put some water on it and bring it to a boil and when it is cooked, strain it and add the sugar and milk. Mash it well with a blender and puree it. Then boil for 2 more minutes on the stove and remove from the stove. Milky Zucchini is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For Pea Mushroom Buckwheat Salad, mix honey and vinegar in a small bowl and set aside. Boil 1 glass of water in a saucepan and leave the mushrooms in the boiling water for 20 minutes. Then drain the mushrooms and keep the boiling water aside, then finely chop the mushrooms and soak them in lemon water. (Lemon will prevent the mushrooms from darkening.) Boil 8 glasses of water in another pot, add the fresh peas and boil for 6-7 minutes. Drain the peas after boiling. Meanwhile, boil 2 cups of water, add the buckwheat and cook for 5 minutes, stirring constantly. After boiling, drain the buckwheat and put it in a salad bowl. For the buckwheat vinaigrette, pour the boiling water of the mushrooms into a small saucepan. Boil for 5 minutes on medium heat. Take the saucepan off the heat, transfer the water in it to a bowl and add the lemon juice, vinegar, shallots, salt and pepper, and olive oil and mix well. Then transfer the peas and mushrooms to the bowl with the buckwheat and pour the sauce on top. Mix the salad well and serve immediately. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach pasta recipe; Dice the bell peppers and sauté them in olive oil in a pan. After sautéing for a few minutes, wash the spinach in plenty of water, chop it finely and add it to the pan with the broth. Then add black pepper and let it cook. Cook the pasta in water to which you add salt for 10 minutes until it remains slightly fresh and drain. Then add it to the sauce you prepared and mix it a few times. Finally, add walnuts and parmesan cheese and mix a few more times. Spinach Whole Wheat Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Yufkali Rice recipe; Put the pan on the fire and add oil, when the oil is hot, add the chopped onions to the pan and saute. When the onions soften, add the almonds and continue sautéing, then add the grated carrot and mix. When the color of the carrots starts to turn yellow, put the thinly sliced mushrooms in the pan and mix. When the mushrooms soften, add the rice, mix it for a while, add the allspice and continue sautéing. Finally, add the water, salt and pepper and close the lid. While it is a little moist, remove the rice from the fire and wait for it to cool. Add oil to another pan and place a sheet of phyllo in the center of the pan, Spread the rice inside and cover the dough. Bake in the oven until colored. Enjoy your meal.

For the cacao dry bean dessert recipe; Wash and boil the dried beans. Put it in a blender and puree it. Add crushed walnuts and 1 glass of Splenda and mix. Add vanilla and orange zest to the bean mixture. Lightly oil a rectangular glass baking dish and pour this mixture. Bake in a preheated oven at 170 degrees for 25-30 minutes. To prepare the cocoa sauce, add the egg, flour and cocoa to the cold water and whisk well. Stir and cook on high heat. Take it from the fire. While the sauce is hot, add the margarine and the sweetener (Aspartame) that you crushed in the mortar and mix well. When the dried bean dessert has cooled, pour the cocoa sauce you prepared on it. Rest for 2 hours in the refrigerator. Cut into 16 equal pieces and serve. Dry bean dessert with cocoa is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Rolled Kadayif with Walnut; As a preliminary preparation, lay the phyllo sheets on the counter. Cut the phyllo dough into a square shape by cutting the rounded edges straight (this way you separate half of the phyllo). Pour three tablespoons of melted margarine into each of the square-shaped phyllo and spread with your hands. Place the wire kadayıf in pieces on the oiled phyllo and pour the crushed walnuts on it. Roll the kadayif phyllo tightly starting from one edge. Cut each roll you make into 15 equal slices, each two inches thick (30 pieces in total). Arrange each piece that comes into the shape of a wheel on a lightly oiled tray, uninterruptedly. Bake in a 230 degree oven until golden brown. When you are going to eat, pour the syrup (by boiling the sweetener and water) that you prepared for 1 portion (2 pieces) over your kadaifs. It will be used for the water and splenda sherbet in the recipe. Enjoy your meal.

For the sweetened rice pudding recipe; After sorting and washing the rice, boil it in a little water until it becomes soft. Put milk in a pot and boil it. While the milk is boiling, crush the starch with water in a bowl, add the salt and mix. Slowly add the mashed starch to the boiling milk by mixing it. Add the boiled rice and continue to cook, stirring. When the rice pudding comes to a thick consistency, remove the rice pudding from the fire, add it while it is warm and mix it well. Pour evenly into bowls and leave to cool in a cool place. After it cools down, garnish with cinnamon and serve. Sweetened rice pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Sweetened Walnut Güllaç recipe; Boil the milk in a saucepan. Take it off the fire. Add sweetener and mix well. Let it cool. Pour the warm milk into a large tray. Lay the Güllaç leaves one by one on the tray. Take the Güllaç leaves from the tray before they get soft. Divide it into two equal parts. Fold one of the leaves you cut in half in half. After putting some walnuts in the middle, wrap it in the form of a bundle. Arrange the bundle-shaped Güllaç leaves side by side on the serving plate with the folded side down. Pour rose water and remaining milk on the Güllaç and let them absorb well. Serve after 30 minutes. Diabetics! You can eat this special dessert of Ramadan days by making it according to this recipe. Enjoy your meal.

For the sweetened crepe cake recipe; Put 1 glass of low-fat milk, eggs, flour and baking soda in a deep bowl and whisk. Heat a Teflon pan (20-25 cm in diameter), add 1 tablespoon of oil, and spread the mixture on the pan so that you get 6 pancakes from the mixture. Cook back and forth until the crepes are eye-catching. Cook 6 crepes in the same way. For the cream, mix 1 glass of low-fat milk and flour in a separate pot and cook until it reaches the consistency of pudding. Take it off the stove, add the margarine while the mixture is hot and mix well. Add the sweetener and mix again. Put one of the pancakes on a flat, round plate that you will serve, and spread 2 tablespoons of the sweetened cream you have prepared on it. Prepare 3 crepes on top of each other in the same way. Arrange the thinly cut kiwi and strawberries on the 3rd crepe. After preparing the other three in the same way, pour all the remaining cream on the top. Garnish with kiwi and strawberries. Crepe cake with sweetener is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

sautéed meat; Chop the onions for cooking, put the chopped garlic and the mutton cubed together in the pot and saute a little. Remove the stems and seeds and chop the peppers, put them in the pot, add the tomato paste and continue cooking. Cook for 45-50 minutes on low heat with its own juice. Finally, add the peeled and diced tomatoes and cook a little more. When the meat is tender, add the finely chopped parsley, salt and pepper and mix. Remove the saute from the heat, serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the eggplant recipe; Put the oil in the pan and fry the chopped onions and peppers on it. After the onions and peppers are roasted, add the diced tomatoes and continue frying. Cook by adding the eggplants you cut into cubes last. Eggplant dish is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled meatball recipe: grate the onion, finely chop the parsley. Put the parsley, onion, minced meat, bread crumbs, salt, spices in a deep bowl and knead. Make 24 flat meatballs from the meatball dough. Cook the meatballs on the grill or in a Teflon pan. When the meatballs are cooked on both sides, distribute them on the plates. Grilled meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for seasoned meatballs with parsley: put the ground beef, rice, salt and pepper in a bowl. Crack 1 egg on it and knead by mixing. Break off walnut-sized pieces from the meatball dough and roll it into flour and form into meatballs. On the other hand, put water in a pot and boil it. Add the meatballs to the boiling water and continue cooking on low heat until the rice is cooked. Put the other egg in a bowl and squeeze the lemon juice on it and whisk it well. Pour the dressing over the meatballs and mix. After another 1-2 minutes of boiling, remove from the stove. Garnish with chopped parsley, sprinkle with paprika and serve hot. Seasoned meatballs with parsley are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of juicy meatballs with egg; Mix the ground beef, 2 eggs, rice, salt and pepper and knead. Break off walnut-sized pieces from the meatball dough and roll it into flour and form into meatballs. On the other side, put the oil and grated onions in a pan and fry the onions until they turn pink, add the tomato paste. Put water on it and boil it. Add the meatballs to the boiling water with tomato paste and continue cooking on low heat until the rice is cooked. Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot. Juicy meatballs with egg are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for meatballs with vegetables: put the ground beef, egg, rice, salt, pepper and grated onion in a bowl and knead by mixing. Make round meatballs by breaking off walnut-sized pieces from the meatball dough. On the other hand, wash the potatoes and carrots and cut them into cubes. Put the oil and grated tomatoes in a saucepan and cook. Put water on it. When the water boils, add the meatballs, peas, potatoes and carrots. Continue cooking on low heat until the vegetables are cooked. Meatballs with vegetables are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Izmir meatball recipe: put the minced meat, egg, bread crumbs, salt, pepper and grated onion in a bowl and mix and knead. Prepare 24 long meatballs from the meatball dough. On the other side, put the oil and tomato paste in a shallow pan and cook. Put water on it. When the water boils, kneel the meatballs. Place round cut tomatoes and peppers cut into two or three pieces on the meatballs. Close the lid of the pot. Cook on low heat. When the meatballs are cooked, distribute them on the plates. Izmir meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the green lentil chicken recipe; Boil the chicken breasts and cut into thin long strips. In a separate pot, put the chopped onions and oil and fry a little. Add chicken broth, salt, pepper, mint and lentils and cook for 1 hour until the lentils are soft. Mix the cooked lentils and the chicken you cut into a heatproof glass bowl. On the other side, in another bowl, mash the milk and flour and cook on low heat until it reaches the consistency of pudding. Add margarine and salt and mix well. If the sauce is thick, you can adjust the consistency by adding chicken broth. Pour the sauce over the lentil chickens and bake in the oven set at 200 degrees for 30 minutes. Green Lentil Chicken is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken casserole recipe; Add the oil to your casserole, the diced chicken meat and chopped onions and cook until the color of the meat changes. Add the washed, peeled and diced carrots and potatoes, peeled and diced tomatoes, canned peas, salt, thyme and hot water, respectively. Let it boil over medium heat. Bake for 20-25 minutes. Cook your casserole in a preheated oven at 200 degrees for 1 more hour with its lid closed and serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mushroom Chicken Salad recipe; Boil the chicken, remove the bones and skin and cut into small pieces. After washing and cutting the mushrooms, boil them in the chicken's water for 3-5 minutes. Wash and scrape the carrot, grate it on the coarse side of the grater. Chop the onions for cooking, wash and chop the peppers and mix them all together with the carrots and put them in a deep salad plate. Add the mushrooms, chopped chicken meat and mix. Finally, add the peeled and diced tomatoes. Add the finely chopped parsley, salt, olive oil and lemon juice to the salad and mix. Serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the ground beans recipe; Chop the onions for cooking, chop the garlic finely, put them in the pressure cooker with salt, sugar, tomato paste and oil and fry the onions. Add the minced meat. Continue cooking until the ground beef turns colour. After adding the tomato paste and 1.5 cups of water, add the pre-soaked dried beans and cook for half an hour in the pressure cooker. Serve hot. Red beans with minced meat are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the green lentil recipe with minced meat; Chop the onion with food and put the onions, oil, salt in a pot and fry the onions a little. When the onions turn pink, add the minced meat. Continue cooking until the ground beef turns colour. After adding the tomato paste and 2 glasses of water, pass the lentils in water, drain them well and add them to the pot. Cook on low heat until the lentils are soft. Serve hot. Green lentils with minced meat are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Green Lentil Soup with Barley Noodles; Put the grated onion, oil and tomato paste in the pot and cook for a while. Put water, salt and the lentils you have cleaned and washed on it. Cook thoroughly for 30 minutes. Add the noodles and continue cooking. Crush the flour in cold water and add it to the soup being cooked. Add the mint. After boiling for a few more minutes, take it off the stove. If you wish, you can use vinegar during the service. Serve hot. Green lentil soup with barley noodle is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Ezogelin soup recipe; Put the water and the lentils and bulgur that you have cleaned and washed in the pot. Let it boil. Add the grated onion and salt to the pot and cook for 40 minutes. Melt the butter in a Teflon pan, add the flour and fry until it turns slightly yellow, add tomato paste, mint and red pepper, add the hot soup and mash. Add the tomato paste mixture to the soup. Cook stirring until it boils. Serve hot with lemon juice. Enjoy your meal.

For the Minced Chickpea recipe; Cook a little by adding oil and chopped onion, salt and sugar to the pressure cooker. Add the minced meat. Continue cooking until the ground beef turns colour. After adding the tomato paste and 1.5 cups of water, add the pre-soaked chickpeas and cook in the pressure cooker for half an hour. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chicken Chickpea recipe; Put the oil and chopped onion, salt and sugar in the pressure cooker and cook a little. Add the diced chicken meat. Continue cooking until the chicken meat turns colour. After adding the tomato paste and 1 glass of water, add the pre-soaked chickpeas and cook in the pressure cooker for half an hour. Serve hot. Bon appetit.

For the bean soup recipe; Boil the whole broad beans in a bain-marie in a pressure cooker. Put the grated onion and oil in the pot and sauté a little. Put the water in which you boiled the broad beans on the onions. Chop the beans into small pieces. Add the pods and salt to the onion water. Boil. On the other side, put the cold water and flour you prepared for finishing in a deep bowl. Beat well. Put the dressing in the boiling soup and bring it to a boil. Serve hot.

For the okra soup recipe; wash the okra. In a saucepan, turn the oil a little by mixing the chopped onion. First, add the grated or peeled and diced tomatoes, water and lemon juice. After the water boils, add the salt and okra and cook on low heat for 20-25 minutes until the okra is soft. Add the black pepper and mix. Serve hot. Okra soup is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken pea recipe; Add the oil and chopped onion and chicken meat to the pan and sauté until the chicken changes color. After adding the tomato paste, add 1 glass of water, salt and the peeled and washed peas and cook for 15 minutes in a pressure cooker. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for stuffed peppers with soy mince; Boil the soy mince. While the ground beef is boiling, wash the peppers. Cut off your stems. Cut the top of the peppers so that the lid does not break completely. Clean the insides. To prepare the inside; Grate the tomatoes and onions, wash and chop the parsley. Strain the boiled soy mince and put it in a deep bowl. Add the rice, 2 tablespoons of oil, salt, grated tomato and onion mixture on it and mix well. Stuff these stuffed bell peppers. Knee in the pot. Add water and cook on low heat until the rice is cooked. Serve hot. Stuffed peppers with soy mince is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Stuffed Red Peppers with Bulgur recipe; Cut off the seeds of the red peppers. Place the peppers on the baking tray. After 10 minutes of baking, peel the skins off. On the other hand, put bulgur in a bowl and add hot water to it. Let the bulgur swell by closing the lid. After it cools down a bit, mix the mashed feta cheese and boiled potatoes, chopped parsley, salt and pepper into the bulgur and mix. Fill the stuffing you have prepared with red peppers, keep it in the refrigerator for a while and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Egg Red Pepper recipe; Wash the red peppers and remove the seeds. Place the peppers on the baking tray and cook for 20 minutes. Peel and chop the bell peppers out of the oven. Put the oil in the Teflon pan. Saute the chopped peppers in a little oil. After adding the salt, break the eggs on it. Mix. When the eggs are cooked, place them on a serving plate. Serve with yoghurt on top. Paprika with egg is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the potato broccoli gratin recipe; Wash and sort the broccoli, separate the florets and chop the stems. Cut the carrots and potatoes into thin rounds and boil them in salted water for 5 minutes. Drain the vegetables, separate the water in which you boiled the vegetables. Add flour to cold milk and whisk until smooth. Cook the milk, stirring until it reaches the consistency of custard. While the sauce is hot, add the margarine and continue mixing until the butter melts. Add the water in which you boiled the vegetables, half of the grated cheddar cheese, salt and pepper to the sauce and mix. Spread it on the vegetables that you previously lightly boiled and placed in a rectangular glass baking dish. Sprinkle the remaining cheddar cheese on the sauce and bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees for 30-40 minutes, until the top is golden brown. Cut it into 8 equal parts. Serve hot. NOTE: The cheddar will be added in a grated form. Enjoy your meal.

For the Broccoli Pasta Recipe; Wash and clean the broccoli, separate the flower parts, chop the stems and boil them in 1 glass of salted water for 5 minutes. Strain and separate the water. Sort, wash, cut the spring onions. Turn with oil. Add the flour and fry some more. Add the vegetable broth and milk and bring to a boil, stirring. Remove from heat when sauce thickens. Add salt and pepper to the sauce and mix. Add the previously boiled broccoli to the sauce. Boil the pasta in salted water by draining the water.
