Mix the boiled pasta with the sauce in the serving bowl. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the artichoke salad recipe; After cleaning the artichokes and boiling them in lemon water, drain the water and chop them into small pieces and put them in a deep bowl. Finely chop the mushrooms and dill. Add boiled corn, peas, chopped mushrooms, olives, dill and salt and mix well. Beat the yogurt and mayonnaise in a separate bowl with a fork. Pour this sauce you prepared on the artichoke mixture and mix. Remove to serving plate. Artichoke Salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the yoghurt carrot recipe; wash and scrape the carrots clean. Then grate it coarsely. Put the oil in the pan and heat it. Add carrots and salt and cook by mixing. Continue cooking until the water has evaporated. When the carrots lose their vitality, let them cool. Meanwhile, mix the yoghurt and finely chopped garlic in a bowl. Pour the yogurt mixture over the cooled carrots and mix. Carrot with yogurt is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach omelet recipe; Wash and finely chop the spinach. Grate the onion, put it in a saucepan. Fry a little with 1 tablespoon of oil. Add the spinach with salt and pepper and cook until the spinach is absorbed. On the other side, beat the eggs well, add a little salt. Put some oil in a Teflon pan and heat it. Cook your omelet by pouring a quarter of the beaten eggs into the pan. Make 4 omelets by cooking the rest of the eggs in the same way. Put the spinach you prepared in the middle of the omelet and wrap it in a roll. Garnish with parsley leaves and serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the potato spinach salad recipe; boil and peel the potatoes. Wash the spinach leaves in plenty of water and pass them through the blender. Mash the boiled potatoes with a fork, add to the spinach with the orange juice and mix. In a separate bowl, beat the salt, pepper, mayonnaise, yogurt and garlic and mix. Then add it to the spinach and potato mixture. Potato Spinach Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Zucchini Liked Chicken Saute recipe; Chop the chicken breast into cubes. Put the oil, finely chopped onions, peppers, chicken, salt and pepper in the pan, sauté on low heat. Add the diced tomatoes to the chicken and cook. Finely grate the peeled zucchini, put them in a Teflon pan with oil and enough salt. Cook the zucchini until they release their water. In another pan, heat the butter, add the flour and fry until it turns pink. Add the milk, cheese and zucchini on top and cook, stirring constantly, until thickened. Take your favorite on a serving plate and spread the chicken sauté you prepared on it. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for celery salad with mustard sauce; Peel the celery, cut it into half moons and boil it in a bain-marie. Finely chop the celery leaves. Grate the carrots. Mix the celery leaves with the grated carrot. Arrange the boiled celery on the plate. Pour the carrot mixture over the celery. Mix the lemon juice, salt, oil and mustard in a bowl and pour over the carrots. Celery salad with mustard sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Cabbage Wrap with Olive Oil; Finely chop the onions or grate them with the coarse side of the grater. Put the oil, onions, salt, pepper and cinnamon in the pot. Throw in the peanuts, fry a little. Add the washed and stems removed currants. Add 1/2 glass of water and the rice you have cleaned and washed, and cook on low heat until the rice absorbs the water. Close the lid of the pot and let it brew a little. On the other hand, separate the leaves of the cabbage and boil it. Put 1 teaspoonful of the inside of the cabbage leaves you have prepared, wrap them and place them in the pot. Add the remaining 1/2 cup of water and cook on low heat until the rice is cooked. Take the wraps on a serving plate. Serve cold. Use the parts of the cabbage that you can't wrap to make kapuska. Enjoy your meal.

For the corn soup recipe; peel the skins off the potatoes. Scrape the carrots. Grate with the coarse side of the grater. Put the water, salt and grated carrots and potatoes in the pot and cook until they are soft. Add the milk and pepper. Add the corns. After cooking the soup for 2-3 minutes, turn off the stove. Beat the egg yolk and add it to the hot soup. Add the soft butter to the hot soup and mix well until the butter melts. Serve the soup hot. You can chop the carrots and potatoes coarsely, boil them and then pass them through the blender. Corn soup is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the eggplant chicken burger recipe; Put the eggplants, which you have peeled and cut into round slices, in salted water. On the other side, cook the chicken breast and eggplant on both sides in a skillet without oil. Grease your baking dish with 1 tablespoon of oil. First place the eggplants, the chicken breasts on top, and the tomatoes cut into round slices, peeled off the skin. Pour the tomato paste juice that you prepared with 1/2 tablespoon of tomato paste over the eggplant burgers and bake in the preheated oven for 15-20 minutes. Before taking them out of the oven, sprinkle the cheddar cheese on the tomatoes and put them back in the oven. When the cheese is melted, take it out of the oven and serve hot. Eggplant chicken burger is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Eggplant Salad with Soda (Eggplant Paste); After washing the eggplants, peel them completely, leave them whole in salted water. Cut the peeled eggplants in half lengthwise in the middle and place them in a pot. On the other side, sauté finely chopped peppers, grated tomatoes, finely chopped garlic with salt in a pan with vegetable oil. Pour this mixture and 1 bottle of soda over the eggplants. Cook on low heat. Garnish with parsley and serve cold. Enjoy your meal.

For the eggplant salad recipe with sauce; After washing the eggplants, cut into finger-thick rings and bake in the oven. On the other side, sauté finely chopped peppers and grated tomatoes in a pan with vegetable oil. Add salt and pepper and pour over the eggplants. Garnish with parsley and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the fresh bean salad recipe; Wash the green beans. Boil in a pressure cooker for 5 minutes in a bain-marie. Cut the boiled beans in half lengthwise. On the other hand, cut the eggplants into cubes and boil the peppers in a little water. Put all the vegetables on the serving plate and mix. Mince the garlic. Mix the garlic with salt and olive oil in a bowl. Pour the sauce you prepared over the vegetable mixture. Finely chop the dill and mix it with yogurt. Finally, pour the yogurt mixture into the salad and mix well. Fresh bean salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the seasoned fresh bean soup recipe; Boil the green beans as a whole in a pressure cooker in 6 glasses of water in a bain-marie. Put the water and salt in which the beans were boiled in the pot. Chop the beans into small pieces. Grate the carrots, put them in the pot, cook. On the other side, put half a glass of cold water and flour, egg yolk and lemon juice that you prepared for finishing in a deep bowl. Beat well. Put the dressing in the boiling soup and bring it to a boil. Serve hot. The seasoned green bean roast is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for purslane with minced meat; Wash and sort the purslane. Chop food. Put the oil, chopped onion and minced meat in the pan and cook until the minced meat turns colour. Add the diced tomatoes, put the purslane on it with salt and cook. Add the amount of water (1/2 ÇB) and rice that the rice will absorb and keep on low heat until the rice is cooked. Serve hot with garlic yogurt. Enjoy your meal.

For the purslane soup recipe; Wash and chop the purslane. Cook some oil, salt and chopped onions together in a saucepan. Add the purslane. After the purslane is cooked, puree it in a blender. Add the hot water to the purslane puree. Let it boil. On the other hand, mash the cold milk and flour. Slowly add the milk flour into the purslane soup, stir and boil for another 10 minutes. Take it off the fire. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Menemen recipe; wash the vegetables. Peel and wash the onion, Chop the onions for edibles. Separate the stems and seeds of the peppers and chop finely. Add oil and chopped onions, peppers and salt to the pan and cook a little. Wash and grate the tomatoes. Add the tomatoes to the onion-pepper mixture. Continue cooking until the vegetables are cooked. Wash and finely chop the parsley. Add to cooked vegetables and mix. Crack the eggs over the cooked vegetables and mix. Continue cooking on low heat. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Potato Meatballs with Bulgur recipe; Put the bulgur in the pot, add water until it is 1 finger above the top, close the lid and let it brew on low heat until the water is gone. Boil and mash the potatoes. Cook the chopped onion in vegetable oil with tomato paste. Mix the brewed bulgur and mashed potatoes after they have cooled, and add the cooked onion with tomato paste. Add finely chopped fresh onion, parsley, sumac, red pepper flakes, salt, lemon juice and mix well. Give it the shape of a meatball, put it on a serving plate lined up with curls, and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Garlic Bulgur Meatballs recipe; Put the bulgur in a deep bowl with salt. Add hot water and let it steep for 10 minutes. Add the egg and knead well. Add flour to the mixture and continue kneading. Break off hazelnut-sized pieces from the mixture and roll them. Boil the meatballs you prepared by throwing them in boiling water. For the sauce on the other side, put the oil, tomato zest and crushed garlic in a saucepan and cook. Add the tomato paste, red pepper, cumin, black pepper and salt to the tomato and cook the meatballs together with the boiling water for 4-5 minutes. Serve hot with parsley and lemon. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mushroom Chicken Pasta recipe; Put the water in the pot and boil it. Throw salt and pasta into water, mix. Cook with the lid of the pot open by draining the water. On the other side, put the oil, edible chopped or grated onions, cut mushrooms in a pan and cook a little until the mushrooms release their juices. Finally, add the boiled and cut into small pieces of chicken to the pan and cook for a couple of minutes. Divide the pasta on 6 plates, pour the chicken sauce you prepared on it and serve it hot. Enjoy your meal.

For tuna pasta recipe; Put the water in the pot, bring it to a boil. Throw salt and pasta into water, mix. Cook with the lid of the pot open by draining the water. On the other side, put oil, edible chopped or grated onions, finely cut peppers and grated tomatoes in a pan and cook. Lastly, add the sliced tuna fish to the pan and cook for a moment or two. Divide the pasta on 6 plates, pour the tuna-vegetable sauce on it and serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Simple Pasta recipe; Put the water in the pot, bring it to a boil. Throw salt and pasta into water, mix. Cook with the lid of the pot open by draining the water. When the pasta is cooked, add the oil and mix. Serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Meat Rice recipe; Put the oil in the pan. The stove is near. Add the oil and the chopped onions and turn it a little. Add the cubed meat to the onions and continue cooking in the meat's own juice over low heat until the meat is tender. Add water and salt to the cooked meat and let it boil. On the other side, sort the rice, wash it. When the water boils, discard the rice, mix the meats with the rice. Turn the stove down. Turn off the stove when your pilaf is eye-catching. Infuse your rice for 15 minutes. Mix and serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Meyhane Pilaf recipe with Minced Meat; Put the oil in the pan. The stove is near. Add the oil and the chopped onions and turn it a little. Add the finely cut peppers to the onions and cook some more. Add the minced meat to the onions and continue cooking, stirring with a spoon until the minced meat turns colour. Add the peeled and diced tomatoes and cook some more. Put the water and salt, let it boil. On the other side, sort the rice, wash it. When the water boils, discard the rice, mix the minced vegetables with the rice. Turn the stove down. Turn off the stove when your pilaf is eye-catching. Infuse your rice for 15 minutes. Mix and serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Dill Mint Rice recipe; Put the oil in the pan. The stove is near. Add the oil and the chopped onions and turn it a little. Add the boiled and chopped carrots to the onions and cook a little more. Put the water and salt, let it boil. On the other side, sort the rice, wash it. When the water boils, discard the rice, mix the vegetables with the rice. Turn the stove down. Add the finely chopped dill and mint and mix. Turn off the stove when your pilaf is eye-catching. Infuse your rice for 15 minutes. Mix and serve hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled pumpkin pie recipe; Mix the flour, water and salt into a dough in a deep bowl. Make 10 meringues from the dough and roll each one in 20 cm diameter. On the other hand, to prepare the stuffing, grate the zucchini, grate the peeled onions and add to the minced meat. Add water, salt and pepper to it and mix well with a spoon. Put 1 tablespoon of the inside that you have prepared to correspond to half of the dough you have rolled out and fold it in a D shape. Cut it with a dough roller or press it with your fingers to make it stick. Cook the pastries you have prepared by pouring oil in a Teflon pan and turning them upside down (or you can cook the pastries on both sides after heating them in the toaster and lubricating them with a little soft butter). Serve the pastries hot with ayran. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach pie recipe; Wash the spinach in plenty of water and boil it in a deep pot. Chop the onions and fry them in oil. Add the tomato paste, salt and spices. Add the boiled and drained spinach, mix a little and take it off the stove. Cut a phyllo dough in half, spread a piece of it on the counter and apply oil on it with a brush. Place the spinach mixture you prepared randomly on the phyllo dough. Start at the long edge and roll it up. Place the rolled roll on the greased baking tray, starting from the middle and wrapping it around. Crack the eggs in a bowl and when all the phyllo is done, brush scrambled eggs on the pastry and put it in the oven. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven until golden brown. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetable bun recipe; Put the egg, oil, water, yoghurt, flour, baking soda, salt and pepper into a deep bowl and whisk. Peel the skins of the potatoes and tomatoes. Chop the potatoes and tomatoes into cubes, the onions for food, and the peppers finely. Slice the sausages into thin rounds. Add diced potatoes and tomatoes, diced onions, finely chopped peppers and thinly sliced sausages to the flour mixture and mix well. Pour into a greased square tray, add sesame seeds and chili peppers and bake in a 200-degree oven until golden brown. Divide into 9 equal parts. Vegetable bun is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian baked potato recipe; Cut the potatoes into apple slices. Put olive oil, paprika, salt and thyme in a bowl and mix. Put the potatoes you cut into apple slices in this bowl and find it thoroughly. Place aluminum foil on the baking sheet and then lay the potatoes on the foil. Bake in a preheated oven at 180-200 degrees for 20 minutes until golden brown. Vegetarian Baked Potatoes are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

In order to roast beef, the meat must first be rested for a day. First, we add tallow to the pan and prefer the fatty parts of our meat to make it delicious and tender. Then we take the beef into the pan and put the whole onion in the same way. First of all, we cook it on high fire so that the meat does not leave its juice. If we roast it on low heat, the meat will leave its juice and it will be hard. Then we cook it on low heat. After our meat is roasted a little, we add 1 glass of water into it. Veal takes longer to cook. We add salt and spices to the roast beef at the last stage. Roast beef is ready to serve, enjoy your meal :)

For the cheddar tomato soup recipe; Peel and grate the tomatoes, fry the margarine and flour on low heat, add 1-2 tablespoons of tomato paste if you want. Add the grated tomatoes to the flour you roasted and cook for 2-3 minutes on medium heat by stirring. Add 1 glass of milk and 4 glasses of water to the tomatoes. Stir until the soup boils. After the soup boils, cook for another 7-8 minutes and turn off the stove. Add grated cheddar cheese on it while serving, tomato soup with cheddar is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the shepherd's roast recipe; First of all, put the cubed meat in the pot and let it cook on low heat until it releases its water and shrinks slightly. Add the oil and onion and continue sautéing. Peel the tomatoes and chop finely. Chop the peppers into thin rings. First add the garlic and pepper and fry them together with the meat. Add salt and seasoning and mix. Add the chopped tomatoes, close the lid and let it cook on low heat for 20 minutes. Shepherd's Roast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for meatballs with vegetables in the oven; First of all, peel the eggplants and cut them into round slices. Sprinkle plenty of salt on it, add enough water to cover it completely and leave it in salted water for half an hour. Then wash and strain. Peel the potatoes and cut them into edible cubes. Put the potatoes in a deep bowl. Sprinkle some salt and 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil on it and mix until all sides of the potatoes are covered with oil. Lay the baking paper on the baking tray and spread the oiled potatoes on the baking paper. Take the eggplants in a deep bowl in the same way and pour 1 tablespoon of oil on them and make sure that they are smeared all over. Sprinkle the oiled eggplants on the baking paper. Bake the vegetables in the oven heated to 200 degrees for 20-25 minutes. Mix all the meatball ingredients and knead. After resting in the refrigerator for half an hour, make round meatballs. Place them on a baking tray lined with baking paper and bake at 200 degrees for 25 minutes. Peel the tomatoes and cut them into cubes. Cut the shallot into four. Cut the chili peppers into several pieces. Chop the garlic finely. Put 1 teaspoon of salt, garlic, tomatoes, peppers and 1 tablespoon of oil in a pan and sauté for 5 minutes. Add 1.5 cups of hot water to it. Take the cooked potatoes, aubergines and meatballs into my debt, and pour the diluted tomato sauce on it. Bake in the oven for another 15-20 minutes and remove. Meatballs with vegetables in the oven are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian green beans recipe; First, cut the beans in half. Finely dice the tomatoes and onions. Add the beans, tomatoes, onions, olive oil, sugar, salt, and 1 cup of water to a saucepan and cook until the beans are tender. Turn off the heat when the beans are cooked. Vegetarian green beans are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetable couscous, let's first cut our vegetables in julienne form. Then sauté in a pan with five tablespoons of olive oil. In a different pot, fry the couscous for 3 minutes with four tablespoons of olive oil. Add 3 cups of water and cook until the couscous is soft. After cooking, add 1 teaspoon of black pepper and cumin, a teaspoon of cinnamon, a teaspoon of turmeric and enough salt, and add the vegetables together with them and mix. Couscous with vegetables is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the mint yoghurt soup, first whisk the egg, yoghurt and milk. Slowly add a spoonful of flour in the pot and mix it by whisking so that it does not form lumps. Keep stirring until it boils. Add a handful of mint close to cooking. While serving, you can add butter according to your preference. Yogurt soup with mint is ready to serve, enjoy your meal :)

For the barley noodle soup recipe; Put the oil in the pan first. Add the tomato paste and continue frying. Add water to it and boil it. When the water boils, add the barley vermicelli and reduce the heat and continue boiling until the vermicelli are large and soft. Add the chopped parsley, salt and pepper until it is cooked and turn it off. Barley noodle soup is ready to serve, bon appetit :)

For the recipe for Green Lentil Soup with Noodles; First of all, boil the green lentils for 5 minutes and strain the water. Put olive oil in a pan, put the chopped onions and fry them until they turn pink. Then add the tomato paste and turn it a little, then add the broth. Add the lentils you have boiled in boiling water for 5 minutes and then the noodles. Adjust salt and seasoning to taste and cook until noodles are tender. Green lentil soup with noodles is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Chickpea Rice recipe; soak the rice in salted boiling water for half an hour beforehand. Strain the water, wash it in plenty of water until it becomes clear and let it drain. Heat the butter in a wide, thick-bottomed rice cooker. Throw in a pinch of salt along with the drained rice. Cook over low heat, stirring with a wooden spoon, until the rice grains become transparent. Pour the hot water over the rice. Adjust your salt. Add the boiled chickpeas and mix lightly. Bring to a boil over medium heat. Turn the fire down now. Close the lid of the pot. Take the rice water from the fire when it is teary-eyed. Open the lid slightly and let it brew for 15-20 minutes. Stir carefully from the outside in with a wooden spoon. Chickpea Rice is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Basil Bead Pasta recipe; First of all, put the cubed tomatoes, olive oil, garlic, basil, salt and pepper in a small saucepan and cook. On the other hand, boil the pasta in plenty of salted water for 12 minutes and drain. Put the strained pasta on the serving plate, pour the tomato sauce you prepared on top and serve. Bead Pasta with Basil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

When grilling legs: Preparation: Chicken legs will be opened from the bones. The presence of skin and bones on the thigh depends on your preference. Tomatoes will be cut into rings. The hot peppers will be washed and used whole. Onions and garlic will be peeled. In the purée chamber of the grater, first the garlic will be grated and then the onion will be grated. The puree will be filtered, the resulting water will be used and the pulp will be discarded. Preparation of Chicken Leg Sauce: Sunflower oil, onion juice, tomato paste, yogurt, black pepper, cumin, very little salt will be put into the container and mixed. Chicken thighs will be dipped in sauce and the lid of the container will be closed. The thighs will be rested in the sauce for 3 hours. Chicken thighs rested in sauce will be placed on a well-heated grill. After the grill mark appears on the meat, the meat will be rotated and salt will be sprinkled on it. The same process will be applied to the other side. After grill marks are formed on both surfaces of the meat, the meat will be cooked according to your taste. During the service of the grill, you can sprinkle thyme or other spices on it, according to your preference. Grilled leg is ready to serve, enjoy :)

For vegetarian zucchini kalye, first chop the zucchini coarsely and put them in the pot. Add the washed rice and grated tomatoes, drizzle olive oil on it, close the lid. Let it cook on a very low heat on the stove without adding any water. Then add the chopped dill and mint, close the lid and continue cooking. If you want, you can add up to 1 tea glass of water for the rice. It is possible to prepare this dish without adding onions. It can be served hot or cold. Enjoy your meal :)

While Chicken Emense: First mix the chicken with oil, milk and spices. Grate the garlic and marinate your chickens in this sauce for 5-6 hours. If you have little time, it can wait up to 1 hour. Chop the onions for cooking. Fry them in oil, add the spinach, and fry them on high heat until the spinach is wilted. Do not over-kill the spinach so that they do not lose their green color. Pre-bake your chickens in the oven set at 250 degrees for 15 minutes, then pour your spinach mortar and bechamel sauce on it and return it to the oven. After a little cooking, put grated cheddar on the top. Put the tray near the top shelf of the oven. Take the chicken out of the oven when the cheddar is melted and browned. Cut as you wish and serve with the help of a spatula. Making the bechamel sauce: melt the butter and fry it with flour. When the flour starts to turn white, add 1 handful of grated cheddar cheese (for the top) little by little and prepare it in a pudding consistency. If the chicken is sucked, it is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the milk spinach soup recipe; first wash the spinach in plenty of water and remove the sand. Chop edible and boil in four cups of boiling water. After it is boiled, pass it through the blender. Keep this spinach juice aside. Put the oil in a separate pot. Add the flour and stir fry until it turns pink. Pour two glasses of water and one glass of milk over it and mix. Add the pureed spinach juice. Add your salt. Boil on medium heat. Milk spinach soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Steak with Mushroom Sauce recipe; First, fry the steaks in very little oil. Then pour oil into the pan and heat it up and fry the chopped mushrooms in it. Add the red peppers, add the cream and salt close to cooking and remove from the stove. Steak with Mushroom Sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the creamy carrot soup recipe; Grate the carrots with the small side of the grater and fry in oil. Add flour and ground pepper and add water. Add the milk and cream when cooked. Add the parsley and salt last. Creamy Carrot Soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach chicken gratin recipe; First, rest the chicken meat with olive oil, soy sauce and chicken seasoning. Cook them back and forth in a Teflon pan and line them in a baking dish. Wash the spinach in plenty of water, chop it for cooking and fry lightly with finely cut onions. When the water is gone, drain the water and add the garnish, salt and pepper. Divide this mixture with spinach over the chicken meat. Pour the béchamel sauce you bought over the spinach one by one. If you want, you can make bechamel sauce yourself instead of the ready mix. Sprinkle grated cheddar on the top and bake in a preheated 200 degree oven for about 8-10 minutes until the cheddar melts and turns brown. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Vegetarian Spinach; Wash the spinach with plenty of water. Heat the olive oil in a pan and sauté the finely chopped spinach. When the spinach is cooked, turn off the heat and let it cool. Then open the phyllo on a large table and divide it into two. Put the milk, cheese, sunflower oil and eggs in a bowl and whisk. Spread the sauce on the dough, not too wet. Lay the sautéed spinach lengthwise evenly on each sheet and roll it up. Put on the greased tray. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 20-25 minutes. Then cut it to the size you want. Vegetarian Spinach Wrap is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the oven rice pudding recipe; Wash the rice and boil it with 2 glasses of water until cooked. Add milk and vanilla to the boiled rice and bring to a boil. In a bowl, mix 1/3 cup of milk with wheat starch. When the mixture starts to boil, add sugar and 3 tablespoons of wheat starch mixed with 1/3 cup of milk. Boil for another 10-15 minutes and turn off the heat. Divide the rice pudding into the heat-resistant rice pudding bowls suitable for the oven. Fill the tray with cold water so that the water reaches half of the rice pudding cups and place the rice pudding cups on the baking tray. Place the tray on the top shelf of the oven. Cook the rice pudding at 200 degrees until golden brown. Oven Rice Pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Vegetarian Oven Types; Peel the skins off the eggplants. Chop the bell peppers. Finely chop all the vegetables. Finely chop the garlic. Then put all the vegetables in the mixing bowl. Add salt, spices and olive oil, mix and transfer to the baking dish. In a bowl, thin the tomato paste with 1 glass of hot water and transfer it over the vegetables. Cover the baking dish with parchment paper and then aluminum foil. Bake in the preheated oven until the vegetables are tender. Your Vegetarian Oven Type is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

To prepare semolina halva with chocolate sauce; First, put the margarine in a saucepan and melt the semolina lightly. Then, put sugar, 1 glass of water and 3 glasses of milk in a separate pot, heat it and prepare the syrup. Slowly pour the syrup into the roasted semolina and mix it so that it absorbs well. Put the semolina halva you prepared in a small cake mold to take shape, turn it upside down and put it on the serving plates. Finally, drizzle the chocolate end and pour it over the semolina halva. Semolina halva with chocolate sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Mahluta Soup recipe; finely chop the onions. Add the olive oil and the chopped onions to the pot. Mince the garlic and fry it until it turns pink. Add chicken broth to the mixture and wait until it boils. After boiling, add the washed lentils and rice. After adding the spices and lemon juice, cook the rice and lentils until they are soft. Your Mahluta soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mushroom Quinoa Salad recipe; Cut the mushrooms in julienne and soak them in lemon water. Pour 2 cups of boiled quinoa into the salad bowl. Add finely chopped spinach, arugula, lettuce and basil on it. Boil the mushrooms you have kept in lemon juice until they are soft. After adding boiled mushrooms to the salad mix, you can add oil and lemon to serve your Mushroom Quinoa Salad. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare home-style lentil soup; First, soak the lentils. Then peel and finely chop the onion and fry it in a saucepan with margarine until it turns pink. Add the tomato paste and broth and let it boil. Then strain the lentils and add it. When the lentils are cooked, add the noodles, salt and pepper and let it cook. Then melt a tablespoon of margarine in a separate pan. Add red pepper flakes and mint on top, add this mixture to the pot and mix. Homemade lentil soup is ready. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Mint Bulgur Soup recipe; In a saucepan, take the flour and the oil and fry it. Add the tomato paste and cold water and mix. In another pot, sauté the onion, garlic and bulgur in oil. Then add this mixture into the tomato paste mixture and add hot water. Add the broth and salt to it and let it cook. Melt the butter in a small pan and add the mint and paprika and fry. Add the mint sauce to the pot last. Mint Bulgur Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetable meatballs recipe; Put the ground meat, seasoning for meatballs, stale bread, finely chopped parsley in a bowl and knead. After kneading, prepare it in walnut size. Cut the potatoes and carrots into cubes and fry them in a little oil. Then fry the meatballs. Finely chop the onions. Put the oil in the pan and heat it, fry the onion in the oil, add the tomato paste and turn it once or twice, then add the carrots, potatoes, meatballs and peas and stir a few times. Add the spices and mix again. Add 2 glasses of water and cook on low heat for 10 minutes. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Buttery House Ravioli; First, put the flour, egg, a teaspoon of salt and water in a bowl and knead. When it reaches the consistency that will be a little harder than the earlobe, divide it into 4-5 pieces of meringue. Roll out the dough to medium thickness with the help of rolling pin. Divide the sheet dough into small squares. Prepare the stuffing using ground beef, black pepper, parsley, onion and a teaspoon of salt. Put a pinch of the minced meat you have prepared and close the dough in the form of a bundle. Then fill the pot with water and boil the water. While the water is boiling, add a pinch of salt to it. After the water boils, put the ravioli in the pot and cook. Meanwhile, melt the butter and red pepper flakes in a pan. Then put the grated garlic in the yogurt and whisk. Take the ravioli on a plate and pour the yoghurt first, then the melted butter. Buttery House Ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

To prepare Vegetarian Okra; Roast the onion by chopping it, add the chopped pepper when it turns pink and fry the peppers. Add diced tomatoes and tomato paste. Mix for 2-3 minutes and add the washed okra. When the okras are roasted in 1-2 minutes, squeeze the juice of half a lemon and add hot water. Finally, add salt and spices and let it cook without mixing too much. Vegetarian Okra is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for Roasted Chard in Olive Oil; First, wash the chard thoroughly and finely chop the leaves. Fry the chopped onions in oil. When the onion turns pink, add the finely chopped bell pepper. Add salt and pepper to your taste. Add the garlic and mix. Then add the biceps. Roast the chard until soft and turn off the stove. Serve hot. If you want, pour it on the garlic yogurt. Roasted Chard in Olive Oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the zucchini mucver recipe with cheddar cheese; Zucchini is grated. Other ingredients are added and mixed well. A maximum of 2 tablespoons of olive oil is added to the pan each time, and one tablespoon of our mortar is added to the pan at intervals. It is cooked at medium heat. Your mucver is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the lady's belly recipe; Mix the ingredients except water, sugar and nuts and knead the dough in the consistency of an earlobe. Roll walnut-sized meringues from the dough and place them on a greased tray. Dip hazelnuts in the middle of each meringue. Bake in the oven at 200 C until well browned. As the dough rises, the hazelnuts will rise, so press the hazelnuts to the bottom while they are baking. Prepare the syrup in the pot. Cool the syrup and pour it over the meringues you have cooked while they are hot. Lady Belly is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

Put the milk in a pot first. Then put the egg into it and whisk. After adding cocoa, sugar and flour, take the pot to the stove. Cook without stopping stirring. When it thickens, break the dark chocolate into it, break it into it and continue mixing. Stir for a while and melt the margarine. Now let the supangle cool down, but stir it occasionally so that it does not stick to the crust. Break off large pieces of the cake and put it in the bowls you will serve. Beat the warmed supangle with a mixer until it reaches a smooth consistency and divide it into the bowls. Decorate it as you wish. . Enjoy your meal :)

To prepare tomato barley noodle soup; Chop tomatoes and onions. Add olive oil and tomato paste to the pot and mix. Add the dried mint and mix. Then add chicken broth and bring to a boil. After boiling, add the barley noodles and cook until the barley noodles swell. Tomato barley noodle soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Ezme Chickpea Soup recipe; Fry the chopped onions in olive oil. Then add tomato paste, pepper paste and spices and fry some more. Add the chickpeas and two liters of boiling water and let it boil for 15 minutes on the stove. Pass the Cooked Chickpea Soup through the blender. Boil for another 5 minutes and turn off the heat. Ezme Chickpea Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal .

For the recipe for stew with meat; first chop the onions for food and fry them in a casserole. Then place all the chopped vegetables in the casserole in rows and add the spices, garlic and diced meat on top of it. Put chopped tomatoes and peppers on it again and cover it with aluminum foil. Cook, checking from time to time. All kinds of meat in casserole are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the cauliflower recipe with olive oil; Add the oil to the pan and sauté the chopped onions until they turn pink. Add the carrots that you peeled and cut into rings and sauté for a while with the onions. After adding tomato paste, salt and spices, add the chopped cauliflower to the pot. After mixing the ingredients, add enough hot water to cover it by an inch or two and cook on low heat until the cauliflower softens. Cauliflower with olive oil is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for Bulgur pilaf with Pepper and Tomato; Finely chop the peppers and tomatoes. First, fry the peppers in oil in the pan. Then add the tomato, tomato paste and salt. Put three glasses of water and bouillon on it. When the water starts to boil, add the bulgur. Sprinkle mint on it and cook until it absorbs its water. Bulgur pilaf with peppers and tomatoes is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Oven Pasta recipe; Put the pasta in boiling water. Boil for 8-10 minutes. Then melt the butter in a pan and mix it with flour. Then add cold milk and keep stirring until it boils. After removing it from the stove, break the eggs and mix. Then take the boiled pasta in a large bowl. Pour the prepared sauce over it. Add the grated cheddar cheese, salt and pepper. Bake in the oven until browned. Oven Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the cherry cut pudding recipe; Put all the ingredients except vanilla in a deep saucepan and cook on low heat, stirring constantly. Add vanilla last and mix. After mixing it for a few minutes, turn off the heat. After shaking a long thin glass with water, pour the hot pudding into this glass. Let it rest in the fridge for a day. The next day, take it out of the glass and cut it to the thickness you want and pour it into the coconut. Garnish with frozen cherries. Cherry cut pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the mushroom recipe with olive oil; First, wash and chop the mushrooms. Chop the onion and fry it in oil. Add the mushrooms and chopped red peppers and continue frying. Add the spices and saute. Next, prepare the garlic yogurt. Take the cooked mushrooms on a serving plate, pour the yogurt on them and garnish with dill. Mushrooms with Olive Oil are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Baklava sherbet; Add 3.5 cups of sugar and 3.5 cups of water to the pot and boil it until it thickens slightly. Add the lemon juice you squeezed just before taking it from the stove and let the syrup cool. For the Baklava dough; Add eggs, milk, water, olive oil and salt into the mixing bowl. Add half of the flour gradually to make a soft dough. After kneading the dough, make small meringues and rest the meringues for 30 min-1 hour. 20-24 meringues are enough for a medium tray. To roll out the dough, mix the wheat starch and the remaining flour, and roll out tray-sized phyllo from the meringues you have made. In the meantime, pass the pistachios into rondodon. Sprinkle the pistachios, which you have taken in two or one time, between the phyllo dough. After the dough is rolled out, cut it into lozenges or small squares. Melt the butter in a pan over low heat and pour the melted butter over the baklava. Bake in a 200 degree oven until golden brown. After resting the baklava for 5 minutes, pour the cooled syrup over it. Baklava is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

To prepare Vegetarian Kapuska; Take the liquid oil in the pan and fry the onions that you chopped for cooking. Add the chopped cabbage and continue frying until the cabbages absorb their water. After the cabbages are well roasted, add the rice, tomato paste that you crushed in hot water and salt together with hot water until it reaches the cabbages, close the lid of the pot, and cook it on low heat, checking it from time to time. Vegetarian Kapuska is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Barley Noodle Rice recipe; Roast the barley vermicelli in oil until it turns brown. Then add the rice and fry some more. Add boiling water and salt to the thickness of a finger and cook with the lid closed until the water is absorbed. Cover the bottom of the rice that absorbs the water and mix it. Add 1/2 tea glass of boiling water to the rice and infuse for 15 minutes with the lid closed. Enjoy your meal.

For the couscous recipe; First, fry the noodle, add the couscous and continue frying. Then add boiled water and add salt. Cook on low heat until it boils. Couscous is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the strained lentil soup recipe; Wash the lentils in plenty of water. Add 6 glasses of water, slice the potatoes and onions thinly and boil all the ingredients. Fry the flour in a separate pan and cool it. Crush it with half a glass of water so that there are no lumps. Add the watery flour to the cooked ingredients and pass it through the blender. Add cumin, lemon juice and salt. Strained lentil soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For Chicken Shish recipe; First of all, prepare the yoghurt, garlic, salt, paprika, tomato paste, oil and cumin for the marinade by whisking until you get a homogeneous sauce. Chop your chicken meat into medium and cubes, pour it into the sauce you prepared and mix it. Refrigerate the mixture for at least two hours. Then place the chickens on the skewer sticks without tightening them too much. If you wish, you can also arrange them on a tray lined with greaseproof paper. Set the oven to the grill setting, insert the skewers and cook them on all sides by turning them occasionally. Chicken Shish is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Muska pastry recipe; Boil the potatoes and mix the mashed potatoes by adding other ingredients. Cut the dough into strips 4 inches wide. After putting a spoonful of mortar on three parts of the dough, wrap it in a triangle shape. So that it does not open, dip the tip in a small bowl of water and stick it. Fry both sides in hot oil. Muska pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian cowpea recipe; Soak the cowpeas in hot water 1 hour before cooking. When the black-eyed peas swell, put them in a pressure cooker and add enough water to cover the black-eyed peas and cook. Chop the onion into small cubes. Put the olive oil in a saucepan and heat it. Then add the onions and fry the onions. Dice the tomatoes as well. Add the tomatoes, tomato paste and black pepper to the onions and continue cooking until the tomatoes are cooked too. Turn off the stove when it's done. Drain the boiled black-eyed peas. Put the drained black-eyed peas on a serving plate. Pour the tomato-onion sauce over the black-eyed peas. Finally, finely chop the parsley and sprinkle it over. Vegetarian kidney bean is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Poached Chicken with Olive Oil; Boil a small amount of water in a small saucepan and add salt to it. Crack eggs into boiling water and boil for 5 minutes. With the help of a spoon, take the cooked eggs from the water and place them on the serving plate. Add olive oil and paprika. Pour the pepper sauce you prepared over the eggs. Poached Chicken with Olive Oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Roasted Chicken with Mushroom recipe; First, chop the chicken breasts and mushrooms. Cook in separate pots. Dice the onion and fry it in oil. Add the diced tomatoes and tomato paste. Add mushrooms and salt and cook well, then drain the black juice. Add the chicken breasts to the mixture with their water, then add the mushrooms and spices and mix. Roasted Chicken with Mushroom is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian broccoli recipe; Chop the onion, potato into cubes, carrot into rings and garlic finely. Put the garlic and onion in the pot. Then place the potato, carrot and broccoli on it. Mix a spoonful of tomato paste with a glass of water and pour over it. Add salt, pepper and 2 tablespoons of olive oil and cook for 30 minutes. Vegetarian broccoli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetable noodle recipe; First, boil the noodles like pasta and drain the water. Chop the onions into half moons and fry them in oil until lightly pink. Cut the potato into cubes and add to the onion and fry a little. Chop the parsley into mink pieces by hand and put it in the pot. 1-2 min. mix, add the tomato paste and spices and cook for 2 minutes. then mix and add the boiled noodles, mix some more and turn off the stove. Vegetable noodles are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For panna cotta recipe; Put the milk and cream in a saucepan, add sugar and stir constantly on low heat. When the mixture boils, add the gelatins and vanilla sticks that you have broken into small pieces. When the gelatin melts, remove the vanilla sticks and pour into the cups. After it cools down a bit, put it in the fridge. Refrigerate until it reaches a jelly-like consistency. Then take the sweets out of the containers with the help of a plate. You can serve panna cotta with any fruit sauce you want. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for Mushrooms with Béchamel Sauce; Wash and chop the mushrooms. Heat the oil in a teflon pan and add the mushrooms. Add the salt, pepper and crushed garlic and cook until the mushrooms have evaporated. In a small saucepan, melt the butter and add the flour. After frying for a while, add milk little by little and mix. Add very little salt. When it boils and gets a thick consistency, turn off the stove and pour the sauce over the mushrooms. Add the cheddar cheese and cook it in the oven at 180 degrees until the cheddar melts and starts to brown. Mushroom with Béchamel Sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pasta recipe with bechamel sauce; Boil the pasta in a deep pot in plenty of water for 8-10 minutes. Strain the boiled pasta, run it through cold water and leave it in a strainer to drain. While the pasta is draining, put the margarine and flour in the pot for the béchamel sauce. Fry in oil on medium heat until the flour changes color. While adding the milk little by little, mix it by whisking with the robot. When the sauce has a thick consistency, take it off the stove. Put the pasta in a large bowl and add bechamel sauce and 1 glass of cheddar cheese on it and mix. After mixing well, pour it into my debt. Spread 1 cup of cheddar cheese on it and bake in a preheated 200 degree oven until golden brown. Pasta with bechamel sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for chicken baguette with vegetables in the oven; First, peel the potatoes and cut them into slices of apples and place them on the baking tray. Chop some of the peppers and separate some whole. Chop the onion, garlic, carrot, eggplant and zucchini, put them on the tray, pour oil on them and mix them. Wash the baguettes and place them on top of the vegetables and add the tomatoes to the tray after dicing them. Put the peppers you have separated on the top of the tray, the knees and the peas, and add your salt and spices. Finally, slice the butter on the top and cook it in the oven at 180 degrees until it absorbs its water. Chicken baguette with vegetables in the oven is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Walnut Noodle recipe; Put water in a pot and when it boils, add the noodles and boil. When the noodles swell, drain them and fry them in butter a little. In another pan, fry the walnuts in a little oil. Pour the roasted walnuts into the noodles. Add salt and mix. Walnut Noodles is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Sesame Dessert recipe; Put the flour in the mixing bowl and grate the lemon peels on it. Add the egg, oil and dry yeast. Add the baking powder and the semolina. Knead until it reaches a non-sticky consistency. When you get a non-sticky dough, let it rest a bit. Grease the baking tray. Take out round pieces from the dough, roll them with your hand, form a ring and place them on the baking tray with sesame seeds on one side and sesame seeds on the top. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 20-25 minutes. For sherbet, boil granulated sugar and water in a saucepan. Add 1 slice of lemon to it. Pour the syrup you boiled over the cooked dessert and let it cool. Sesame Dessert is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Olive Oil Chard Wrap recipe; Wash the chard leaves with plenty of water and cut the stems and put them in a separate place. (You can roast the chard stalks as a separate dish) Put a pot of water on the stove and bring it to a boil. Put the chard leaves in 4-5 leaves, wait for 1-2 minutes to boil, take it with a strainer and add the new leaves to the pot. Repeat the same process until the chard leaves are gone and put all the chard in the strainer and let it cool. While the leaves are cooling, to prepare the inside of the chard wrap, wash the rice and pour it into a separate pot. Stir with a wooden spoon over medium heat for 1-2 minutes until the rice is dry. Add 1 tea glass of olive oil, spices and tomato paste on top. Stir for about 3-4 minutes on low heat on the stove. Finely chop the garlic and onion, add the walnut and pepper paste on top and mix for another 2-3 minutes. Cover the mixture before it cooks too much. At this stage, stir from time to time so that the bottom does not stick and let it cool. If the chard leaves are large, cut them in half and fill them with mortar and wrap them. After the wrapping work is finished, put the remaining veins and stems from the chard at the bottom of the pot. Knee the wraps and add 2 cups of water on top. Lay a flat plate on top of the last wraps. Cook for 30 minutes on medium heat. Close to the cooking time, squeeze the salt and 2-3 lemons, add them to the top, boil them with salt and lemon for 10 more minutes and turn off the heat. Enjoy your meal.

For the chocolate cup recipe; Mix the flour, sugar, egg and cocoa in the saucepan and add milk little by little and beat with a mixer. After adding the mastic, let it boil over low heat, stirring constantly. After it boils, take it off the heat, add the vanilla and beat with a mixer for 2 more minutes. Then put it in mugs and grate dark chocolate on it. Put the cups in the fridge and let them sit for a few hours. Your chocolate cup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the cheese pastry; Cut the phyllo into 8 pie slices. Mash the cheese with a fork, finely chop the parsley and dill, add to the cheese and mix it all together. Put a teaspoon of the material on the wide side of a triangular piece of dough, fold and wrap both sides. After wrapping them all, fry them on high heat. Cheese pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the coconut custard recipe; Put the milk, granulated sugar and flour in a deep saucepan and whisk well. Then put the pot on the stove. Stir the ingredients until they boil to avoid lumps. When the pudding thickens, reduce the heat and add the grated coconuts while stirring on low heat. Cook the custard, which boils for another 5 minutes, by stirring, and put it in bowls. When it cools down, the coconut pudding is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare profiteroles; Put 1 glass of water and margarine in a small saucepan and bring to a boil. Then add 1 cup of flour and mix well. Cook the mixture for 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly. Turn off the stove and wait 10-15 minutes for the dough to cool. After the dough has rested for a while, beat 3 eggs into the dough. However, break the eggs into the dough one by one and do not break the other egg until one is well fed. Mix well so that the dough rises. After the eggs are eaten, rest the dough for 10 minutes. With the help of a spoon, take walnut-sized pieces of dough and pour them into the greased tray, paying attention to the 2-3 cm gap between them, as in the picture. Put the dough in the oven, which we previously heated at 180 degrees. Bake for about 40 minutes until golden brown. After the dough is cooked, prepare the cream. Cook the milk, sugar, 3 tablespoons of flour and 1 egg in a saucepan until it reaches a creamy consistency, then add the vanilla and mix. Divide the cooked dough of profiteroles into two or fill them with cream using a cream squeezing bag, if any, and place them on the tray. After filling all the profiteroles, pour the chocolate you melted in a bain-marie. Note: This is how you melt the bain-marie chocolate. Take the chocolate in a heatproof bowl and place your bowl in the boiling water. Make sure that the chocolate melts so that it does not come into contact with water. Melt the chocolate with the heat it gets from the hot water. Your profiteroles are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal. .

For the Basil Tomato Soup recipe; Peel the skins of the tomatoes and cut them into cubes. Finely chop the onion and garlic. Fry the onion and garlic in olive oil until golden brown. Add the tomatoes and fry for another 7-8 minutes. Add tomato juice, water and half of the basil and cook for 25 minutes on low heat by closing the lid of the pot. After cooking, puree the mixture with a blender. Return the saucepan to the stove, add the cream and boil for another 5 minutes, then add the salt, pepper and the remaining basil. Divide the soup into bowls and serve hot by adding parmesan cheese and basil leaves. Basil Tomato Soup is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

For the spinach ravioli recipe; take the flour on the counter and open the middle like a pool. Crack eggs into it, add 3 tablespoons of olive oil and salt and knead. After resting for 15-20 minutes, roll it out to 1 mm thickness with a rolling pin. Cut circles with the rim of a small glass. To prepare the inside of the ravioli, chop the onion and garlic into small cubes. Fry with 1 tablespoon of olive oil. Add the finely chopped spinach, sauté and leave to cool. Then add the ricotta cheese. Put the spinach filling in the middle of the ravioli and close. Then boil the ravioli in boiling salted water for 4 minutes, drain the water and set aside. To prepare the tomato sauce, grate the tomatoes. Finely chop the garlic and basil and add to the tomatoes. Add salt and pepper and let it cook. Add the boiled ravioli to the tomato sauce and cook for another 4-5 minutes. Add the butter, mix and turn off the stove. Divide the ravioli onto serving plates. Garnish with slices of Parmesan cheese and, if you wish, mint leaves. Spinach ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Shakshuka recipe with Olive Oil; Cut the eggplant into cubes and soak in salted water for 20-30 minutes. After chopping the peppers into cubes, mix them with 2 tablespoons of olive oil and bake in the oven. For sauce; Cook the tomatoes, sugar, salt, pepper and vinegar and oil in a saucepan for 25 minutes. Pour the sauce over the baked şakşuka and place it on the serving plate. Shakshuka with olive oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the strawberry mug recipe; poured the milk into the pot. Add the granulated sugar, flour and starch to the milk and boil by mixing. Keep mixing until the custard thickens and becomes eye-to-eye. Take the custard from the stove. Add the vanilla and whipped cream. Mix for 5-6 minutes with a mixer until it reaches the consistency of chewing gum. Pour the custard into the cups you will serve. But don't fill it all in. Leave 2 inches of room for the strawberry sauce. Put the strawberries in the rondo. Add powdered sugar on them and pass through the rondo. Divide the strawberry puree into the cups. We rested the strawberry cups in the refrigerator for 2-3 hours. Strawberry cups are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Telshehriye soup; First, boil 1 liter of water and take the bouillon into a tea glass and add boiled water to it. Then add the olive oil and butter to the pot and add the mint after the oil melts. Add tomato paste after mixing. After 2 minutes, add the vermicelli and mix. After mixing, mix the bouillon in the glass with a teaspoon and pour it into the pot. Add the boiled water, adjust the salt and let it cook. The vermicelli will cook very quickly. Wire noodle soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian spinach recipe; Wash and clean the spinach with plenty of water. On the other hand, finely chop the onion and fry it in oil until it turns pink. Add the tomato paste and add the spinach. Fry the spinach until it melts. Then add half a tea glass of washed rice, salt and spices. Add a glass of boiling water and close the lid of the pot. Cook on low heat until the rice is soft. Vegetarian Spinach is ready to serve. You can serve it with yogurt on the side. Enjoy your meal.

For the Cheese Pasta recipe; Put enough water in the pot to boil the pasta and add salt. When the water boils, put the pasta in it. Boil the noodles until they are soft. After it is boiled, put the cheese and melted butter on it and mix it all together. Cheese Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the broccoli recipe with olive oil; Chop the onion and garlic finely and put them in the pot. Then add the washed and chopped potatoes, carrots and broccoli on it. Mix a spoonful of tomato paste with a glass of water and pour it over it. Add salt, pepper and 2 tablespoons of olive oil and cook for 30 minutes. Broccoli with Olive Oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mediterranean Style Chicken recipe; Put the chicken thighs in a bowl, put the spices and olive oil on it and knead. Put the chickens in the preheated cast iron pan. Close the lid and cook on both sides. Take it on a serving plate. Put the julienne chopped onions and peppers in the pan in which you fry the chicken and sauté by stirring. Add the garlic, sprinkle with a little salt and cook. When you take it from the stove, slice the pitted black olives and mix them. Pour over the chicken. Your Mediterranean style chicken is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach mucver recipe; Finely chop the spinach leaves and put them in a mixing bowl. Crack the eggs. Chop the onion small. Shred the feta cheese and grate the cheddar cheese. Add 4 tablespoons of flour. Add salt and pepper and knead. Heat the oil in the pan and cut the pieces of the hash dough with a spoon and fry it in oil. Put the fried muffins on a paper towel. Finely chop the garlic and mix it with the yogurt. Serve with garlic yogurt. Spinach hash is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for roasting vegetables; After washing all the vegetables, finely chop them lengthwise. Put the oil in a saucepan and heat it. Add the beans first, then the carrots and zucchini, then the peppers and sugar, and stir-fry until the vegetables are soft. Finely chop the basil. Sprinkle half of the chopped basil over the vegetables and reserve the other half for garnishing. Put the roasted vegetables on a serving plate and garnish with the reserved basil. Roasted vegetables are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Vegetable Pasta recipe; Add salt, half a tablespoon of oil and water and boil the pasta with the lid of the pot open until it absorbs its water. On the other hand, take 2 tablespoons of oil in a pan and sauté the finely chopped onion and green peppers. When the onions change color slightly, grate the carrot, dice the tomatoes, add them and continue to sauté. Pour the sauce you prepared on your pasta and mix. Add the finely chopped parsley, close the lid of the pot and let it sit for 5 minutes. Helozon Pasta with Vegetables is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare zucchini dessert with walnuts; After slicing the squash, peel it and remove the seeds. After washing, chop 2-3 finger widths. Arrange in layers in a saucepan, sprinkling sugar between them. Keep it closed overnight. There is no need to add water while cooking, as the zucchini will release water during this waiting period. Cook the zucchini, which you have kept overnight, on medium heat until soft. Cook the zucchini with the lid open for a while to thicken the syrup. After it cools down, transfer it to a serving plate. Sprinkle crushed walnuts on top and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the creamy broccoli soup recipe; Clean the broccoli and cut it into small pieces. Put the olive oil, flour in the pan and fry it. Add the broccoli, water, salt and cook until the broccoli is tender. Then pass it through the blender. Add the cream, mix and cook on medium heat. After the cream of broccoli soup boils, turn off the stove. Creamy broccoli soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the waterfall meatball recipe; Put the grated onion, minced meat, stale bread, egg, dried allspice, black pepper, dried mint, cumin and salt in a bowl and knead. After putting greaseproof paper on the baking tray, put the meatballs in foiled bowls, cover the inside of the bowl with meatballs and place them on the tray. Slide the tray into the oven. Boil and peel the potatoes. Mash the boiled potatoes in a bowl, add the milk, butter and salt, and mash with the robot. After the meatballs are lightly browned, take them out of the oven and fill the meatballs with mashed potatoes. Then mix two spoons of tomato paste and 2 glasses of hot water in a bowl. Pour this mixture on the bottom of the tray and return it to the oven. Then cook for a while. Waterfall meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare chicken farfalle; Put the chicken slices in a large bowl, add wine, half of the finely chopped rosemary, add salt and pepper, mix well and set aside. Heat the oil in a pan and add the finely chopped onion and the diced salami. Fry for 5 minutes over medium heat, stirring frequently. Boil the pasta in a pot of slightly salted boiling water for 10-12 minutes. In the meantime, add the chicken mixture you prepared to the pan and fry it on high heat for 3 minutes. Pour the vinegar over the chicken. Add canned tomatoes and chili peppers, mix well and cook slowly for a few more minutes. Put the rest of the chopped rosemary and the boiled pasta in a deep bowl. Pour the chicken mixture you prepared on it and mix it well. Chicken farfalle is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the gummy pudding recipe; Add milk, flour, oil and sugar and cook on low heat until it reaches the consistency of pudding. When it reaches the consistency of custard, add the mastic gum and cook for 1-2 more minutes, then take it from the stove and share it in bowls and garnish with cinnamon. Gummy pudding is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Kalburabastı; For the syrup of the dessert, put the water and sugar in a saucepan and bring it to a boil. When it starts to boil, add the lemon juice. Boil for another 5 minutes and let the syrup cool. For the dough; Take all the ingredients except wheat flour and walnuts in a deep bowl and knead well. Add wheat flour little by little and continue kneading. After obtaining a soft and shaped dough, let the dough rest for 30 minutes. Take walnut-sized pieces from the dough and press it on a grater. Put the coarsely crushed walnuts in it and close it without disturbing the shape of the dough. Place on a lightly greased tray. Bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees until well browned. Pour the cold syrup on the hot dessert and wait for 1 hour to absorb the syrup. Kalburabastı is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare peregrine soup; Soak chickpeas the day before. Cook until the chickpeas are soft. Add the cooked lentils in a separate pot. After a little cooking, add the sliced onions. Add the previously boiled dry red pepper close to cooking and take it off the stove when the ingredients are cooked. Add red pepper and black pepper in the heated oil. Alaca soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Badempare recipe; First, we cut three glasses of sugar, three glasses of water and two slices of half a lemon, which we will use for the sherbet of almond paren, and put them in a saucepan and boil on the stove. After the syrup boils, we boil it for 15 minutes and leave it to cool. We put the butter, oil, yoghurt and egg that we will use to make the almond paste into the mixing bowl and mix it in such a way that it mixes well. Then we add the powdered sugar. Then we add the semolina and continue mixing. Add 100gr of ground almonds and baking powder to this mixture and mix them well. By adding the flour little by little, we knead it so that it will not be hard (to a consistency that can take shape). We take the walnut-sized dough in our hands, roll it, press it lightly and arrange it on the greased tray. We apply the egg yolk, which we call five tablespoons, on the almond pieces that we put on the tray and dip an almond in each. We bake in a preheated oven at 170 degrees until golden brown. 5 minutes after taking the almonds out of the oven, we pour the syrup on them, which we left to cool. Then we turn a tray on it and wait until it cools down. Badempare is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the meatball recipe; Chop the onion, garlic and parsley finely and put them in a bowl. Then add this coarse ground beef, egg, breadcrumbs, paprika, black pepper, salt, tomato paste, cumin and knead well for about 15 minutes. Then take walnut-sized pieces of this dough that you kneaded and roll it in the palm of your hand in the form of marbles. Place the rounded meatballs on the tray and let them rest in the refrigerator for about half an hour. After the meatballs have rested, cook them in 3 tablespoons of oil that you have heated in the pan. Misket meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chocolate Panna Cota recipe; We leave the gelatins in a bowl with ice water for 15 minutes. Put the milk, cream and sugar in a saucepan and bring it to a boil over medium heat, stirring. After it boils, take it from the stove and add the chocolate into pieces. After adding the chocolates, we filter the gelatin out of the water, add it and mix it and feed it. We pour the prepared chocolate panna cota into bowls. Chocolate panna cota is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Penne Arabiata recipe; Chop the onion finely and the garlic finely. We grate and prepare the tomatoes. We slice the black olives. Put the olive oil in the pan, add the onion and garlic, and fry it until the smell is gone. Then we add the grated tomatoes and olives. Add salt and pepper to it and cook until the water is absorbed. In the meantime, we put some salt and some oil in the pasta boiling water in another pot and bring the water to a boil. Boil penne pasta until cooked. We add the sauce we prepared on the distribution of the boiled pasta to the serving plates. Penne Arabiata is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For the Farm Kebab recipe; After chopping the onions finely and frying them in margarine oil in a saucepan, we add the diced lamb meat on it. Cook, stirring occasionally, until the meat releases its juices. We add the finely chopped fresh onions and peppers and continue cooking. We add the peeled and diced tomatoes, the finely chopped parsley, dill and salt, black pepper, and thyme to the pot and mix one last time. We cook it for about 20 minutes without opening the mouth. Farm Kebab is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

For the Handmade Chicken Snitzel recipe; We thin the chicken breasts with the help of a knife, mix the red pepper, black pepper and salt in a plate. We dip the thinned chicken breasts into this mixture. We break four eggs in another plate and beat them a little. We dip chicken breasts dipped in spices in egg. Then we dip the breasts dipped in egg into breadcrumbs all over. We heat the oil in a pan, then we fry the chicken breasts dipped in breadcrumbs in oil. Handmade Snitzel is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian green lentilK recipe; Boil the lentils, which are kept in salted water for 2 hours, for 30 minutes. We chop the onions into small pieces and fry them in another pot until they turn pink. First, we put the flour on it and fry it a little more, then add a tablespoon of tomato paste and fry it a little more. Add five glasses of water and then chop the potatoes into small pieces and add. When the water boils, we add the boiled lentils and cook a little more. Vegetarian green lentil dish is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Tutmaç soup recipe; Boil green lentils that have been soaked in water beforehand. Strain the boiled lentils, put them in the pot, add 7 glasses of boiling water, put them back on the stove and cook until the lentils begin to soften. When the lentils start to soften, add the noodles and olive oil and cook together until they are soft. Put the yoghurt, egg yolk and flour in a bowl and whisk well. When the lentils and noodles are cooked, put 2 ladles of water from the pot where the lentils and noodles are boiling, into the bowl with the yogurt, mix and let the yogurt mixture heat up. Slowly pour the warmed yoghurt mixture into the pot with the lentils, stirring constantly. When the soup starts to boil again, reduce the heat, add salt and cumin, and boil for another 10 minutes, stirring occasionally. When it boils well, turn off the stove and add the dried mint and mix. Before serving, melt the margarine in a saucepan and add ground red pepper and mix. While serving the soup, pour it with a drizzle of red pepper oil. Tutmaç soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the apple tart recipe; We grate the apples and cook them with granulated sugar until the water evaporates. We add the cinnamon and turn it a little, take it from the stove and leave it to cool. We take the margarine for the dough, a tea glass of sugar, baking powder, egg in a large bowl and knead. Then add the flour little by little. When it reaches the consistency that it will not fall apart, we let the kneaded dough rest for 15 minutes. We separate an orange-sized dough from the rested dough and open the rest on the counter in tray size. We put the dough that we opened in the size of a tray on the tray and spread the apple mortar on it. We open the dough and cut strips, and we place these strips on the tray by giving them the shape of a cage. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven until the tops are golden brown. After cooling, sprinkle powdered sugar on top. The apple tart is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Zucchini Mucver recipe with Olive Oil; First of all, we bring the oven to 180 degrees to warm up. In a medium bowl, grate the zucchini, chop it into small pieces, add the onion, egg, cheese, dill, flour and finally olive oil and beat with a fork. Add the salt and pepper. We lubricate two standard-sized six-packs with oil. Put the mixture you have created in these containers and cook it in the middle of the oven for almost 30 minutes until it is golden brown. Zucchini Mucver with Olive Oil is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

For the Roasted White Cabbage Recipe with Olive Oil; Finely chop the cabbage and wash it. Chop the onions and fry them in oil. Then add the grated carrots and continue frying. Add the cabbages after the carrots and continue the roasting process. After the cabbages become lifeless, add the coarsely chopped spring onions and add the rice when they lose their freshness. Add a little hot water from a glass of water and let it cook on low heat. When the rice is cooked, add olive oil, salt and pepper to it, remove it from the fire and leave the pot to rest with the lid closed. Roasted White Cabbage with Olive Oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Cake Supangle recipe; We put milk in a pot, break the egg into it and whisk it. Then we add cocoa, sugar and flour and put it on the stove. Keep stirring and cook until the consistency thickens. When the consistency thickens, we break the dark chocolate into it and continue mixing. When the consistency thickens, we take it off the stove and add the margarine into it and mix. After melting the margarine, we leave the supangle to cool, but we keep stirring from time to time so that it does not dry out. We place the cakes in my bordeaux and spread the supangle we prepared on it so that it is all over it. Cake supangle is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian spinach gratin recipe; Wash the spinach thoroughly, separate the stems and chop the leaf part to the thickness of a finger. Cut the onions into thin or cubes, lightly fry them in oil and add the chopped spinach to the onions. Fry for a few minutes and turn off the heat. In another bowl, mix the flour, milk and oil, which are the ingredients of bechamel sauce, and cook. Then add salt, pepper, red pepper and 2/3 of the cheddar cheese into the bechamel sauce and mix with the help of a spoon. Pour the remaining grated cheddar cheese on a lubricated borek. Bake the cheddar in the oven at 180 degrees until they turn pink. Vegetarian spinach gratin is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pasta recipe; fill the pot with water and boil it. Then add the pasta and salt into it and mix it and let it boil. After the pasta is boiled, put it in a strainer and run it under cold water. Meanwhile, put the oil in the pan and heat it. Add the boiled pasta and mix well. Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Sour Meatballs recipe; grate the onion. Mix it with ground beef, rice, salt and pepper and knead well. Make ball meatballs by taking hazelnut-sized pieces of ground beef and rolling them in your wet palm. Put the flour on a flat plate and turn the meatballs into this flour. Add half a teaspoon of salt to 4 glasses of water and bring to a boil in a saucepan. Put the meatballs in boiling water and cook on low heat for 15 minutes. Squeeze the juice of the lemon and mix well in a bowl with the yogurt and egg yolk. Add 5 tablespoons of the soup's water little by little to this mixture and add the seasoning you have obtained to the soup by mixing it slowly. Cook for another 5 minutes and serve. Sour Meatballs is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Pendik Pilaki with Olive Oil; Soak the beans in water for 10 hours. Then drain the water and wash it with plenty of water. Empty into a pot. Pour water so that it is a finger above it, bring it to the boiling point on high heat first, then cook it on medium heat. In the meantime, heat the oil in another pan, put the chopped onions in it and fry them until they turn yellow. Finally, finely chop the parsley and peppers and add them. Pour this mixture over the beans, which have finished boiling, without straining, add sugar and salt and let it rest for 2 hours on very low heat. Pendik Pilaki with Olive Oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Ankara pan with chicken in casserole; Put 1 tablespoon of olive oil in the pan and turn on the stove. Add the diced chicken thigh meat and start frying at high heat. Add the chopped onions and continue to turn. When the broth is absorbed, add the diced peppers, then the datomatoes. Put olive oil in a separate pot and start frying the barley noodle. When the vermicelli turns color, add the chicken meat and sprinkle with salt and pepper. Add boiling water and butter and cook on low heat like rice. After the Ankara pan dish with chicken in the casserole is brewed, serve in a casserole or copper bowl. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for halvah with chocolate sauce; Put the butter in a saucepan and put it on the stove. Slowly pour the flour on it and fry the flour with a wooden spoon. Pour cold milk on it and continue cooking, stirring constantly. Add the granulated sugar gradually and when it starts to thicken, add the dark chocolate and continue cooking, stirring with a wooden spoon. When it thickens and becomes difficult to turn, close the bottom and divide the bowls into the serving. Sprinkle with ground hazelnuts on top. Chocolate flour halva is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the tahini cup recipe; Cut the cakes into cubes and divide them into the bottoms of the cups. Sprinkle chocolate chips and peanuts over the cakes. Take the plain tahini halva in a bowl and mash it with a fork. Add 1 cup of milk and whisk until smooth. Put the remaining milk, sugar, flour and vanilla in the saucepan. While continuing to stir, add the halva mixture and cook on medium heat until it thickens. Top the muffins with the custard you prepared with tahini. When it comes to room temperature, put it in the fridge to cool. Tahini mug is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian leek recipe; It cleans and chops the leeks and washes them with plenty of water and allows the water to drain. Clean the outside of the carrots with the help of a knife and cut them into rings. Put the oil in the pot and add the tomato paste and fry it. Then add the carrots and fry them all for 2-3 minutes. After adding the drained leeks, close the lid of the pot and cook. Cook in this way until the leeks are wilted. Finally add the washed rice, salt and sugar and add enough hot water to line up with the food. Cook with the lid of the pan closed until the carrots and leeks are cooked. Vegetarian Leek is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Walnut Wire Kadayif recipe; Separate the wire kadayif with your hands. Melt the butter in a saucepan. Grease the tray you will use as much as 3-4 tablespoons of the melted butter. Pour the remaining butter on the wire kadaifs and mix. Spread half of the oiled and separated kadayifs on the greased tray and press them with your hand. Sprinkle the walnuts you took in the rondo in between. Add the remaining kadayıf to the walnuts and press it with your hand. Put a weight on the dessert and leave it for 10-15 minutes. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven until golden brown. On the other hand, for the sherbet of kadayif, boil the sugar and water in a saucepan. When it boils, add lemon juice and boil for 5 more minutes and remove from the stove to cool. Pour the cooled sherbet over the hot dessert. After the kadayif sherbet is drawn, the walnut string kadayif is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Aegean style zucchini; Peel the zucchini and cut into large cubes. After sautéing the onions in oil, add the chopped peppers and continue sautéing for a few more minutes. Then add the tomato paste, grated or finely chopped tomatoes. A few minutes after adding the tomatoes, put the zucchini in the pot and sprinkle with salt and pepper and mix. Add a little water if needed. Cover and cook on very low heat until soft. Sprinkle chopped dill on top, mix and remove the squash from the stove. Aegean style zucchini is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare cowpea with olive oil; Chop the onions and garlic. Peel the tomatoes and chop finely. Pour olive oil into the pan and fry the onions. Then add the garlic and mix. Then add the kidney beans and mix. After frying well, add the chopped tomatoes. Put in salt and sugar. Add a little water, close the lid and let it cook for 20 minutes on low heat. Black-eyed peas with olive oil are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Cinnamon Rice Pudding recipe; Wash the rice and put it on fire with 1 liter of water and cook it. Then add the cold milk. Mix and wait for it to boil. Meanwhile, crush 2 tablespoons of rice flour with 1 glass of cold water in a bowl. Take 1-2 scoops of the milk that is boiling in the pot and add it to the bowl. Add the rice flour to the pot and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally. Add 2.5 cups of granulated sugar, mix and boil. While cooking the rice pudding, beat the nuts. When the rice pudding becomes thick, divide it into bowls and sprinkle the hazelnuts crushed with cinnamon. Hazelnut Cinnamon Rice Pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled meatball recipe without parsley; First, soak the stale bread in water until it softens and squeeze it out in your palm. Put the bread crumbs that you have removed the water in a bowl. Then grate the onion and sprinkle with salt, pepper, cumin and crack the egg. Add the minced meat that you opened with your hand to this mixture. Mix well for 10 minutes. yoghurt. Then break off walnut-sized pieces with your hand, roll them slightly, then shape them into an ellipse and crush them with your hand. Make a longitudinal hole in the middle with your index finger.
