The meatballs are ready, cook both sides on the grill or in a Teflon pan. Grilled meatballs without parsley are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the basil pasta recipe; Add water and 1 tablespoon of salt to a pot and bring the water to a boil. When it boils, add the pasta. While the pasta is boiling, grate the tomatoes, filter them, remove the seeds and transfer them to another pot. Add olive oil and salt to it. Cook until it loses its shape. Finely chop the basil and onions, crush the garlic and add to the tomatoes. Stir for 1-2 minutes, then remove from heat. Drain the boiled pasta and add the oil to the pot where you boiled the pasta and heat it. Once the oil is hot, add the pasta to the pot and stir. After stirring for 1-2 minutes, turn off the heat and divide into plates. Pour the basil sauce over the pasta evenly on each plate. Basil Pasta is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Potato Recipe with Minced Pepper; Peel the skin of the potatoes and cut into cubes. Put oil in the pan and heat it. While the oil is heating, finely chop the onions, add them to the oil and fry them until they turn pink. Finely dice the tomatoes. Add the tomatoes and tomato paste to the pot, fry for 3 more minutes on low heat. Finely chop the peppers and add to the pot. Fry for 2 more minutes and add the ground beef. Fry the mince until the water is absorbed. Add the potatoes last. Put enough hot water and salt to cover it. Cook until the potatoes are soft. Minced Potatoes are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Adana Kebab recipe; Clean the insides of the red peppers and finely chop them. Mix the ground beef, peppers and salt and knead well. Cut into round portions with wet hands. Put this ground beef mixture on flat skewers and grill the skewers. Adana kebab is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Urfa kebab recipe; Add the twice-ground ground beef, peeled, seeded and chopped into small pieces, the tomato, grated onion, olive oil, salt, spices and chopped parsley. Knead well for 35 minutes. Thread the finger-length meatballs onto skewers and cook them over a strong but flameless coal fire. Urfa kebab is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the skewer recipe; First make the sauce. Crush the garlic, put all the ingredients in the bowl and mix well. Then add the cubed chicken meat and mix well. Rest in the refrigerator for 3-4 hours. Arrange the chicken, peppers and tomatoes on the skewers and cook them on the grill. The skewer is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the liver skewer recipe; Chop the lungs into small pieces. Peel the garlic and crush it well. In a large bowl, mix the olive oil, garlic, salt and spices well. Add the livers to this sauce and rest for 1 hour. After 1 hour, skewer the livers and grill them. Liver skewer is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Hasan Pasha meatballs; Take the ground beef in the mixing bowl and grate the onion on it. Break 1 egg and add stale bread, then add salt and meatball spring and knead. Break off walnut-sized pieces, roll them with your hands and press them lightly in the middle. Grease the baking tray and arrange the meatballs on the baking tray. Bake the meatballs in a preheated 200-degree oven. For the puree, boil the potatoes and grate them and put them in a mixing bowl. Take milk on the grated potato, add grated cheddar cheese and salt and mix. Take the meatballs out of the oven. Put the mashed potatoes in a whipping bag and squeeze into the middle of the patties. Add the grated cheddar to the potatoes and cook until the cheddar is browned. For the sauce, add oil, tomato paste and water to obtain a sauce. Take the cooked meatballs on the serving plate and take the sauce on the serving plate. Hasan Pasha Meatball is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken steak recipe on a bed of spinach; Clean the chicken meat. Put the spices and add salt, milk, soy sauce and mix. Keep in the refrigerator for 1 hour. Meanwhile, sort, wash and chop the spinach. Put a little olive oil in the pan and put some coarsely chopped onions and garlic and fry them. Add the spinach, salt, pepper, paprika. Cook the spinach, stirring occasionally, until it releases its water and absorbs it again. Put a tablespoon of oil in the non-stick pan and fry the chicken meat on both sides. Make a bed of roasted spinach on a serving platter and place the fried chicken on it. Chicken Steak on a bed of spinach is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare chicken kebab; Mince the chicken breast in a food processor, grate the onion, remove and wash the parsley, chop finely. Peel the garlic and crush it in a mortar. Put all the ingredients in a mixing bowl, add egg white, breadcrumbs, black pepper, salt and cumin and knead until it comes to a thick consistency. Thread the mortar you prepared on the skewers and cook it on the grill. Chicken kebab is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the eggplant fritter recipe; Peel the eggplants, cut them into cubes, soak them in water so that the bitter juice comes out. Chop the onion very finely and sauté in oil. Add the ground beef and continue sautéing. Add the eggplants and cook on low heat until soft. Add finely chopped green peppers and grated tomatoes. When the tomatoes are cooked, add salt, pepper and leave to cool. To prepare the sauce to be spread between the dough: Beat the egg, add oil and milk and mix. Get a medium tray. Place one of the pastry sheets with the edges hanging out. Drizzle the milk-egg mixture over the phyllo dough. Do the same with the other piece of dough and spread the eggplant mixture evenly over the dough. Place the other phyllo sheets on the tray in the same way with the sauce between them. Gather the edges of the last hung phyllo at the top and apply the remaining milk-egg mixture all over the pastry. Bake in a preheated oven at 180-190 degrees. Eggplant fritters are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the pita meatball recipe; For the meatballs, grate the onion and garlic. Add the ground beef, bread crumbs and seasonings and prepare the meatballs. Cook meatballs with little or no oil. For the sauce, melt 2 tablespoons of butter. Add tomato paste. Mix well and add water. Boil a pot. Heat the pita and chop it into small pieces. Place it on the plate. Put the meatballs on top and pour the sauce. Meatballs with pita are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare fettuccine with curry sauce; Put more than half of water in a pot and boil it. Put the fettuccine pasta in boiling water and boil it. Reserve 1 glass of water while straining the water. Put the oil and flour in the pot where you boiled the pasta and fry it. Add the cream gradually and cook, stirring with a wooden spoon, until a thick consistency is formed. Mix the curry by adding it to the pasta water you have reserved. Add the curry to the cream and mix a few times. Finally, add the pasta and mix it well, then serve it on the plates. Fettucini with curry sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Bead Pasta with Sauce; While the pasta is boiling, grate the tomatoes and crush the tomato paste. Crush the garlic and pour it into the mix. Melt the butter in the pan, pour the tomato and garlic mixture you prepared and cook. Then add the spices. Pour the sauce over the boiled and drained pasta. Bead Pasta with Sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare cauliflower pan with olive oil; clean the cauliflower, wash it and separate it from the cob. Put water in a pot and bring it to boil. Squeeze the juice of a lemon into the boiling water and add the salt, then add the cauliflower, which we have cut into four, into it and boil it to a medium softness. Take the boiled cauliflower out of the pot and let it cool. Pouch the cooled cauliflower with its branches in a flower-like shape. Mix the flour and cheese on a plate. Dip the cauliflower in egg and cheese mixed with flour and fry in hot oil. Turn the cauliflower so that it is browned on both sides. Serve the fried cauliflower with yogurt. The pan with olive oil and cauliflower is ready to serve Enjoy your meal.

For Adana Kebab recipe; Clean the insides of the peppers and finely chop them. In a bowl, thoroughly knead the parsley, peppers, minced meat, tomato paste and vegetable oil together. Complete the kneading process by adding salt at the end. Refrigerate for one to two hours. Attach this meatball paste to the soaked flat wooden skewers and grill the skewers. After it is cooked, wrap it in a wrap with lavash bread and tomatoes. Adana wrap is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Urfa kebab recipe; Add 1 peeled and finely chopped tomato, grated onion, olive oil, salt, spices and chopped parsley to the minced meat that has been ground twice. Knead well for 30-40 minutes. Thread the finger-length meatballs onto the skewers and cook by turning. After it is cooked, wrap it in lavash bread with tomatoes. Urfa wrap is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken shish wrap recipe; Cut the chicken into cubes and put it in a bowl. Mix the oil, milk, onion juice, crushed garlic and spices together with the chopped chicken and put it in the refrigerator to rest for 3-4 hours. Thread the rested chicken onto skewers and grill until golden brown. After it is cooked, wrap it in lavash bread with tomatoes. Chicken shish roll is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal…

For the vegetable kebab recipe; Put the cubed meat in the pot and cook it for a certain time on low heat. Add the vegetable oil, chopped pepper and onion to the pot. When the meat starts to soften, first add the green beans and add the tomato paste. Cut the zucchini and aubergines in half moons, the carrots into rings, the potatoes and tomatoes into cubes. And add it to the pot in the order you chop it. Then add the black pepper, paprika and salt. And cook for 5 minutes, stirring. Then pour it into the casserole that you lightly oiled, add water to it and cook it on medium heat until the vegetables are soft. Vegetable kebab is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the meat doner wrap recipe; To make the marinade; Put olive oil, yogurt and spices in a bowl. Thoroughly mix the slices of meat with the marinade. Cover the mixture with cling film and leave it in the refrigerator overnight. Then lay the cured meat lengthwise, sprinkling salt between them. Roll it up tightly and keep it in the freezer. Take it out of the freezer 1 hour before cooking and slice thinly. After cooking, wrap the lavash on bread with tomatoes. Meat doner wrap is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken doner wrap recipe; To make the marinade; Put olive oil, yogurt and spices in a bowl. Thoroughly mix the sliced chicken with the marinade. Cover the mixture with cling film and leave it in the refrigerator overnight. Then, lay the cured chicken lengthwise by sprinkling salt between them. Roll it up tightly and keep it in the freezer. Take it out of the freezer 1 hour before cooking and slice thinly. After cooking, wrap the lavash on bread with tomatoes. Chicken doner wrap is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the lamb shish wrap recipe; Cut the meat into cubes and put it in a bowl. Mix the oil, milk, onion juice, crushed garlic and spices together with the chopped meat and leave it in the refrigerator to rest for 3-4 hours. Thread the rested meat onto skewers and cook over medium heat until golden brown. After cooking, wrap the lavash on bread with tomatoes. Lamb shish roll is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal…

For the liver wrap recipe; Chop the livers into cubes and put them in a bowl. Mix the oil, milk, onion juice, crushed garlic and spices together with the chopped liver and leave it in the refrigerator to rest for 3-4 hours. Thread the rested liver onto skewers and cook over medium heat until golden brown. After it is cooked, wrap it in a wrap with lavash bread and tomatoes. Liver wrap is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the roasted pepper; Wash the peppers and dry them thoroughly. Then place on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Put it in a preheated 200 degree oven. Roast in the oven for about 30-35 minutes, turning it occasionally. Roasted pepper is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chicken Sauteed with Mushroom recipe; Put the finely chopped onion, finely chopped or grated garlic, finely chopped green and red pepper in a large pan and cook for 2-3 minutes. Wash and slice the mushrooms thoroughly. Chop the chicken into cubes. Add the chicken and mushrooms to the ingredients in the pan. Cook over medium heat until the mushrooms release their water and absorb it again. Then dice the tomatoes and add them to the dish. Add salt, pepper and cayenne pepper. Close the lid of the pan or the pot, cook a little more and turn off the stove. Mushroom Chicken Sauteed is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

To prepare Beef stroganoff; cut the meat into thin strips. Heat the olive oil in a saucepan and fry the meat on it. When the meat starts to absorb its juices, add the finely chopped onion and garlic. Add 1 teaspoon of salt and pepper, mix for a couple of times and close the lid. When the onions are soft and cooked, add mustard and a glass of hot water. Mix and close the lid again. Cook on low heat until the meat is tender. Meanwhile, wash and cut the mushrooms, add them to the pot. Add another teaspoon of salt on it and close the lid. When the mushrooms release their water and cook, add the butter and close the lid again. Whisk the cream with a spoonful of flour until smooth. Pour over the cooked food and mix. After cooking for 10 more minutes on low heat, turn off the stove. Beef stroganoff is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

To prepare vegetable paste soup; Finely chop the onion and fry it with olive oil. Add 1 tablespoon of flour and mix 1-2 times. Add the leeks, carrots, and celery that have been processed in a food processor. Stir for a few more minutes and add the water. When the vegetables are lightly cooked, add the potatoes passed through the robot and cook. Then, beat the yolk of 1 egg with the juice of 1 lemon in a separate bowl. Take the water from the soup little by little with a spoon and warm the seasoning. Then slowly add the seasoning to the cooked soup. Add your salt. Vegetable mashed soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian seasoned celery recipe; Finely chop the onions and put the oil and onions in a pan and fry them until they turn pink. Peel the celery, boil it, then slice and drain it and add it to the pot. Cook for a few minutes, stirring, then close the lid and cook for 20 minutes on medium heat. In another bowl, whisk together the egg yolks, the water in which you boiled the celery and the juice of the lemon. Then slowly pour it over the celery in the pot, mixing it. After pouring, cook for a few more minutes by stirring and turn off the heat. Vegetarian seasoned celery is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetarian potato gratin recipe; Peel the potatoes and cut them into thin slices. Bow to a small rectangular bowl. Then mix 1 box of cream, salt and half of the cheddar cheese in a bowl and pour it over the potatoes. Smooth it over and bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees for 35 minutes. Open the oven door and sprinkle the remaining cheddar cheese all over the pyrex and put it back in the oven. Cook for another 5 minutes until well browned. Vegetarian potato gratin is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Noodles with Olives; First, start boiling the noodles in a saucepan. Strain through a strainer before it gets too much boiled and crushed. Mix the tomato paste and spices in a separate bowl and add the noodles in it. Then add the olives into it. After you take it to your plate, sprinkle the corn kernels and cheddar cheese. Olive Noodles is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Spiral Pasta with Tomato Sauce recipe; Put water and some salt in a pot and bring it to a boil. Put the pasta in the boiling water and while the pasta is boiling, grate the tomatoes and crush the tomato paste in it. Crush the garlic and pour it into the tomato paste mixture and mix. Melt the butter in a pan, pour the tomato paste sauce and cook. Then add the thyme and cayenne pepper. Pour the sauce over the boiled and drained pasta. Spiral Pasta with Tomato Sauce is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

For the Farm Rice recipe; Extract two glasses of rice and wash the rice with plenty of water. Soak in salt water for an hour. Take two tablespoons of butter in a saucepan. Add long chopped carrots, finely chopped peppers, mushrooms cut in half and saute. Add two glasses of water and boil it. Add a lump of sugar, bay leaf and salt. Cook for 15 minutes on low heat. Add peas, boiled chickpeas, finely chopped dill and half a teaspoon of black pepper to the rice you take from the fire and mix well. Farm Rice is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Mushroom Stew with Olive Oil; Clean the mushrooms, finely chop the potatoes, carrots, tomatoes, peppers, onions and garlic. Mix mushrooms, potatoes, carrots, tomatoes, peppers, onions, garlic, sugar, vinegar and salt and put them in a saucepan. Mix the juice of half a lemon and oil in a bowl and pour it over the ingredients. Cover the pot with baking paper and close the lid. Cook it in its own juice on a heavy fire. Mushroom stew with olive oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Islamic meatball recipe; Peel the eggplants and cut them into long strips. Soak in salt water until the bitter juice comes out (about half an hour). On the other hand, grate the onion for the meatballs, add the ground meat, egg, bread crumbs, spices and prepare the meatball dough. Cut off pieces slightly larger than walnuts and roll them. Drain the aubergines that have been waiting in the water and dry them with a paper towel. Fry the eggplants in hot oil. After the eggplants are done, fry the meatballs. Wrap the meatballs with either a double eggplant or a single eggplant. Cut the tomatoes into rounds and the peppers into quarters. Stick the chopped tomatoes and peppers on the eggplants with a toothpick. Place the prepared meatballs on the baking tray. Prepare the sauce by whisking the tomato paste with 2 glasses of water. Pour the sauce you prepared with tomato paste and water on the meatballs. Bake in the oven at 200 degrees until the tomatoes and peppers melt. Islim meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Baby Skewer recipe, cut the chicken breast into two finger-thick hand lengths. Mix with black pepper, cayenne pepper, cumin, onion powder, garlic powder, thyme, salt and oil. Insert a litter bottle and dip it in the egg. Then dip it in breadcrumbs and fry. Baby skewer is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the Anatolian Soup recipe; Put the broth in a large pot, adjust the salt and let it simmer by closing the lid. While the broth is boiling, do other operations. Put oil in a pan, melt the oil slightly, pour flour on it and fry for 2-3 minutes. Finely chop the bell peppers and tomatoes in a separate bowl. When the broth boils, pour the roasted flour, boiled rice, peppers and tomatoes into the broth and mix. Boil for another 15 minutes and remove the soup from the fire. Anatolian soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Tomato Wire Noodle Soup recipe; Wash and clean the tomatoes, then grate them, kill them a little with oil and add salt. Put half a liter of water on it and let it boil. Throw the vermicelli into the boiling water and turn it once or twice. Close the lid after 15 minutes. Add lemon juice and finely chopped parsley on it. Tomato vermicelli soup is ready. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the Turkey Tandoori (Apple Sliced Potato) recipe with Thyme; Set the oven to 200 degrees. Cut the onion into four. Chop the carrots into large cubes. Make small nicks on the turkey meat with a knife and place it in the baking dish. Mix the olive oil, salt and pepper to the meat. Scatter onions, garlic, carrots, and sprigs of fresh thyme over and around the meat. Sprinkle water on it and cover it with aluminum foil and cook for half an hour. Then reduce the oven temperature to 180 degrees and bake for 1 more hour. After an hour, you took the foil and kept it in the oven for half an hour until the top of the meat was browned. Turkey Tandoori with Thyme is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Sausage Puff Pastry recipe: After the puff pastries are thawed, cut the sausage in half and place it in the middle of the puff pastry and wrap it. Take care that the fold is down, lay them on the tray and notch the puff pastry with a knife on the diagonal. Brush with egg yolk and sprinkle with black cumin and bake in a preheated 180 degree oven. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the vegetarian sailor style dried beans recipe: boil the beans that have been soaked and drained overnight in a pot with 3-4 glasses of water for 30-50 minutes depending on the type. While the beans are boiling, put the oil in another pan and fry the coarsely chopped onions. Finely chop the tomatoes and add. Cook until the tomatoes release their juices. Then add the boiled and drained beans to the pot and mix. Add 2-3 glasses of water, medium-sized red peppers and salt and cook for half an hour, then turn off the heat. Vegetarian sailor style dry beans are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Roasted Eggplant recipe: Roast the eggplants in the oven or on the stove, peel them after roasting. Finely chop the peeled eggplants. Sprinkle salt on it and it's ready to be served. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the Höşmerim recipe: Melt the butter. Add the semolina and fry until it turns golden brown. Boil sugar, milk and water in a separate saucepan. Pour this syrup over the semolina, which turns golden yellow. Grate the tongue cheese and add it to the dessert. Cook until the cheeses melt. Take my höşmer off the fire and give it neat shapes with a spoon on the serving plate. Garnish with unshelled almonds. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the spinach chicken wrap recipe; Finely chop the chickens and sprinkle them with salt and pepper. Wash and clean the spinach with plenty of water, chop the onion in piyaz. Put the oil in the pan and fry the onions. Then add the spinach and continue frying. Set aside, add the pine nuts and chili peppers. Put the chickens you've been waiting for on the edge of the puff pastry dough. Add the spinach stuffing on the chicken and wrap it in a roll. Lay on the baking tray. After wrapping the others in the same way, brush them with eggs, sprinkle black cumin seeds and bake them at 190 degrees until they are completely browned. Chicken Wrap with Spinach is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the New Year's Eve dessert recipe; First, put the walnuts and almonds in a blender. After breaking into small pieces, add honey and oat paste to the mixture and mix until they are well mixed. At the bottom of a bowl, place some of the kiwi and blueberries that you cut into cubes. After adding the other mixture on it, add the remaining fruits on top. You can add yoghurt on top and keep it in the freezer for 5-10 minutes and serve. Enjoy your New Year's Eve dessert.

For the Cinnamon Gingerbread Cookies recipe; Mix the flour, salt and baking powder in a bowl. Beat the sugar and butter in another bowl until creamy. Add the milk, ginger, lemon peel, cinnamon and egg to this creamy mixture and mix. Then add the flour, salt and baking powder mixture to this mixture and knead until you get a soft dough. Keep this dough in the refrigerator for about half an hour. Open the dough on a flat surface with a rolling pin and shape it with new year patterns such as Santa Claus, pine tree, deer. Then put these cookies on the tray and bake them in a preheated 175 degree oven for 20 minutes.

For the Christmas chocolate forest cake recipe; Beat 5 eggs and 5 tablespoons of sugar in a deep bowl with a mixer for 4 minutes until foamy. In a separate bowl, mix the flour, baking powder and 5 tablespoons of starch. Add the flour mixture by sifting it into the mixture mixed with the mixer. Lay the greaseproof paper on a medium sized round tray and pour the mixture on it. Spread the dark chocolate chips over the mixture and bake this tray in the oven at 220 degrees for 10 minutes. Then let the cake cool and rest in the refrigerator for 1 hour. Melt 200 grams of white chocolate in a bowl and mix it to cool. While it is a little runny and not too hot, apply it over and to the sides of the pastry cake that has been rested in the refrigerator. Arrange the defrosted cherries around the edges of the cake. Christmas chocolate forest cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the orange chocolate cake recipe; Cook the cocoa powder pudding with 5 glasses of milk. Add the chocolate to this mixture, stir until it melts, and when it melts, take it off the stove. Cook the vanilla powder pudding by mixing the remaining 1 glass of milk, orange juice, and grated orange peel. Knee enough catnip to cover the bottom of my rectangular pyrex and pour two-thirds of the chocolate pudding over it. Line up another row of biscuits and spread the orange pudding on top. Arrange the biscuits for the third time, add the rest of the chocolate pudding and level with the back of the spoon. Sprinkle hazelnuts on top and chill in the refrigerator for at least 2 hours and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Crispy Cauliflower Balls recipe; Separate the flower parts of the cauliflower and wash it with plenty of water. Peel it into a medium-sized saucepan, add lemon and water to it and boil for 5 minutes. After boiling, drain the water, mash the cauliflower in a large plate and break an egg on it. Then, if there is stale bread, pass it through the rondo, add the chili pepper, cumin, black pepper, thyme and salt on it and knead. While kneading, add a cup of flour gradually and continue kneading. Make walnut-sized balls as the mixture takes on the consistency of meatballs. Distribute the vermicelli on a flat and slightly wide plate, and roll the balls you have made into the vermicelli so that they are wrapped around the vermicelli. Add 2 tablespoons of oil and fry these balls by turning them in the frying pan. Enjoy your meal.

For the Homemade Salep recipe; Put the rice flour, wheat starch and sugar in a saucepan and add the milk little by little. Stir on low heat until it thickens. After boiling, keep it on fire for a few minutes and keep stirring. Serve in cups and garnish with cinnamon. Enjoy your meal...

For the coconut cookie recipe; Put the egg whites and powdered sugar in a large bowl and beat for 1.5 minutes. Then add the coconut on it and keep whisking until it all gets mixed and soft. Mix this soft mixture in a preheated pan on low heat for 4-5 minutes by turning it with a wooden spoon. Then let this mixture cool down and when it cools, form balls the size of walnuts. If you wish, put the walnut-sized balls inside the colored cookie sheets and line them up on my debt, if you wish, directly on my debt. Bake in a preheated 160 degree oven for 25 minutes. Coconut cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Wet Cookies recipe; Put the softened butter, powdered sugar and egg in a deep glass bowl and knead. When the ingredients are mixed together, add the cocoa and vanilla and continue kneading. Add the oil, baking powder and half of the flour to the soft mixture that has formed. Knead the mixture again. Then slowly add the remaining flour and knead the dough until it loses its stickiness. Small pieces of this dough are torn off and given a round shape and lightly pressed on it. Lay these balls you made on the greaseproof paper you put in the tray. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 10-12 minutes. To create the wetness of the cookie, put water and sugar in a saucepan and bring to a boil. Afterwards, dip the cookies you baked into this cooled syrup and wait for it to absorb the water by placing it on a serving plate. Wet Cookies are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Flour Cookies recipe; Put the melted butter in a large bowl, add powdered sugar, baking powder, one and a half glasses of flour and knead slowly. Then slowly add the remaining glass of flour to this mixture and continue kneading. When the dough does not stick to the hand, divide the dough into two equal parts. Shape one of the pieces with your hands into a long stick like using a rolling pin. Draw a straight line with a thin stick over this long dough. And cut the dough in a baklava type and lay it on the greased tray paper that you laid on the baking tray. Take walnut-sized pieces from the other dough and roll them and place the pistachios on them. Arrange the round flour cookies on the tray. Then bake in a preheated 200 degree oven for 10 minutes. Then lower the oven temperature to 160 degrees and cook at this temperature for 20-25 minutes. After the cookies have cooled, arrange them on the serving plate and sprinkle powdered sugar on them. Flour Cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Grape Cookie recipe; Put the egg and granulated sugar in a bowl. Beat until it approaches a white color. Then add the softened margarine at room temperature and knead it. Add three glasses of flour slowly to this liquid mixture and knead it. After kneading, add the baking powder, walnuts and raisins and mix. Mix it well and when it reaches the consistency of the earlobe, place it on the tray by giving it a messy shape or a round shape with your hands. Bake the tray in a preheated 180 degree oven for 25 minutes until golden brown. Arrange the cookies on a serving platter. Raisin Cookies are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Jelly Cookies recipe; sift the flour into a hollow bowl. Heat and melt the margarine and pour it into the middle of this dough. Break the egg on it, add the baking powder, vanilla, a tea glass of powdered sugar and crushed hazelnuts and knead until the dough does not stick to the hand. From this dough, break off pieces of hazelnut size, roll them and press them with your fingers to form a medium-wide round dough. Place these doughs on the oiled paper you put in the tray and bake them in a preheated 180 degree oven for 15-20 minutes until they turn pink. Spread the jelly on the cooled cookies and put the jelly parts of the two rounds together and press them lightly to stick them. Arrange the cookies on a serving plate and sprinkle cinnamon and powdered sugar on top. Jelly Cookies are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For the Jellybean Cookies recipe; Put the softened butter and powdered sugar in a deep bowl and mix well. Add the flour gradually and knead until the dough is not sticky to the hand. Wrap the dough in cling film and rest in the fridge for half an hour. Open the rested dough with a rolling pin and cut round dough with the rim of the tea glass. Make a slight indentation in the middle of the dough you made with the back of another small lid. Place one or two jelly beans in these pits. Line the dough you have made on the oiled paper that you have placed in the baking tray. Bake the tray in a preheated 170 degree oven for 15 minutes. Jellybean Cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the chocolate blueberry fit cookie recipe; After melting the butter in a pan, add sugar to the beaten egg in a separate bowl and mix. Add the flour and other ingredients and the grated dark chocolate to the mixture. After mixing all the ingredients in the same bowl, take small pieces on the greaseproof paper in small pieces and place them without shaping. After cooking for 13 minutes in the oven at 180 degrees, serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Light Easy Supangle recipe; Put the flour, cocoa and splenda in a deep saucepan and mix. Add the milk slowly. Cook until it reaches a custard consistency. Add in the vanilla and margarine. Beat the eggs in a separate bowl. Take the pudding on the stove and add the eggs without waiting and beat with a mixer. Place the cat tongues in the bowls and pour the supangle you prepared on it with the help of a ladle. Light Easy Supangle is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal...

For Light Semolina Dessert, put the semolina, milk and splenda in the pot and cook by mixing until it thickens. Add vanilla and margarine in it. Then, whisk it well with a fork or whisk until it reaches the consistency of boza. After whipping, pour half of the custard into a mold and sprinkle half of the cinnamon and hazelnuts on top. Pour the remaining semolina dessert in the pot on top and sprinkle with hazelnut and cinnamon again. You can serve after it cools. Enjoy your meal...

For the oven-baked tabby fish recipe; Take the cornmeal and salt in a freezer bag and mix them. Throw the tabby fish into it and shake the bag so that the fish are floured and then shake off the excess flour. After preparing all the fish in the same way, place them on a baking tray greased with sunflower oil. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven for about 30-40 minutes until the fish is browned. Lightly grease the cleaned onions with olive oil with the help of a brush. Cook on the hot grill for about 5 minutes on each side. Slice half a lemon and place the Fish on a serving plate and serve with grilled onions and sliced lemons. Enjoy your meal.

For the Raw Borek recipe; Put the flour in a glass bowl and add salt and water gradually and knead the dough. When it reaches a non-sticky consistency, cover your mouth with a cling wrap and let the dough rest for 15 minutes. While the dough is resting, add ground beef, grated onion, black pepper and a teaspoon of salt to another bowl and knead. Then break off 2 walnut-sized pieces from the dough you rested. With the help of a rolling pin, flour the pieces you cut off and open them in a round shape. Spread the minced meat you prepared on the half of the dough you have rolled out. Cover the part you didn't put inside over the part you put inside and stick the tips together with your fingertips. With the dough cutting wheel, give a serrated shape from the part you pasted to the end. Add oil to a pan and fry the raw pastries you prepared in this oil when the oil is hot. Lay the lightly browned pies on the plate on which you laid a napkin. Raw pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal...

For the vegan banana cookie recipe; Line a baking tray with greaseproof paper. Peel the banana and mash it well with a fork. In the mixing bowl, mix the margarine with the sweetener thoroughly. Add the banana and vanilla and mix well. Add the flour with the baking soda into the mixture. Knead until you get a soft, smooth dough. Take small pieces from the dough and roll them with your hands. Lay it on greaseproof paper, flatten it and arrange it evenly. Put in the oven preheated to 180C. Bake for about 12 minutes until the bottoms and edges are lightly browned. Enjoy your meal.

For the fruit vegan cake recipe; Mix the flour, half the sugar, vanilla, cocoa, baking powder and salt in a large bowl. Open the middle like a pool and add olive oil, cold water and vinegar. Mix the ingredients well with a spoon or wire whisk. Grease a small square cake tin and pour the mixture into it. Bake in a preheated oven at 175 degrees for about 30 minutes. Check if the cake is cooked by inserting a toothpick. Thoroughly mix oat bran, wheat starch and half of the sugar in a deep bowl. Slowly add the soy milk, stirring constantly. Cook like a custard. Leave the base and edges of the cooled cake and take out the middle. Spread warm custard and coarsely crushed hazelnuts in the middle of the cake that has formed into a pool. Slice and arrange strawberries, kiwi and bananas on the cooled pudding. Rest in the refrigerator for an hour. Enjoy your meal.

For the Quinoa Rice recipe; Chop all the ingredients for food and grate the carrots. Add the oil to a flat pan and fry in the oil until the ends turn pink, then add the tomato paste. Then add all the chopped vegetables and stir fry. Finally, add the quinoa, which has been thoroughly washed and soaked in hot water, and add 2 cups of hot water and cook on medium heat. When the quinoa is drained, turn off the heat and let it rest. Quinoa Rice is ready to serve. Bon appetit.

For the chickpea quinoa salad recipe; Chop cucumbers, carrots and peppers, tomatoes into small cubes. Put it in a deep salad bowl. Finely chop the dill and mayonnaise and add it. Add the cooked quinoa and chickpeas and mix. Lastly, add olive oil and pomegranate syrup and mix once or twice more. Chickpea quinoa salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For vegan burger recipe; Grate the peeled zucchini and carrots with the coarse side of the grater. Chop the onion into piyaz or small cubes as desired. Saute the onions until they turn colour. Continue sautéing after adding the grated vegetables. Keep the mortar you have taken from the stove aside to cool. Puree the Mexican beans. Mix beans with vegetables, sunflower seeds, cumin, coriander, peanut butter. Fry both sides in the pan. Put it between the lettuce and tomatoes and the bread. Enjoy your meal.

For the green zucchini soup recipe; Grate the zucchini and potatoes and mash them. Mix the soy milk, water and your grated vegetables and cook. Add salt and pepper before removing from the stove. After the green zucchini soup is cooked, you can pass it through a blender and add the dill and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Whole Wheat Cheese Pasta recipe; Put 2 cups of whole wheat pasta in pre-boiled hot water with added salt and boil it. After straining, add six tablespoons of crushed white cheese and 8 tablespoons of ground walnuts and mix well. Add fresh mint leaves on it. Wholemeal Cheese Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. (We will not need to add extra oil, as the oil in the cheese and walnuts will be sufficient.)

For the Home Kumpiri recipe; Roast the peeled potato by scratching it a little in the middle with a knife. Then take out the roasted potato and, without breaking the potato, mix it with a knife and add 1 teaspoon of oil until it becomes a puree. Then add grated cheddar cheese and mix it a little. Add the finely chopped pepper and the olives that you have removed from the seeds and sliced. Then mix in the corn, yogurt, and peas, then add to the potatoes. Homemade kumpir is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.
To make Amasra salad; Finely chop all the ingredients. After mixing them in a deep bowl, add their sauces. Enjoy your meal.

Finely chop the onions. Fry the onions in olive oil until they turn pink. Add the peppers and fry them. Add the ground beef and other ingredients. Add the parsley when the water has evaporated. Crack the eggs. Serve. Enjoy your meal.

Sift the flour, add salt and sugar to the sifted flour and mix. Knead the dough with lukewarm water until it reaches the consistency of the earlobe. After kneading for 15-20 minutes, let the dough rest for 15-20 minutes. Then roll the dough into a cylinder. Divide the dough into 20 equal parts. Roll each piece into a ball. Let these balls sit for 15-20 minutes. Then, open the tiny balls to the size of a dessert plate, grease them with oil, and leave them on a plate for another 15 minutes, with 5 of them on top of each other. Roll the 5-layer dough thinly with oil. Oil the dough that you have opened well and wrap it like a bundle. Let the dough rest for another 15 minutes while it is rolled up. Divide the roll into 5 equal pieces. Press the center of the pieces with 2 fingers. Bake in the oven at 200 degrees. Enjoy your meal.

For the Minced Cauliflower Gratin; Fry finely chopped onions in oil for 2-3 minutes. Add the peppers and ground beef. Add the cauliflower in small florets and add 1/2 cup of water. Cook for 15 minutes until the water evaporates. In another bowl, make bechamel sauce with butter, milk, pepper, salt and flour. Take the cauliflower in a bowl. Pour the béchamel sauce. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 20-30 minutes. Add the cheddar that is close to cooking. Cauliflower gratin with minced meat is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Cauliflower Recipe with Soy Minced; Boil cauliflower in salted water. In another bowl, add enough water to cover the soybean mince and wait for it to swell. Cook for 15 minutes with the diced tomatoes. Add your spices and pour over the cauliflower. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 15-20 minutes. Cauliflower with soy mince is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Lemon Cake recipe; Beat eggs and sugar. Add oil and milk. Add the lemon juice and peels and mix. After homogenizing in the flour and baking powder, pour it into the cake mold and bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 30 minutes. The lemon cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Sweetened Walnut Cake recipe; In a bowl, whisk the milk, oil and eggs well. Add the other ingredients on it and mix it to form a cake batter. Grease the cake mold with 1 level teaspoon of margarine. Pour the cake batter into the mold and sprinkle walnuts on top before putting it in the oven. Bake in a preheated oven at 220 degrees for 40 minutes. Sprinkle cinnamon powder with a tea strainer after taking it out of the oven. Serve lukewarm. Enjoy your meal.

For the sweetened wet tiramisu cake; Beat eggs (4 pieces) and heat resistant sweetener (20 g). Add wheat (60 g) and rye flour (60 g), water (1 tea glass), cocoa and baking powder and mix. Pour into greased pan (26 cm) and bake at 175 °C until puffed. To wet the cake; Mix milk (1.5 cups), instant coffee and heat-resistant sweetener (1.5 tablespoons) and wet the cake with this mixture. For the cream; Heat wheat flour (40 g), heat resistant sweetener (10 g), margarine and egg (1 piece) in a saucepan and gradually add milk (0.5 cups). Keep stirring while pouring the milk so that it does not solidify. When it reaches the consistency of boza, pour it into the cake. You can serve after refrigerating overnight. Enjoy your meal.

For the sweetened chestnut cake recipe; Crush the biscuits until they reach the consistency of flour in the food processor and add the chestnuts by crumbling them. Chop the banana, grate the apple. Thoroughly mix the grapes, grated apple, chopped banana and melted margarine in a bowl. Combine this mixture with the chestnut mixture, wrap it in foil and freeze it in the freezer. Mix the water, milk, cocoa, and heat-resistant sweetener in a saucepan and cook over low heat, stirring, until thick. After the pudding-like mixture has cooled down a bit, pour it over the cake you have frozen in the refrigerator. Sweetened chestnut cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Hazelnut Almond Biscotti recipe; Beat butter and sugar until creamy. Add the eggs to the mixture. Add the flour and baking powder. Add the nuts and lemon zest. When the dough mixture has a consistency, divide it into 2 equal parts and put it in the form of a roll on greaseproof paper and bake. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 40 minutes. After removing from the oven, slice and bake for another 10 minutes. Hazelnut Almond Biscotti is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For SDM chicken flavored soup recipe; Mix the powder from the package with 1 glass of water until you get a homogeneous density. Heat in the microwave on high for 1 minute, or heat on a medium stovetop by stirring with a wooden spoon. Turn off the heat as soon as it boils. Stir with a mixer for better mixing. SDM chicken flavored soup is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For SDM vegetable soup recipe; Mix the powder from the package with 1 glass of water until you get a homogeneous density. Heat in the microwave on high for 1 minute, or heat on a medium stovetop by stirring with a wooden spoon. Turn off the heat as soon as it boils. Stir with a mixer for better mixing. SDM minestrone soup is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For SDM cheese flavored omelet recipe; Mix the powder with 120 ml of room temperature water until a homogeneous density is obtained. Heat the pan that you have oiled and oiled with a paper towel. Cook both sides for 1-2 minutes. SDM cheese flavored omelet is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Yoghurt Pasta recipe; Boil the pasta in enough water to cover it by 2 inches. In a separate bowl, mix the yoghurt with the grated garlic and salt. Take the boiled pasta in a large bowl and pour the yogurt on it. After making a sauce with tomato paste, red pepper and mint in olive oil, pour it over the yoghurt. Yoghurt pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Eggplant with Olive Oil recipe; peel the eggplants variegated. Cut each eggplant into 4 cylindrical parts. Soak in salted water for 5-10 minutes. Finely chop the onions and tomatoes. Fry the onions in olive oil until they turn pink. Then add the tomato paste and tomato paste. After squeezing the eggplants you have soaked in water, add them into the pot. Add enough water to not exceed it. Grate the garlic that is close to cooking. Eggplant with olive oil is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the fit pizza recipe; Spread the labneh on wholemeal lavash. Spread the eggs and cheddar that you mixed in the bowl on the lavash. Add the sliced tomatoes, peppers and mushrooms. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven. Serve with arugula.

For Le Pain Quotidien Grain Bread recipe; Add flour, water and salt to Le Pain Quotidien sourdough and knead. If the dough is hard, you can soften it with water. Give this dough the shape you want after waiting for 2 hours. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven. Le Pain Quotidien Cereal Bread is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Le Pain Quotidien Chicken Sandwich recipe; Place the boiled chicken and lettuce in the Le Pain Quotidien multigrain bread baguette. Chicken Sandwich with Le Pain Quotidien is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Yogurt-Free Ravioli recipe; Put the flour in a wide bowl and open the middle of the flour, break the egg into this part, sprinkle a pinch of salt and knead the dough by adding water little by little. After kneading the dough until it does not stick to the hand. Make meringues from the dough, roll them out one by one, thicker than the ready-made dough, and cut them squarely. On the other hand, add paprika, black pepper, salt and grated onion into your mince and knead a little. Put the small pieces of minced meat on the dough you cut squarely. Bring the 4 corners of the dough together and shape them. On the other hand, boil water in a large pot and add some salt. When the ravioli is ready, pour it into boiling water and cook for 15-20 minutes. Meanwhile, melt the butter in a small pan and fry the tomato paste. Add this mixture to the water of the cooked ravioli. After cooking for another 5 minutes, take it off the stove. Put the ravioli on plates, pour garlic yogurt on top and serve with mint and plenty of sumac. Enjoy your meal.

For Diet Hamburger recipe; Fry the hamburger patties in a Teflon pan without adding oil. While the hamburger patties are cooking, spread a teaspoon of ketchup on a slice of white toast. Lay the pickled cucumbers on top of the ketchup you apply. Combine the lettuce leaves into a funnel and put the hamburger patty you heated and a thin slice of low-fat cheddar cheese inside. When the cheddar starts to melt among the lettuce, put the lettuce-wrapped meatballs and cheese on the toast you prepared. Your six lettuce diet burgers are ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mushroom Meat Saute recipe; dice the meat. Cook in a pressure cooker until soft. Finely chop the onions and peppers. Saute the onions and peppers in a deep pan. Add the boiled meat on it. Add the chopped mushrooms on it and sauté. Saute a little more after adding the last seasonings. Sauteed Meat with Mushrooms is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For chicken tenderloin recipe; Mix the spices and oil well in a bowl. Mix the chickens with this mixture. Cook on low heat without adding oil in a ceramic pan. Chicken tenderloin is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Whole Grain Toast recipe with Tomato and Feta Cheese; Spread the feta cheese on the whole grain bread. Place the tomatoes you sliced into circles on it. Add thyme and cover the other bread. Wait before pressing it from the toaster. Whole Grain Toast with Tomato and Feta Cheese is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chocolate Cake recipe; Beat sugar and eggs until creamy. Add the oil and milk to the mixture. Add the flour and whisk the mixture until homogeneous. Add the baking powder and vanilla. Then add the cocoa. Grate the chocolate or break it into small pieces. Add walnuts and chocolate. Add the last 3 tablespoons of boiled water to the mixture and mix well. After oiling the inside of the cake mold a little, pour the filling you prepared. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 40 minutes. Chocolate cake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Curd Cheese Pie recipe; Whisk the milk, egg, oil and yoghurt well in a bowl and turn it into a sauce. Finely chop the parsley leaves and mix the curd cheese with the parsley in another bowl. Cool the phyllo on the baking tray, leaving the skirts out, pour a little of the sauce on it and spread it all over. Spread another layer of dough on it. Pour a little of the sauce and rub it all over. Add the curd cheese and parsley mixture on it. Do the same for each layer of dough. After putting the last layer, cover the outside skirts and pour the remaining sauce and wet it thoroughly with sauce. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees until golden brown. Curd cheese pie is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Curry Sauce Chicken recipe; Slice the chicken into cubes. Add oil in the pan and cook until the water is absorbed. In another bowl, fry the flour and butter until the smell of flour comes out. Add milk slowly after removing from heat. Add the water after the mixture and add the spices last. Mix from all transactions. Put it on fire last. And mix it until it reaches the consistency of custard. Add the sauce over the chickens and cook until it's done. Chicken with curry sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
For the Bacon Egg recipe; Fry the bacon in the oil you melted in the pan. Crack the egg after turning it upside down. Eggs with bacon is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Meat Pancake recipe; Grate the onions, finely chop the parsley, add salt, pepper and ground beef and fry in a pan. Leave this mortar you prepared for 10 minutes until it cools down. Lay one of the phyllo on the counter. Fold the 20 cm piece upwards from one side of the dough you have laid on the counter. Put a quarter of the ground beef mixture on the fold. Close the side edges of the dough first, then the top part, and get a shape like a bundle. Do the same with the other phyllo dough. Heat a wide, thick-bottomed steel skillet over the fire. Put the butter in the heated pan and melt it. After the butter melts, put the dough you prepared and cook it on medium heat until the front and back sides turn pink. The minced meat flatbread is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Potato Pancake recipe; First, boil the potatoes in a pot. Then peel the potatoes in a bowl and mash them with a fork. Add the grated onion, tomato paste, salt, pepper and olive oil to the potatoes and mix. Lay one of the phyllo dough on the counter and, since you have prepared it in the middle, put 1/4 of it and wrap it around the edges in the form of a bundle. Do the same for the other yufkas. Put the sunflower oil in a teflon pan and heat the oil on the fire. Cook the pancakes you prepared in the pan until the top and bottom turn pink. Potato pancakes are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the calamari recipe; Rub the extracted squids thoroughly in salt, baking soda, milk and lemon water. Leave it in the fridge for 3-4 hours. After straining, dip in flour and deep fry in oil. Calamari is ready to serve.

For the Spinach Pancake recipe; Finely chop the onions. Heat oil in a pan and fry the onions in this oil. Add salt when onions are browned. When the onions turn pink, add the cooked spinach and egg, mix for a few more minutes and turn off the heat. Keep it aside until the stuffing you have prepared has cooled down. When the spinach stuff cools down, divide it evenly into the phyllo and place it in the middle of the phyllo and fold it into a bundle. Then, put a tablespoon of sunflower oil in a pan and fry the spinach pancakes you prepared in the pan until they turn pink. Spinach pancake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the puff pastry recipe; Mix milk, egg and oil in a bowl. Lay a sheet of dough on the tray. Apply this mixture on it. Divide the dough into 2. Mix the cheese and parsley in a bowl. Pour this mixture on the dough as a mortar. Wrap both phyllo as a roll and place them one after the other in the shape of roses on the tray. Do the same for each phyllo. Brush egg on the puff pastry. Sprinkle with black cumin and sesame seeds. Bake in a 180 degree oven until golden brown. Blueberry pie is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Cheese Pita recipe; Take the flour in the kneading bowl and knead it in the middle, add oil. Warm the water, add the yeast to the warm water, melt it and pour it into the middle of the flour. Add sugar and salt and knead the dough. When the dough reaches a non-sticky consistency, cover it and let it ferment. While the dough is waiting, chop the onions into small pieces in a hollow bowl for the inside of the pita. Then put the cheese in this coarse and mix the cheese and onions with the help of your hand. Divide the dough into ten equal parts and roll them. Roll each one out with a rolling pin. Put the inner mortar you prepared in the middle of the dough you rolled out and fold it so that the middle of the sides is slightly open. After making sure that the ends are well covered, place them on the middle grill of the oven, which is preheated at 200 degrees. When the top is browned, take it out of the oven and apply butter on it with the help of a brush. Cheese Pita is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Potato Pita recipe; Put the flour, sugar, salt, water, 1 teaspoon of salt, yogurt and fresh yeast in a bowl and knead. When it reaches a non-sticky consistency, close your mouth and wait for 20-25 minutes. While preparing the dough, peel the boiled potatoes. Mash the peeled potatoes in a bowl with a fork. Chop the onions small. Put sunflower oil in a pan and heat it. Put the onion and tomato paste in the heated oil and fry it lightly. Then add salt, pepper and black pepper, mix a few times and turn off the heat. While you're waiting for it to cool, make egg-sized balls from the dough you've been waiting for and roll it out with a rolling pin. After rolling out the dough, add the onion mixture you prepared in the pan on the mashed potatoes and mix. Put it in the middle of the dough you have made from this mortar and fold it so that the middle is open from the sides. fold it. Place the pitas on the middle grill of the oven, which is preheated at 180 degrees. Take them out of the oven when they are browned. Potato Pita is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
For the mushroom omelet recipe; Saute the mushrooms that you cleaned and cut into strips in a pan. Crack the egg on it and add the salt. Mushroom omelet is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
For the omelet recipe; melt the butter in the pan. Pour the beaten egg into the pan after the oil is hot. Add the spices. Omelet is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the candlestick recipe; Separate the yolks and whites of the eggs. Open the middle of the flour you added to a bowl and add the egg yolks. Add other ingredients. And knead until it thickens. Take walnut-sized pieces from the dough and make a ring and place them on the tray. Brush the egg white on the bagels and sprinkle with muffins or sesame seeds, if desired. Bake in a 200 degree oven. The candlestick is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
For the onion omelet recipe; finely chop the onions. Saute the onions in an oiled pan. Add the seasonings to it. Crack the egg. Onion Eggs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the white cheese omelet recipe; Crack the egg in a bowl. Grate the cheese on it. Mince the parsley and add to the mixture. Add the mixture to the oil that is heated in the pan. White cheese omelet is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Pita with Kushbassi recipe; Put the flour, salt, yeast in a deep bowl and mix. Knead by slowly adding warm water to these mixed ingredients. When you get a soft dough that does not stick to the hand, divide it into 6 equal parts and roll it. While the dough is resting, finely chop the onion, pepper and tomato for the inside of the pita and put them in a bowl. Then add the cubed meat, olive oil, 1 teaspoon of salt, thyme and black pepper and mix some more. Roll out the 6 pieces of dough you have kept in a thin and long rolling pin. Put the flaked mortar in the middle. Fold the dough on which you put your mortar so that the top is slightly open from the edges. After making sure that the ends are completely covered, place the pitas you prepared on the middle grill of the oven preheated to 200 degrees. When the pitas are browned, take them out of the oven and brush them with a little butter with a brush. Cubed Pita is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal

For Mixed Vegetable Recipe in Oven Bag; Wash the vegetables thoroughly. Remove the seeds from the peppers. Cut the zucchini into thin rings. Chop the mushrooms and peppers into thick rings. Mix the vegetables with olive oil and spices and place in the baking bag. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees.

For the Baked Zucchini Chips recipe; Cut the zucchini into 1 cm thick rounds. Crush the meat and mix it with the spices. Soak the zucchini in water first. Then find this mix back and forth. Line up on baking paper. Spray oil on it. Bake in the oven at 220 degrees. Baked Zucchini Chips are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mengen Soup recipe; First of all, remove the stones from the bulgur and wash the bulgur. Soak the washed bulgur in hot water until they are boiled. While the bulgur is waiting, put the butter in a saucepan and melt it. Finely chop the onion and fry it in butter. Add the flour and continue frying. After frying, add the tomato paste. Then add water and mix. Add the broth and continue mixing. Finally, drain the boiled bulgur and add it to the pot with the spices and mix. Mengen Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the SDM Spinach and Mushroom Pasta recipe; Cook the SDM pasta according to the recipe. Saute the mushrooms in a wok with 1 teaspoon of olive oil. Add the spinach leaves when they are soft. Then add the boiled pasta and add the spices. SDM Spinach and Mushroom Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the SDM Zucchini Basil Pasta recipe; Cook the SDM pasta according to the recipe. Saute the finely chopped zucchini in a wok with 1 teaspoon of olive oil. Add basil leaves when soft. Then add the pasta and seasonings. SDM Zucchini and Basil Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mexican Style Chicken recipe; Peel the skin off the chicken thighs. Wipe the peeled thighs with a paper napkin, dry them and turn them in flour so that they are lightly floured. After flouring the thighs, put 3 tablespoons of oil in a deep, wide and non-flammable saucepan and fry the thighs for 6-8 minutes by turning them over high heat. Take the fried thighs out of the pot. Finely chop the onions, crush the garlic, cumin, hot pepper paste, salt, pepper and cocoa into the pot you use for frying the thighs. Mix these ingredients a little and add 1/2 tea glass of water and oil and cook until the ingredients are soft. Add the chopped tomatoes, tomato sauce and chicken broth, mix and boil a little more. Then put the chicken legs in it and cover it and continue to boil slowly for 40-45 minutes until the legs are soft. When the consistency is not very liquid, turn off the heat and wait for a while. Mexican Style Chicken is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. Note: If you wish, it can be served by garnishing with arugula.

For the Yoghurt Ravioli recipe; Take the flour in a deep bowl and open the middle in the shape of a pool. Add the egg and a teaspoon of salt to the middle and gradually take the flour and start kneading. Add water slowly while kneading. Continue kneading after adding water. When you get a dough that is harder than the consistency of the earlobe, stop kneading and let the dough rest. While resting the dough, start making your stuffing. Grate the onion on the minced meat, add salt, pepper and tomato paste and knead. After preparing the inner mortar, divide the rested dough into large balls that you can roll and roll them into 1-2 cm thick, not too thin. Cut into small squares and place small pieces of minced meat in them. Close the ravioli stuffed with minced meat in a triangle shape. Put these closed ravioli on a floured tray. Sprinkle flour on the ravioli on the tray from time to time so that they do not stick together. Boil water in a saucepan and add a teaspoon of salt to it. Boil the ravioli you prepared in salted water. After it is boiled, remove it with the help of a strainer and let it cool. While the ravioli is cooling, put the yogurt in a bowl and grate the garlic into it. Add the cooled ravioli to the yoghurt mixture and mix it so that it does not get crushed. Manti with Yoghurt is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken caesar salad recipe; Wash the belly salad, lettuce and divide it equally into two salad bowls. Cut the edges of the toast breads and dice them. Put the butter in a pan and fry the sliced toast breads. Slice the chicken breasts thin and long. Put a tablespoon of olive oil in a separate pan, fry the chicken cut into thin slices until lightly browned. Divide the crusty breads and chicken pieces on the salads. For the chicken caesar salad dressing; Prepare the sauce by mixing two tablespoons of olive oil, mayonnaise, mustard, lemon juice, crushed garlic, pickled capers, salt and pepper in a blender. Pour the Caesar dressing you prepared on the salads and eat it everywhere. Finally, grate the Parmesan cheese on them. Chicken Caesar Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pumpkin fainted recipe; Saute onions, garlic, carrots and parsley in a pan. Add 6 tablespoons of oil to another pot. Cut the zucchini in half like a boat. Cook the arachnids in the oil until they are soft. Place the stuffing you prepared into the pumpkin. Cover the tomatoes. Add water and let it cook. The zucchini is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Fruit and Herbal Bar recipe; crush the banana. Then add olive oil, milk, honey and oat and mix. Finally, add the coconut and the apples you cut into small cubes and mix again. Put the mixture you get on the oil paper by taking pieces. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 15 minutes. You can consume a can (200 ml.) of low-fat milk and a slice at snacks. The fruit and herb bar is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal!

For the mushroom roasted red pepper omelet recipe; chop the mushrooms and peppers julienne. Saute in the pan to which you add oil. Crack the egg on it. Mushroom and roasted red pepper omelet is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Whole Wheat Pasta with Curd Cheese; Boil the pasta in water for 8 minutes. Take the boiled pasta on the serving plate and add the curd cheese on it. Whole wheat pasta with curd cheese is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the yogurt recipe; First roast the eggplants and peel them. Take it in a bowl and mash it well with the help of a fork. Add 1 teaspoon of salt to it and mix well. Then add the yoghurt to this eggplant and mix well. Add paprika to the olive oil you have heated in another pan and after a short while, take it off the stove. After taking the eggplant with yogurt on a plate, drizzle olive oil on it. Your yogurt is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the chia seed omelet recipe; Mix milk and chia seeds in a bowl. Wait until the chia seeds absorb the milk and form a gel. In another bowl, add the eggs, salt and whisk. Add the gelled chia seeds to the mixture. Pour the mixture into the oil you have heated in a pan. Throw the cheddar on it. Chia seed omelette is ready to serve, enjoy your meal.

For the Curd Cheese Chard recipe; Wash the biceps thoroughly. After chopping the onions and carrots into cubes, fry them in a pan with oil. Add the chard leaves and garlic on it. Close the lid of the pot. Cook on low heat. After it cools down, serve with curd cheese on it by adding the house chili peppers. Chard with curd cheese is ready to serve, enjoy your meal.

For the Plum Puree recipe; Wash and peel the plums thoroughly. Remove the seeds and chop finely. Steam until soft. After adding the yogurt and banana, pass it through the robot. Throw in the ice. Serve cold. Plum puree is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Meaty Fresh Beans recipe; Chop the meat into cubes. Then put the meat in a pot. Cook on medium heat until the water evaporates. Add the oil and the chopped onions and fry them. Add the tomato paste and powdered pepper and mix. Add the beans and tomatoes you picked to the pot. Add water to cover it a little bit. Cook it by adding the salt that is close to cooking. Beans with meat are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Almond Dessert recipe; First, make a soft dough using eggs, yogurt, oil, baking powder, flour and 5 tablespoons of semolina. Break off small pieces of dough and shape into almonds. Find the given shapes on the remaining semolina. Then arrange them on the greased tray. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 20-25 minutes. Boil 5 cups of sugar with 5 cups of water in a saucepan until it thickens. After turning off the heat, add the lemon juice and let it cool. Pour the cold syrup over the hot dough. Your Almond Dessert is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Almond Sherbet recipe; Remove the pumpkin seeds and put 2 cups of ground almonds in a hollow bowl. Add milk, cardamom, pumpkin seeds, rose water, saffron and granulated sugar and mix with a blender. Heat the syrup a little and put it in a glass container with a lid. Cover with cling film and refrigerate for 1 day. You can filter and serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Egg Leek recipe; Chop the leeks and sauté a little in oil. After adding salt and pepper on it, break the egg. After the eggs are cooked, distribute the chili pepper on top and serve. Fried Egg Leek is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Herb Pancakes Recipe; finely chop the parsley and dill. Mix all the ingredients in a bowl. Pour the oil into the frying pan with the help of a ladle. Herbed pancakes are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Baked Cheese Tomato recipe; Chop the tomatoes into rounds. After blending the cheese and thyme on it, divide it. Throw it in the oven. Tomatoes with cheese in the oven are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.
For the Rice Soup recipe; put the broth in a pot. When the broth boils, add the rice, grated tomato, parsley and butter. Cook until the rice is soft. Rice Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Lentil Zucchini Meal recipe; Soak green lentils overnight. Drain the wash. Finely chop the onions and zucchini. Put the olive oil in a saucepan and heat it. Add the onions and fry them. Then add the tomato paste and fry some more. Add the green lentils and water to it and let it boil. When the water boils, add the zucchini and cook for 25 minutes. Add salt and mix. After mixing, crush the garlic and mix with lemon juice. You've got the sauce, add it to the pot, mix it a few times and close the bottom of the pot. Lentil Zucchini Meal is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the peach cold tea recipe; Boil 5 glasses of water. When you put the water on the stove to boil, add the sliced lemons to the sugar and wait. After the water boils, add the sugar and lemons to the boiling water. Add mint leaves and tea bags to the water. Close the lid and wait for it to brew like this. After removing the skins and seeds of 2 peaches, blend them in a blender until they become puree. Strain the tea and add the peach puree to the mixture. Add cold water to reduce its density. After putting it in the refrigerator, serve it with ice and garnish with the remaining 1 peach. Peach iced tea is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the salty patisserie cookie recipe; Thoroughly knead the granulated sugar, egg whites and oil in a bowl. Add 3 cups of flour, baking powder and black cumin and continue kneading the mixture. Add flour and knead until you have a medium hard dough that does not stick to the hand. Roll out the dough with a rolling pin to 1 cm thickness. Give it the shape you want. Lay on wax paper. Brush the egg yolk on it. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven until lightly browned. Salty patisserie cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Hazelnut Biscuit Cake recipe; Cook by mixing all the custard ingredients except vanilla so that there are no lumps. After it boils, take it off the heat and add the vanilla and whisk. Lightly moisten the bottom of a medium-sized pyrex with a little milk and place a layer of biscuits on it. Pour a third of the custard over it. Smash the hazelnuts with a hard object. Pour one third of the crushed hazelnuts and do this in the same way, with 3 layers of biscuits and 3 layers of pudding. Then let it cool in the fridge. Hazelnut Biscuit Cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the curd dessert recipe with strawberry sauce; In a deep bowl, mix the curd cheese, milk and powdered sugar. Add whipped cream, walnuts and cinnamon. Whisk until it thickens. Extract half of the strawberries and add them to the mix along with the coconut. Divide the mixture into bowls and put them in the freezer. Puree the remaining strawberries in a blender. Cook in a pan with starch and sugar until thickened. Share this mixture on the bowls you put in the refrigerator. Wait 3 hours in the refrigerator. Before serving, garnish the curd dessert with strawberry sauce with strawberries and pistachios. Enjoy your meal.

For the Fish Grill recipe; Wash the bonito fish that you have removed with plenty of water. Rub the fish you have washed with oil and salt and open the fins of the fish and put them on the tray. Peel the potatoes, slice them into rings and arrange them around the fish. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 30 minutes. Fish Grill is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Steamed Bonito recipe; Slice the cleaned acorn into finger-thick slices. Peel the onions and cut them into round slices about the same thickness as the fish slices. Slice the tomatoes and lemon in the same way. Place the lemon slices in a baking dish and arrange the bonito, onion and tomato slices alternately on it. Sprinkle black pepper and salt all over. Drizzle olive oil over it. Arrange the bay leaves on the 2 sides of the pots. Cover the bowl with aluminum foil or greaseproof paper and let it cook in a preheated 200 degree oven. After 15-20 minutes, take out the container and take the paper on it and cook it again for another 5-10 minutes. Bonito Steamed is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Trout Steamed Recipe; Cut the cleaned trout horizontally. Peel the onions and cut them into round slices. Slice the tomatoes and lemon in the same way. Place the lemon slices in a baking dish and arrange the trout fillets, onion and tomato slices alternately on it. Sprinkle black pepper and salt all over. Drizzle olive oil over it. Arrange the bay leaves on the 2 sides of the pots. Cover the bowl with aluminum foil or greaseproof paper and let it cook in a preheated 200 degree oven. After 15-20 minutes, take out the container and take the paper on it and cook it again for another 5-10 minutes. Trout Steamed is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Anchovy Pan recipe; Clean the inside and outside of the fish and wash it with plenty of water. Pour flour on a large tray and flour the fish in this tray with flour all over. Put the oil in a pan and arrange the fish with the tails in the middle and the heads towards the edge of the pan. Burn and fry the stove. After one side is cooked, turn the fish with the help of a wide and flat plate and fry the other side. After browning on both sides, place a wide and flat plate in the rim of the pan in the same way and transfer the fish to the plate. Fried anchovy is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Creamy Tuna Pasta recipe; boil the pasta. While the pasta is cooking, to prepare the sauce, put oil in a pan and then chop the peppers and fry them. After the peppers are roasted, add the tuna and cream and fry some more. Then chop the olives into small pieces and add them. Add the salt after you turn it off. Drain the boiled pasta and put it in a deep bowl. Add the sauce to the pasta and mix well. Creamy Tuna Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Baked Fish recipe; Wash the bonito fish that you have removed with plenty of water. Rub the fish you have washed with oil and salt and open the fins of the fish and put them on the tray. Peel the onions, slice them into rings and arrange them around the fish. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 30 minutes. Baked Fish is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Fried Anchovy with Breadcrumbs; Clean the inside and outside of the fish and wash it with plenty of water. Pour flour on a large tray and flour the fish in this tray with flour all over. Put the oil in a pan and arrange the fish with the tails in the middle and the heads towards the edge of the pan. Burn and fry the stove. After one side is cooked, turn the fish with the help of a wide and flat plate and fry the other side. After browning on both sides, place a wide and flat plate in the rim of the pan in the same way and transfer the fish to the plate. Anchovy Fried with Breadcrumbs is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Roast Trout recipe; Clean the inside and outside of the fish and wash it with plenty of water. Cut the fish in the middle to open like a leaf, pour flour on a large tray and flour the fish in this tray with flour all over. Put the oil in a pan and heat the oil. Fry the fish on both sides in oil. After browning on both sides, transfer them to plates and sprinkle salt on them. Trout Roast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Baked Mushroom Shrimp recipe; peel the garlic, cut the large mushrooms into quarters and the small ones in half. Put the garlic and mushrooms in the baking dish. Add the thawed shrimp on it. Sprinkle with salt, pepper and cayenne pepper. Lastly, pour the olive oil all over it. Put in the oven preheated to 180-200 degrees. Bake for about 40-45 minutes. Baked Shrimp with Mushrooms is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the anchovy recipe; Arrange the anchovies that you sorted and washed into my debt. Chop the onion rings and tomatoes on it. After adding oil and salt, bake in the oven at 175 degrees for 25-30 minutes. Enjoy your meal.

For the Anchovy Meatballs recipe; Peel the skins of 1 kg boneless anchovies lightly, chop them like minced meat with a knife and put them in a bowl. Add salt, pepper, cayenne pepper. Crack the egg on it, grate the onion. Finely chop the parsley and add. Add half a glass of flour and 4 slices of stale bread and knead. Break off walnut-sized pieces and form a flat shape in the palm of your hand. Cook the Anchovy Meatballs you prepared in a pan with very little oil. Anchovy Meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for Chicken with Mushrooms and Bechamel Sauce; Spread the boiled peas and the carrots that you cut into small pieces in a debt. Then chop the boiled chicken breast coarsely over the peas and carrots. For the bechamel sauce; First, melt the butter in a pan and fry the flour. After roasting, add two glasses of milk, spices and salt. Stir constantly until you get the consistency of sauce so that there are no lumps in the flour. Pour the ready-made béchamel sauce over my pyrex. Grate the cheddar and finely chop the mushrooms. Bake in the preheated oven for a while until the cheddar is melted and browned. Enjoy your meal.

For Creamy Mushroom Soup recipe; Put the oil and butter in a saucepan and add the onions and fry them. After the onions are roasted, add the grated garlic and cover the pot and let it cook for another five minutes. After five minutes, wash and finely chop the mushrooms and add them to the pot. Continue cooking for another ten minutes. When the mushrooms release their water, add the flour and mix so that the ingredients are completely mixed with each other. Then add boiling water and continue mixing so that there are no lumps. Add salt and pepper and leave the lid of the pot half open and cook for 20 minutes. Then add the cream, mix and cook for another 5 minutes. Creamy Mushrooms are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Fried Mushroom recipe; Beat the egg, flour, starch and salt until smooth. Wash and dry the mushrooms and cut them in half or quarters depending on their size. Find the sauce you have created in a deep bowl. Put the oil in a pan and heat it. When the oil is hot, fry the mantas that you sauced in oil. Mushroom Fries are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Baked Chicken Mushroom recipe; Finely chop the mushrooms, dice the chicken breast and other ingredients finely and put them on the baking tray. Add tomato paste, oil, salt, pepper and thyme, mix it with your hand and let it cook in the oven at 170 degrees. When it's almost cooked, grate the cheddar cheese and sprinkle it back in the oven. Cook until it turns golden brown. Baked Chicken Mushroom is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Çörekotu Fırın Mücver recipe; Grate the zucchini and drain the water well. Finely chop the fresh mint, garlic and spring onions. Mix all the ingredients and bring it to the consistency of boza. Transfer the mixture to the greased baking dish. Bake in the preheated oven for about 30 minutes. Çörekotu Fırın Mücver is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for stuffed tomatoes with meat; Soak the rice in a bowl of hot water. While the rice is swelling, finely chop the onions. Put the minced meat, chopped onions and vegetable oil in a bowl and knead. Drain the rice that you soaked in hot water before, add the rice and knead again. Finally, add salt, pepper, tomato paste and continue kneading. When the ingredients are well mixed, let them rest and cut the bunch of 10 tomatoes in the form of lids. Carve out and clean the insides of the tomatoes you cut like a zucchini. Put the insides of the tomatoes in another clean container. Fill the inside of the tomatoes you cleaned with minced meat and close the lid with the tomatoes you cut. Put the stuffed stuff you prepared in a deep pot. After putting them all together, add water up to half of the pot. Pour the tomato pulp that you took out of the tomatoes on it. Cook with the lid closed for 25-30 minutes. Stuffed Tomatoes with Meat is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Bulgur Tomato Soup recipe; Put the oil and tomato paste in the pan and fry the tomato paste. Grate the tomatoes, add them to the pot with the spices and fry the tomatoes a little. Then add the bulgur and fry some more. After frying, add water, mix, leave the lid ajar and cook for 15 minutes. Bulgur Tomato Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Whole Wheat Bulgur Pilaf recipe with Tomatoes; Chop the oil and onions into cubes and put them in the pan and fry them. Peel the skins of the tomatoes, cut them into cubes and add them to the onions you have fried and mix. Rinse the bulgur, add it to the pot and mix. After frying the bulgur for a bit, add salt and enough water and cook it on the fire with the lid closed until the water is absorbed.
