Take the broth in a normal pot and add the meat to it, warm the seasoning you have prepared and mix it quickly and add it to the soup. Stir until it boils. Keep the boiling soup on the stove for another 5-10 minutes, then turn off the heat. In a small saucepan, melt the butter and add the ground pepper and fry it. Pour the ground pepper butter into the soup and stir. Beef Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pancake recipe; Soak chickpeas and wheat in separate containers overnight. Put the wheat and chickpeas in a pressure cooker, add enough water to cover them by 2 fingers and cook until they are completely soft. Boil the chicken breast in a separate pot until tender. Separate the skin of the boiled chicken and finely chop it. Drain the wheat and chickpeas and put them in a saucepan. Take 2 glasses of the water in which the chicken was boiled and add to the pot with the wheat and chickpeas. Stir continuously on low heat, pressing down with a wooden spoon. After stirring for 5 minutes, add the previously shredded chicken breast. Stir in the same way until the food begins to creep. Add salt and pepper, mix, then remove from heat. Melt butter in a pan. When it starts to sizzle, add the ground pepper, mix and remove from the heat. Pour the oily and chili powder sauce over the food. The pancake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Cereal Grape Cookie recipe; Put the flour, olive oil, baking soda, honey, raisins, cinnamon and crushed walnuts and hazelnuts in a deep bowl. Mix all the ingredients well and knead. Squeeze 2 drops of lemon into the resulting dough and leave it for half an hour at room temperature. Then roll out the dough with a rolling pin and shape it with cookie cutters or by hand. Bake in the oven at 175 degrees for 10-12 minutes until they are browned. Grain and raisin cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the plain pastry recipe; Put the whites of 2 eggs, milk, sugar, yeast, oil, margarine and salt in a bowl and knead. Slowly add flour to the kneaded mixture and continue kneading. When it reaches the consistency of the earlobe, cover the dough and leave it in a warm environment for 40-45 minutes. After the dough has rested, break off pieces slightly larger than the size of a walnut and roll them out. Do this until all the dough is gone. Put the dough pieces you prepared on the baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Preheat the oven at 180 degrees. Brush the egg yolk over the pastries. Bake in the preheated oven for 15-20 minutes. Plain pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken pancake recipe; Cut the chicken breasts thinly crosswise. Beat the egg in a bowl and place on a flat plate. In a separate bowl, mix the salt, ground pepper and breadcrumbs. Dip the chicken breasts into the egg and then into the breadcrumb mixture. Flour both sides. Fry both sides and back in a little oil with the lid of the pan closed. Breaded chicken is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the whole wheat cheese pastry; For the dough, break the egg white into a bowl and whisk. Continue whisking while adding the oil. Add the flour, yogurt, salt and baking powder. Knead well until you have a dough as soft as an earlobe. Cover it with a damp cloth and let it rest for half an hour. Mash the cheese with a fork for the filling. Add finely chopped parsley and mix. Pieces slightly larger than walnuts are cut from the dough. Roll it out to the size of a tea plate with the help of a rolling pin. Put 1 teaspoon of filling in the rolled dough and roll it in your palm. Place on a baking paper lined tray. Brush them with egg yolk and sprinkle with sesame seeds. Bake in an unheated 150 degree oven for 40-45 minutes until golden brown. Whole wheat cheese pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the wholemeal pastry recipe with oat; Put all the ingredients in a deep bowl and mix well. Preheat the oven at 180 degrees. Break off small pieces of dough and roll them out. Line the baking tray with greaseproof paper and line up these pieces. Bake in the preheated oven for 20-25 minutes. Whole wheat pastry with oat is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the sweetened fresh fruit compote recipe; Put the water in a deep pot and boil it. Peel the skins of the fruits and cut them into cubes. Throw the chopped fruits into the boiling water. Cook for 2-3 minutes and then remove from the heat. Finally, add the sweetener and leave the pot on the table to warm up, then rest for half an hour in the refrigerator to cool completely. Sweetened fresh fruit mix compote servie is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the soy flour cookie recipe; Put 1 cup of brown sugar and soybean oil in a large bowl. Mix it well. Add the nut butter and soy milk. Keep mixing gently. Add the vanilla and beat with the mixer for 3-4 minutes. Crack the egg, add it and beat for another minute. Put the flour and soy flour in a bowl and mix. Add the baking soda, salt and mix. Slowly put the flour mixture into the bowl that is whipped with the mixer and beat it with a low-temperature mixer. After adding all the flour, beat for another 3 minutes. Preheat the oven to 190 degrees. Lay greaseproof paper on the baking tray and take 1 tablespoon sized pieces of the cookie dough, pour them on the tray. Add in the soy nuts. Bake in the preheated oven for 10-15 minutes. Soy flour cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Turmeric Chicken Soup recipe; Put the chicken leg and water in a pot and after the chicken is boiled, drain the water and take it to a separate place. Throw the vermicelli into the chicken broth and boil until the vermicelli is cooked. Meanwhile, remove the skin from the chicken, shred it, transfer it into the boiling vermicelli and cook it all together for 5 minutes. After turning off the stove, add salt, pepper and turmeric. Turmeric Chicken Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For spaghetti and meatballs recipe; First, to prepare the meatballs, grate the onion, beat the garlic, finely chop the parsley. Put the ground meat, garlic, onion, black pepper, egg, salt, stale breadcrumbs, parsley and red pepper in a deep bowl and knead until it reaches a non-sticky consistency. Cut off pieces of the size you want and shape them flat. Grease only the bottom of the Teflon pan. Arrange the meatballs and cook them over low heat, turning them occasionally. While following the meatballs, put water in a pot and when the water boils, add the pasta to the pot and boil it for 8-9 minutes. Drain the cooked pasta. If there is any water left in the pot where you boiled the pasta, pour it out and put the oil in the pot and heat it. Throw the pasta into the heated oil and cook for 3-4 minutes. Take the spaghetti on a serving plate, put the meatballs you cooked on it. Spaghetti and meatballs are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the spicy grilled meatball recipe; Grate the onion and garlic, finely chop the parsley. Put it in a deep bowl and add the other ingredients and knead well. After preparing the mortar, shape it and let it rest in the refrigerator for 2 hours if you have time. Grill after resting. Hot grilled meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.
For the popcorn (no oil) recipe; Put the corn in the microwave or popcorn maker. Continue cooking until the corns burst. Then add salt. Popcorn is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the ginger flu soup recipe; clean the carrot, peel the potato and ginger and grate all three. Wash the parsley stalks with plenty of water and chop coarsely. Pour oil into the pan, add the carrot and potato and saute. For her dressing; Put the flour and butter in another pot and fry. Add 1 glass of water into it and stir constantly with a whisk, avoiding clumping and whisking. Then slowly pour the potato and carrot mixture you prepared into the flour mixture. Heat the salt and the remaining 2 glasses of water and add the hot water. Finally, add the grated fresh ginger and mix. Divide into bowls and garnish with chopped parsley. Ginger flu soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Hazelnut Cinnamon Cookies recipe; Melt the margarine in a pan without heating it too much. Put the melted margarine, oil, 4 tablespoons of powdered sugar, flour, baking powder and vanilla in a deep bowl and knead. Then add the hazelnut kernels and continue kneading until the hazelnuts are mixed. Knead until you get a non-sticky dough. Peel off walnut-sized pieces on a greased tray and place them on the tray. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees until golden brown. After taking the cookie out of the oven, wait for it to cool a bit and sprinkle the cinnamon on the cookies. Hazelnut Cinnamon Cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the homemade cookie recipe; First, grate the rind of the oranges. Then melt the butter in a pan without being too hot. In a large bowl, take sugar, eggs, oil, melted and cooled butter, yogurt and orange peels. Add the juice of half an orange. Mix the ingredients thoroughly without using a mixer. Add the vanilla and baking powder to the ingredients. Then slowly add the flour. Knead until you get as soft and non-sticky dough as possible. Shape the cookies into a round shape and place them on the tray. Bake in a preheated oven at 240 degrees until golden brown. Check often while cooking. Homemade cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the carrot and potato salad; Boil the potatoes and grate them. Grate the carrots. Chop the pickles into small pieces. Squeeze the carrot lightly so that it does not release its juice. Mix the potato, carrot, and gherkin in a large bowl. In a small bowl, beat the garlic and add the mayonnaise and yogurt and mix. Pour the sauce you prepared into the potato mixture. Mix a few times with the help of a spoon and pour it on the serving plate. Carrot and potato salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For wholemeal pasta recipe; First, put water and salt in a saucepan and bring the water to a boil. After the water boils, pour the pasta on top and cook for about 10-15 minutes until it has a soft consistency. Then take it off the stove and pour it into a strainer. Whole wheat pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pan egg recipe; Put the oil in the pan and melt it on low heat. Crack the eggs into the oil so that the yolks do not fall apart. After adding the spices by sprinkling on it, close the glass lid of the pan and cook it on high heat until the egg white is cooked. The fried eggs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the tea (with whole milk) recipe; Put 1 glass of water in the pot and boil it. Add the tea to the boiling water and let it brew for 15 minutes. While the tea is brewing, heat the milk. Add from brewed tea to heated milk. Tea (with whole milk) is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the tea (with whole milk, low sugar) recipe; Boil the water and add the tea to it and let it brew. Infuse for about 15 minutes. While the tea is brewing, heat the milk. Add the brewed tea to the heated milk. Add sugar and mix. Serve in cups. Tea (with whole milk, low sugar) is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the fruity iced tea recipe; Add the fruits to 3 glasses of hot water and infuse for 5 minutes. Separate the fruits from the water with a strainer and leave the brewed water at room temperature for 30 minutes. Add cold water to the water you have been waiting for and mix. Fill the glasses with ice, then add enough tea to remain 2 inches from the top. Garnish with mint leaves and serve. Fruity iced tea is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

for oat extract soup; Extract the oat and put it in cold water and cook on low heat for 15-20 minutes. Put the milk in a saucepan and heat it. Take some of the warmed milk. Crack the egg into a plate and whisk. Whisk the separated milk and slowly add it to the egg. Add the soaked oat mixture to the remaining milk in the pot and mash well. Then continue cooking on low heat, stirring. Slowly add the egg that you mixed with the milk close to boiling to the pot. Finally, add the salt and butter and continue cooking, stirring. After 2-3 minutes of boiling, turn off the heat and divide into bowls. oat extract soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the oven-baked carp recipe; wash the carp, take it in a deep pyrex tray. Crush the garlic and mix in a small bowl with all the other spices and tomato paste. Add water to it and get a sauce. Pour this sauce over the fish. Drizzle olive oil on it, cover it and let it marinate for 1 hour. Peel the onion and quarter it. Divide the hot peppers into 2 or 3 large pieces and lay them on the sides of the fish. Bake in an oven at 250 degrees for 45 minutes until well browned. Serve hot. Carp in the oven is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the noodle casserole recipe; First, heat the casserole on the stove, then dice the meat into medium sized cubes and fry the meat a little until it releases its juices. Add the oil, chopped onion, chopped peppers into it. When the onions and peppers are slightly roasted and softened, grate the tomatoes and add them and fry for a while. Add some water and cook until the meat is tender. In another pan, stir-fry the barley noodle with oil until golden brown. Add the roasted vermicelli into the meat and add 3 glasses of water, some salt and pepper to the lowest setting. Let it cook in a covered casserole. Stir occasionally with a wooden spoon. When the meat is thoroughly cooked and the barley vermicelli has absorbed its water, close the bottom of the casserole and cover it tightly with a foil and let it brew. Since the casserole will cool slowly, it will continue to cook after removing it from the fire. The noodle casserole is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for chicken legs in the oven; First, to prepare the sauce for the chickens, put the oil, tomato paste, salt, pepper and thyme in a deep bowl and mix. Then, cover all sides of the chicken legs with this sauce, wrap them in cling wrap and put them in the fridge. Let it rest in the fridge for an hour if possible. Grease my medium-sized borer. Lay the chicken thighs on it. Drizzle the remaining sauce in the bowl over the chicken mulberries. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees until golden brown. Chicken legs in the oven are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the wing skewer recipe; Mix yoghurt, tomato paste, black pepper and oil in a bowl and prepare a smooth sauce. Smoke and thoroughly clean the chicken wings. Put it in the sauce you prepared and let it rest for 1 hour. Then take the seasoned wings from the sauce and put them in a bottle and cook them on the grill. Add salt later. Wing skewer is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Kazandibi recipe; Spread margarine all over the tray and sprinkle powdered sugar with a strainer and cover all sides. Put the rice flour, wheat starch and sugar in the pot. Add the milk slowly and cook over medium heat, stirring constantly. Cover the bottom when it's bubbling. Take two or three scoops of the pudding and pour it into the tray. Put the custard on the stove on medium heat and burn the bottom of it by taking the custard from one place to another with the help of a spatula. When you are sure that it is burned evenly on all sides, put the pudding in the pot back on the stove. Bubbling the custard again and pour it into the pan when it boils. Pour cold water on the kitchen counter or chill the tray on a very wet towel. When it cools, cut it with a spatula and give it shape. Kazandibi is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the lamb shish kebab recipe; Chop the onions into small cubes. Put the chopped onion in a cheesecloth and squeeze out the juice. Put the coarsely chopped lamb meat in a bowl. Add onion juice, oil, bay leaf and thyme and mix. Let the meat rest like this in a cool place, preferably for a day. Thread the marinated meat onto skewers. In the meantime, light the grill and let it heat up. While the grill heats up, place the tomatoes and seeded peppers in a bottle. Grease the grill wire with 1 tablespoon of sunflower oil. After salting and peppering the meat on both sides, put it on the grill, turn it once and cook both sides for about 7-8 minutes until water droplets form on the meat. Brush them with sunflower oil from time to time while they are cooking. Serve hot on pre-heated plates with grilled tomatoes and peppers. Lamb shish kebab is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the squid pan recipe; Clean, wash and chop the squid. Put it in a bowl. Add the baking soda, lemon juice and rub. After rubbing, keep it in the fridge for 1 hour. After taking it out of the fridge, add the salt and mix. Dip the squid in flour and deep fry in hot oil. Grate the garlic. Mix the yogurt, garlic, balsamic vinegar and mayonnaise well in a bowl. Put in sauce pots. Take the calamari on a serving plate and serve with the sauce. The fried calamari is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Keshkul recipe; Put a deep saucepan on the stove over medium heat. Put the rice flour and sweetener in the pot and mix. Then slowly add the milk. Add the crushed hazelnuts. Cook until it reaches a custard consistency. Add the vanilla and cook for another minute or two, stirring, and remove from the stove. Empty into bowls. Keşkul is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For dried fruit mix compote; Wash and drain dried fruits thoroughly. Cut apricots and plums into 2-3 pieces. Take apricots, plums and grapes in separate bowls and add two glasses of water each. Leave for 1 hour at room temperature. Take the apricots, plums and grapes in a large pot with their juices. Add granulated sugar and mix. Let it simmer on medium heat with the lid closed. When it starts to boil, cook for 5 more minutes on medium heat and let it cool. When the compote has cooled, divide it into serving bowls. Serve cold. Dried apricot compote is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the meatball recipe; grate the onion, beat the garlic, finely chop the parsley. Put the onion, garlic, parsley, egg, bread crumbs, ground beef and spices in a deep bowl. Knead until it reaches a non-sticky consistency. If it sticks to your hands, add some more bread crumbs or breadcrumbs. Cut off pieces of the size you want and shape them flat. Lightly oil the bottom of the Teflon pan only. Arrange the meatballs and cook them over low heat, turning them occasionally. Meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Mücver; Take the eggs in a deep bowl and add flour and whisk until smooth. Finely chop the parsley and dill, grate the zucchini, chop the green onions into small pieces. Add the spices, grated and squeezed zucchini, finely chopped green onions, parsley and dill to the bowl and mix. Take oil in a Teflon pan and heat it. Pour a spoonful of the pumpkin mixture and cook the mutton. After both sides of the mucver are browned, take them to a paper towel lined plate. Mücver is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Snow White recipe; Put a deep saucepan on medium heat and add the oil. When the butter melts, add the flour and fry the flour. After roasting the flour, add the starch and sugar and mix for a few minutes. Then add the milk and vanilla and cook, stirring, until it reaches a thick consistency. When it comes to a dense consistency, turn off the heat and mix it well with a mixer for 3-4 minutes. Put 1 spoonful of coconut in 10 medium-sized teacups and fill it to the brim with the dessert you prepared with the help of a ladle. Leave the cups you prepared to cool for 2 hours. Then, by turning the cups upside down on the serving plates, slowly lift the cups and take out the desserts. Snow White is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Caesar Salad (Without Sauce) recipe; Cut the edges of the toasted bread and cut it into cubes. Mix the olive oil, salt, thyme, paprika in a bowl and add the breads and mix. Roast in the oven at 180 degrees. Fry thinly sliced chicken in 2 tablespoons of oil in a pan until lightly pink. Wash lettuce leaves and arugula in plenty of water. Put the washed leaves and arugula in the salad bowl by dividing it with your hand. Finely dice the tomatoes. and add it to the bowl. Place the roasted meats in the salad bowl by scattering them. Drizzle the toasted bread and add it to the bowl. Sprinkle the cheddar cheese you cut into cubes. Caesar salad (without dressing) is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Potato Rings recipe; Peel and dice the potatoes and then boil them. Put the chopped potatoes in a deep bowl. While the potatoes are hot, add the milk, egg, cheese, flour, butter, salt, pepper and chili flakes. Knead until you get a thicker consistency than cake batter. If it is runny, add flour and solidify. Open the dough by spreading it with your hand and cut round pieces from the dough with the mouth of a medium-sized water glass. Then cut it with a smaller glass mouth to remove the middle part of the rounds and add that piece back to the main dough. In this way, apply the same process to all the dough so that you get hollow rings. Add oil to the pan. Fry the potato rings in hot oil on both sides. Potato rings are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the hunter's pie recipe; Chop the onions into small pieces and fry them in a pan with ground beef. Finely chop the parsley. When the minced meat is cooked, add the parsley on the minced meat. Add the spices, add a little oil, turn off the heat and put it in a corner. Divide the yufka into 4 equal parts with the help of a knife, divide the dough into each part one by one, wrap them in the form of a spring roll and prepare. You prepared the pastries, first dip them in egg and then galata flour and fry them in hot oil. Hunter pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the bean on rice recipe; Soak the luru beans the night before. Boil it the day you cook it. Take oil and ground beef in a pan and fry them. Chop the onion and peppers into small pieces. Add the chopped onion and green pepper to the minced meat and fry. Chop the tomatoes into cubes, add 1 teaspoon of tomato paste and cook for 5 minutes and add the dried beans you boiled on it. Add salt, pepper and bay leaf, add enough hot water to go 2 inches above it and cook on medium heat. For pilaf making; Soak the rice in hot water 1 hour before making rice. Put the butter in a saucepan and fry the barley noodles. Add the rice you soaked and then drained. Add salt and pepper, add 2 glasses of hot water and cook on low heat. When the rice is drained, turn off the heat and let it brew. Divide the rice among the plates, then divide the beans and serve. Beans on rice is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the sandalwood pleasure recipe; First, cut the zucchini in half, then hollow out the insides with a teaspoon. Finely chop the peppers and onions, dice the tomatoes, chop the parsley and garlic into tiny pieces. Put the meat in a pan and cook it, then add the onions and peppers. When the peppers and onions release themselves, add the garlic, tomato and tomato paste and cook for two or three more minutes. Finally, add the spices and after it is cooked, add the parsley and cook a little more and turn off the heat. Heat oil in a pan and fry the zucchini. After this process is finished, put the pumpkins in the bordeaux or baking dish and put the stuffing inside the fried pumpkins and fill the boat. Dilute a teaspoon of tomato paste with hot water in a bowl and pour it on the tray. Bake at 200°. Sandalwood is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal

For the pastry recipe; First, break the flour, milk, sunflower oil, margarine, sugar, salt, yeast and eggs into a deep bowl and knead. When it reaches a non-sticky consistency, rest the dough for 1 hour. After resting the dough, break off small egg-sized pieces, roll them and place them on the baking tray. Brush the egg yolk over each pastry. Bake for 15-20 minutes. The pastry is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the fresh plum compote recipe; Wash the plums, remove the seeds and chop them and put them in the pot. Add water to it and boil it. When the plums start to soften, add the sugar and continue boiling. Add cloves and cinnamon to the container you will store later. Let it cool. Divide into containers when cool. Fresh plum compote is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the mussel pan recipe; keep the cleaned mussels in a strainer after washing. Sprinkle 1 teaspoon of flour on it and mix. In another bowl, beat the egg, salt, baking soda and make a liquid dough with the remaining tea glass of flour. Put the mussels in the strainer into this dough bowl and after they are covered with dough, put them on the skewers. Sprinkle the mussels on skewers with flour again and fry them in hot oil. The mussels are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the pancake recipe; finely chop the parsley. Mix the curd cheese and parsley in a bowl and prepare the stuffing. Prepare the sauce by slightly heating the milk, egg whites, oil and butter in a saucepan. Grease the baking tray and spread 1 sheet of dough on it. Spread the sauce you prepared on the dough. Cut a sheet of dough into pieces and lay it out on the tray. Put the inner mortar you prepared on the phyllo that you cut and put. Don't pour sauce on cheese layers. Spread the dough on it and apply the sauce you prepared again. Spread one more layer of dough. Sprinkle again on the cheesy batter. Lay a layer of dough on it. Spread the prepared sauce. Lay another layer of dough on it. For the final cheesy layer, sprinkle the cheeses and lay the remaining pastry on top. Cover the yufkas hanging from the sides of the tray, pour all the remaining sauce over the pastry and let it get wet all over. Finally, slice the pastry by brushing the egg yolk on it. Then bake in a preheated oven at 170-180 degrees until golden brown. Tray pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chicken Roast (with skin) recipe; Rub the cleaned and prepared chicken well with salt and pepper. Pass the chick a thick bottle. Grease the broiler with a brush. In whichever type of machine you will make the chicken turn, place it in its place. Oil the chicken in between and fry for 35-40 minutes until golden brown. Take the chicken off the skewer, divide it into equal parts and separate the bones. Serve without cooling. Chicken Roast (with skin) is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the false chicken breast recipe; Put the cold milk and flour in a saucepan and mix slowly with the mixer. Then light the bottom of the pot and cook until it reaches the consistency of custard. Before removing from the stove, add the softened margarine and mix well. Finally, add the powdered sweetener and beat with a mixer for 15-20 minutes. Pour the mixture into the dampened glass container and wait for it to cool. False chicken breast (with sweetener) is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the mixed grill recipe; Mix the yogurt, tomato paste, salt and pepper in a large bowl. Mix the chickens with this sauce and leave for 2 hours. Put the ground beef, egg, breadcrumbs, salt and pepper in a bowl, knead and prepare meatballs. Grill meatballs and chicken until browned on both sides. Take the middle part of the mushrooms and cook them on the grill until they release their juice 2 times. Distribute the meat and mushrooms evenly on the serving plates. Mixed grill is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the meat souffle recipe; put the butter in a saucepan. Heat the milk in a pot. When the butter melts, slowly add the flour and fry the flour. Then add the boiled milk little by little to the flour, Then add the meat pieces. Whisk 2 egg whites in a small bowl until stiff. Add the beaten eggs, salt and a teaspoon of black pepper to the pot. Pour them all on a tray of suitable size, spread the breadcrumbs on it and bake in the oven for 20 minutes. Enjoy your meal.

For the dumpling (Turkish style) recipe; Put the water, sugar and lemon juice in a saucepan and boil it to prepare the syrup. When it boils, turn off the heat and let it cool. Put the egg, yogurt, flour and baking powder in a deep bowl and whisk. Put the sunflower oil in a pan and heat it. Pour one tablespoon of the mortar you prepared into the hot oil. Smooth the edges into squares with a spatula with quick movements in the oil. Fry the dough until golden brown and pour into the syrup. Leave it in the syrup for 10 minutes and transfer it to the serving plate. Sprinkle coarsely ground walnuts on top and serve. Dumpling (Turkish style) is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Iskender kebab recipe; First of all, chop the meat, which is the main ingredient of Iskender Kebab, into thin doner kebabs. Put oil in a pan and add the finely chopped meat to the pan. Add salt when the meat dries up and fry until it turns brown. Dice the pita and place it on the bottom of the serving plates. Melt 2 tablespoons of butter in a separate sauce pan, put the tomato paste in it and fry it well. Add thyme, chili flakes and black pepper to the roasted tomato paste. Add a little boiled water to make the paste runny and cook. Spread the tomato paste sauce on the pita you cut. Put the fried meat on the pita with the sauce, and add the yoghurt to the edge of the plate. Melt the remaining butter in a small skillet and pour it over the meat. Iskender kebab (with butter) is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For meat doner (portion) recipe; Slice the beef thinly. Grate the onion. After mixing the yogurt, oil, onion, thyme, salt, red pepper and allspice in a large bowl, dip the meat slices into this mixture. Put the meat in the refrigerator to rest. Rest for at least an hour or two. Put the meat on the stove and cook it on low heat until it releases its own juice. Meat doner (portion) is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled vegetable recipe; Chop the zucchini and aubergines into rings, the peppers, tomatoes and mushrooms into 4 equal parts, the onion into round thin rings. Arrange the chopped vegetables on the wire rack. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 10-15 minutes. When the vegetables are cooked, arrange the vegetables on the serving plate. Sprinkle with salt, pepper and thyme and pour over. Grilled vegetables are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the lamb cover recipe; Put a saucepan on the fire and heat it well. Put the meat in the pot, add the salt and pepper and cook until the meat is nicely colored. Add 4-5 glasses of water and close the lid. Boil the meat for about 20 minutes. Chop the onions into rings and lay the cover on the bottom of the pot where you will cook it. Chop all the greens coarsely. Put half of the chopped chard, lettuce, dill and green onions on the onions you have placed on the bottom. Put the cooked meat on the greens and add all the remaining ingredients to the meat and close. Pour 1 glass of meat from the boiled water on it. Sprinkle some more salt and pepper, close the lid and put it on the fire. Cook for 30-40 minutes on medium heat. The lamb is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the setting recipe; melt the oil in the pan. Add the cornmeal to it and fry it lightly, add the water and mix, then add the cheddar, stir quickly until it melts and turn off the stove when it melts. Kuymak is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the finished walnut recipe; For the dough, thoroughly knead the semolina, margarine, flour and water in a deep bowl. Rest the dough for 1 hour. On the other hand, mix the walnuts, granulated sugar, cinnamon and rose water in a bowl and set aside. Walnut-sized pieces are broken from the rested dough. Open a piece in the palm of your hand and put the walnut filling in the middle and roll it. Prepare the other dough pieces in the same way. Place the desserts you prepared on a greased baking tray and let them rest for 1 hour. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven for 20 minutes. After it cools down, take it to a serving plate and sprinkle powdered sugar on it. The finished walnut is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Italian style cheese wrap recipe; Melt mozzarella cheese and parmesan cheese in a pan. Mix in the black pepper, salt, parsley leaves, crushed garlic and fresh thyme. Pour this mixture into a tray and wait for it to cool and solidify. After it cools, roll it with sliced sopressatta, salami, prosciutto and chicory. Then cut this roll into slices. Chop the lettuce leaves into finger thickness. Put the chopped lettuce on a serving platter. Place the slices cut from the roll on it. Cut the green peppers into 4 parts. Serve with split black olives, chopped green peppers, vinegar and olive oil. Italian style cheese wrap is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the country pita recipe; Take all the ingredients except the flour into the mixing bowl and mix. Then add a little flour and knead until you get a soft dough. Let it ferment for 2 hours. Chop the onions small. Take oil in the pan, add the chopped onion and fry it. Then add the ground beef and continue frying. Add the spices last and take it off the stove and let it cool. Take meringues from the fermented dough and roll them lengthwise with the help of flour. Spread the minced meat in the middle of the dough you rolled out. You can preferably slice a few pieces of cheddar cheese and add it to the ground beef. Then close the dough on both sides. Place on a greased or parchment-lined baking tray. Rub egg yolk on it. Bake at 200 degrees until golden brown. The pita bread is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken breast (fried) recipe; thinly slice the chicken breasts crosswise. Put the tomato paste, salt and pepper on a flat plate and mix. Get both sides of your sliced chicken in this sauce. Put half a teaspoon of oil in a large pan and heat it. When the oil is hot, add the sauced chicken breasts to the pan and fry them. Put the fried chicken breasts evenly on the serving plates. Chicken breast is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

for the carrot cake recipe with oat; Crack the eggs into a bowl and beat for 4 minutes until frothy. Add the milk and whisk again. Grate the carrot. pulverize the oat paste in a blender. Add the grated carrot, baking powder, cinnamon, honey, oat paste, vanilla and ground walnuts to the milk and egg mixture and mix. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 10-15 minutes. Then slice and divide on serving plates. carrot cake with oat is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled entrecote recipe; Marinate 4 thin slices of ribeye for at least half an hour. For marinating, add 2 tablespoons of olive oil, black pepper, salt and thyme to the meat thoroughly and keep it in the refrigerator. When you think that the marination process is sufficient, you can take it out of the refrigerator and cook it in a well-heated pan without adding oil. Enjoy your meal.

For the crispy chickpea recipe; Put the boiled chickpeas between paper towels and press them lightly and drain the water. Remove the shells after you absorb the water. In a bowl, mix the olive oil, paprika, cumin and salt well. Add the chickpeas to this mixture you have prepared and mix well. Cook the blended chickpeas in a saucepan for 10 minutes. Then pour and spread it on the baking tray, the bottom of which is covered with greaseproof paper. Bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees for another 20 minutes. After the crispy chickpeas are cooked, divide into bowls. Crispy chickpeas are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetable sauteed mushroom recipe; Chop the mushrooms, cut the peppers into tiny pieces and the zucchini into rings and sauté them in another pan on high heat and little oil. Put the tomato paste, the tomato and onion you have passed through the blender in a large pot and cook. Add the mushrooms, zucchini and peppers to the pot and cook for another 15 minutes. Mushroom sauteed with vegetables is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for roasting cauliflower in the oven; Divide and boil the cauliflower florets. Prepare the sauce by mixing the egg, yogurt, grated cheddar cheese, whole wheat flour and vegetable oil in a bowl. Dip the boiled cauliflowers in the prepared sauce and then place them on the baking tray that you have covered with greaseproof paper. Bake in the oven for about 15-20 minutes. Roast cauliflower in the oven is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the meatball recipe; Mix the ground meat, bread crumbs, salt, pepper, egg and grated onion and knead. On the other hand, wash the potatoes and carrots, boil them and chop them into pieces of backgammon dice. Mix the peas, potatoes and carrots. Roll out the meatball dough with a rolling pin on a hard surface. Add the vegetable mixture to which you add salt and pepper. Wrap the meatball dough in the form of a roll, place it on the tray and put it in the oven heated to 200 degrees. After baking for 25-30 minutes, pour the diluted tomato paste on the rolled meatballs and keep it in the oven for 20-25 minutes. Put the rolled meatballs on a serving plate, slice into 6 equal pieces and serve hot. Meatloaf is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the raisin diet cookie recipe: Mix egg, yogurt and oil and add grated apples. Add the raisins and cinnamon to the mixture, and add the flour, baking powder and vanilla last. Stir until the mixture is thicker than cake batter. Bake at 200 degrees. Enjoy your meal :)
For the pumpkin diet pudding recipe; After crushing the boiled pumpkin, mix it with milk. Then add the other ingredients and let it cook. Serve cold after cooking. Enjoy your meal :)

for the recipe with oat paste and diet milk-lutta; In a bowl, add egg yolk and milk, wheat flour and cornstarch and whisk. Cook on medium heat. After removing from the heat, add the sweetener and vanilla to the mixture. Serve in your serving bowl by putting the pudding first, oat paste on top, then again with the pudding and blueberries. Enjoy your meal :)

For the broccoli cheese omelet recipe; Boil the broccoli first. In another bowl, beat the eggs with the tip of a knife, adding salt. Put 1 teaspoon of vegetable oil in the frying pan and pour the beaten eggs into the pan with the help of a ladle, then fold the omelet by putting the broccoli and feta cheese you boiled in it. After making sure that the inside is cooked well, you can take it to the serving plate. Broccoli cheese omelet is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the cocoa pudding recipe; Mix all the ingredients except vanilla and molasses and cook in a pudding consistency over medium heat. After it has a consistency, remove it from the fire and add sweetener and vanilla. It can be consumed as you wish after distributing it into serving bowls. Enjoy your meal :)

For diet pancake recipe; Beat the egg, add milk and continue mixing, add salt, 2 fingers less than 1 glass of whole wheat flour and mix with the help of a whisk. Cook in an oil-free Teflon or ceramic pan. Diet pancakes are ready to be served, bon appetit.

For the vegetable wrap recipe; Saute the vegetables you cut into small pieces with 1 teaspoon of oil. Then, spread the vegetables inside the wholemeal lavash bread and make a roll. Sprinkle 1 teaspoon of grated cheddar on the wrap and bake in the preheated oven until the cheddar melts. Vegetable wrap is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the vegetable wheat salad, boil the wheat. Cut the zucchini, carrot, eggplant and red pepper into thin strips and sauté. As a sauce, prepare olive oil, lemon, mustard and black pepper in a separate bowl. Place 2 leaves of arugula on a serving plate. Add the sautéed vegetables first, then the wheat, sprinkle with chopped parsley and add the sauce. Wheat salad with vegetables is ready to serve, bon appetit.

For the mashed potatoes, peel the potatoes and cut them into large cubes. Put the diced potatoes in the pot. Add enough milk to cover them slightly. Add the salt and butter pieces to the milk. Let the potatoes soften well by mixing them so that they do not stick to the bottom. When the potatoes are soft, turn off the stove and pass it through the blender. Distribute the puree evenly on the plates. For the meatballs, grate the onion and finely chop the parsley. Put the parsley, onion, minced meat, bread crumbs, salt, spices in a deep bowl and knead. Make 16 flat meatballs from the meatball dough. Cook the meatballs on the grill or in a Teflon pan. When the meatballs are cooked on both sides, distribute them on plates with puree on the bottom. Mashed Potato Meatballs are ready to serve, bon appetit.

For the chicken broccoli gratin recipe; Wash the broccoli well and boil it in salted water. Then fry the finely chopped onions and garlic in olive oil in a deep pan. Put your sauteed sliced chicken breast and diced carrots in the pan and fry them. After these processes, put the broccoli and other ingredients in the oven dish. Beat and mix 1 egg with the cooled bechamel sauce and then combine with the ingredients in the baking dish. After putting the cheddar cheese on top, bake in the oven at 180 degrees. Your chicken broccoli gratin is ready to serve Enjoy your meal :)

For the broccoli meatball recipe in the oven; Wash the broccoli and cut into florets. Boil in salted water. Put it in ice water and leave it for 5 minutes, then strain the water. Take it in a bowl and mash with a fork. Heat the oil in a pan. Add the onion cut into small cubes and crushed garlic and fry. Add the fried onions, eggs, breadcrumbs, cheese on the crushed broccoli and season it with salt and pepper and knead. Place your meatballs on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven until golden brown. Enjoy your meal :)

For the broccoli pasta recipe with basil sauce; First, leave the pasta in boiling water for 10-11 minutes. cook it. On the other hand, boil the broccoli and prepare the pasta sauce. For this, chop the onion and garlic finely and fry them in olive oil. Add tomato paste, chopped tomatoes and basil and fry together. When the consistency thickens by pouring some water on it, remove it from the stove. Take the cooked pasta on a serving plate. Pour the sauce over it. Sprinkle the broccoli you boiled on the top by chopping flowers. Serve with cheese on top, if desired. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for broccoli with minced meat; Add olive oil to the pan and cook the onions on low heat for two minutes. Add the minced meat and sauté for a while, then add a glass of water to the food. Add a clove of garlic and sauté for another minute. Add tomato paste on it and cook until the water evaporates. Add the broccoli cut into small pieces on top. Add black pepper and sweet pepper. Cook until the broccoli is soft. Mix yogurt and garlic in a bowl. Heat both sides of the lavash in the pan and cut it into small triangular pieces. Take the broccoli dish on a plate and add the triangular lavash on it. Drizzle the yoghurt over the dish and add cayenne pepper. Your meal is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For Potato Carrot Lentil Soup; Put the grated onions and tomato paste in a pan and cook it. Put the water and salt. Add the cleaned and washed lentils, grated potatoes and carrots and cook well for 30 minutes. Serve hot. Potato Carrot Lentil Soup is ready to be served, bon appetit.

For the vegetable lentil soup, First cut the leek lengthwise and chop finely. Put the oil, leek and tomato paste in the pan and cook a little. Add the water, salt, grated potatoes, carrots, celery and lentils, cook well and serve hot. Vegetable lentil soup is ready to be served, bon appetit.

For sauteed cabbage with chicken; Put the chopped onions, salt, and oil in the pan. Throw in the chopped cabbage with the onions and cook by mixing, add the tomato paste and continue cooking on low heat by adding the water until the cabbages soften. Add the diced chicken and cook until the chicken turns colour. Put it on a serving plate, garnish with paprika and serve hot. Sauteed Cabbage with Chicken is ready to serve, bon appetit.

For the chicken leek saute, Wash the leeks, cut them lengthwise, chop finely. Put the oil, leeks and salt in the Teflon pan, cook on low heat. Add the garlic and continue cooking, stirring. Add the diced chicken and cook, stirring, until it turns color. Serve hot. Chicken leek sauté is ready to serve, bon appetit.

For the wholemeal bagel recipe; Slightly heat 1.5 cups of water to lukewarm. Mix lukewarm water, salt and yeast in a bowl. Take the flour in a large dough kneading bowl and open the middle like a pool. Add the yeast mixture and knead it until it does not stick to the hand. Form a bagel shape by breaking off pieces from the dough and rolling them with your hands. Dip the bagels you prepared in the remaining half glass of water and take them out. Spread the sesame and sunflower seeds on a large plate. Put both sides of the bagels you prepared with sesame seeds and pita seeds and take them. Arrange the bagels evenly on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Brush some oil on them. Bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees for 30 minutes. They come out of the oven when they are browned. Whole wheat bagel is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the sweetened quince jam; Wash and sort the quinces and grate them without peeling them. Cook the grated quince in a little water on low heat for 1 hour. Turn off the stove, crush or melt the sweetener while the jam is hot, mix it with the sweetener. let it cool down. Quince jam is ready to serve, bon appetit.

For the chicken broccoli recipe; Saute the olive oil, soy sauce, garlic and chicken in a pan for 10 minutes. Then, put the boiled broccoli and peppers in the pan and after frying a little, add the ginger and cloves and continue frying. After the chicken leaves the water, add the cornstarch and make the water thick. Your meal is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the green lentil artichoke recipe; Squeeze half a lemon into the cleaned artichokes and boil them by adding half a teaspoon of salt. Boil the lentils with enough water to cover them for 10-12 minutes and drain. Chop the green onion, dill and red pepper very finely and mix them into the lentils. Add olive oil, remaining lemon and salt and mix well. Take the boiled artichokes on a serving plate, put the lentils on them and leave to cool. Artichoke with green lentils is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the leek pie recipe without phyllo; Boil the leeks and drain the water well, squeeze and mash. Boil the potatoes with their skins in another pot. After boiling, peel the skins and mash in a bowl. Add the leek, egg, grated cheddar and spices. Pour your mixture into the greased baking dish. If you wish, apply 1 egg yolk on it, add black cumin seeds and bake in the oven at 170 degrees. Pie with leek without phyllo is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken skewer recipe with halloumi cheese; Cut the chicken breasts into finger lengths into five pieces. Slice the tomatoes horizontally in half and into quarters. Cut the peppers into four pieces as well. Slice the halloumi cheese slices into rectangles so that 4 bottles of five pieces are attached. Put the pieces of halloumi cheese on the chicken breasts that you sliced finger-length before and wrap them in the form of a roll. Arrange 4 bottles of chicken breasts with halloumi cheese, tomato slices and peppers in order. Put the prepared skewers side by side. Beat the garlic in a bowl and add the salt and pepper and mix. Then brush this mixture on the skewers. Finally, cook both sides of these skewers on the preheated grill. Chicken skewer with halloumi cheese is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the cheese shrimp recipe; Cut the eggplants lengthwise and bake them in the oven until they are a little soft on the inside. Put the cheese in a bowl and mash. Add the dill, parsley, egg, salt, pepper and olive oil to the bowl where you put the cheese and mix well. Open the middle of the eggplants that you have cooked a little in the oven, take some from it and put it in place, evenly from the mortar you prepared. After putting the mortars, spread the cheddar cheese on each eggplant with 1 teaspoon of grated cheddar cheese. Line the eggplants on a slightly greased baking tray and bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 15 minutes. Ketchup with cheese is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

for the chicken breast recipe with oat; Chop the chicken and the dill into small cubes. Grate the zucchini. Put olive oil, grated zucchini, oat bran, salt in a Teflon pan and stir fry. Then add the chopped chicken breasts and continue cooking by mixing. Turn off the heat when the chickens are cooked. Pour the yogurt into a deep bowl. Add the chopped dill into it and mix well. Then divide this mixture into 2 medium bowls. Open the middle of the bowls and place the lukewarm veggie chicken breasts evenly in the openings. Finally, sprinkle the walnuts that you have crushed with your hands by dividing them into bowls. Chicken breast with oat is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the pepper kebab recipe; Chop the tomato and onion into small cubes. Put the chopped tomato, onion, dried mint, salt, pepper, currant, black cumin, bulgur and water in a deep bowl and mix. Clean the insides of the bell peppers and place the stuffed stuffing you prepared evenly in the stuffing. Lay the stuffed stuff you prepared vertically on a small baking tray. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees until the peppers are golden brown. Pepper kebab is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Cinnamon Applesauce, peel the apples after washing them. Slice, remove seeds and place in a saucepan. Add water and cinnamon to it. Cook until the apples are soft. When the apples are soft, pass them through a blender and puree. Cinnamon Apple Puree is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Carrot Potato and Zucchini Mucver, peel and grate the carrots, potatoes and zucchini. Strain the water by squeezing the grated ingredients and put them in a bowl. Prepare the pastry dough by adding whole wheat flour, eggs, salt, black pepper and red pepper. Fry your mucver in plenty of oil with the help of a spoon. Take the fried muffins on the plates on which you lay napkins. Mucver with carrot potatoes and zucchini is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the tricolor pepper omelet recipe; Finely chop the peppers. Crack the egg into a bowl. Add the chopped peppers on it. Add the mixture to the oil that is heated in the pan. Tri-colored pepper omelet is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the dill muffin recipe, beat eggs, yogurt and oil in a deep bowl with a mixer. Add flour, baking powder and salt and continue beating. Add the cheese first, then the finely chopped dill and parsley and mix with a spoon. Grease the muffin tins a little with a napkin. Pour 1.5 spoons of the mixture into the molds, bake in the oven at 180 degrees until they are golden brown. Dill muffin is ready to serve after it has cooled down. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for cinnamon apple slices in the oven; Thinly slice the apples without peeling them. Pour a little lemon juice and cinnamon over the apples. Lay the apple slices apart on the baking tray with baking paper. Bake in the oven at 100 degrees for about 45 minutes. Baked cinnamon apple slices are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

In a mixing bowl, mix the cornstarch and sweetener, add the milk and whisk until a smooth mixture. In a separate bowl, whisk the egg yolks lightly and add to this milky mixture, add the zest of 4 lemons and a little salt. Cook over medium heat, stirring frequently at the beginning and constantly towards the end. Once the mixture has solidified enough to form a layer on the back of the spoon, remove it from the heat. Add the grated lemon peels and mix well. Pour it into bowls, let it cool at room temperature, keep it in the refrigerator for at least 2 hours and serve cold. Enjoy your meal

For the chicken pea salad recipe, boil the chicken and peas in separate pots. Drain the peas with the help of a colander, hold them under cold water and put them in a bowl. Finely chop the chickens. Finely chop the green onion, dill and parsley. Chop the tomatoes and green peppers. Take all the ingredients in a bowl and mix well. Add olive oil and lemon juice to it. Chicken Pea Salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the turkey wrap with vegetables; Put the turkey breast in a medium-sized pot and fill the pot with water to the level above it and boil it at medium heat. Shred the turkeys with your hands after they have cooled. Chop the lettuce, scallions and cucumbers in a Coarse. Add the peeled and diced tomatoes, sliced peppers, boiled turkey meat and chopped parsley and mix well. Add the oil and lemon juice and mix again. Make a wrap by putting the salad you prepared in the lavash. The turkey wrap with vegetables is ready to serve, bon appetit.

For the diet carrot balls recipe, peel the carrots and pass them through the robot. Cook the carrots covered in a Teflon pan. After the carrots have softened and their juices have evaporated, add the oat paste and walnuts you have passed through the blender. Then add cinnamon and honey and knead well. Cut small pieces from the carrot mortar you prepared and give it a round shape. Optionally, you can drizzle with coconut. Diet carrot balls are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Fesliken Noodle Yogurt Soup recipe, first whisk the eggs, yogurt and milk. Slowly add a spoonful of flour in the pot and mix it by whisking so that it does not form lumps. Then add 1 liter of boiled water and add the noodles to the pot. Add salt when the noodles are cooked. Add basil when it's almost cooked. Vermicelli yoghurt soup with basil is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal

For the recipe for crunchy bread with labneh cheese; organic whole wheat breads are toasted in the oven until they become crunchy. Then labneh cheese is spread on them. Your crunchy bread with labneh cheese is ready. Enjoy your meal

For the Zucchini Lasagna recipe, fry the ground beef with salt in a pan. Then strain the oil with the help of a strainer. Add the olive oil to the pan, then fry the garlic and onions. Add the minced meat back to the pan and add the finely chopped tomatoes, finely cut basil, salt and pepper. Cook at low temperature for 30 - 40 minutes until you get a thick sauce. Slice the zucchini thinly, not too thinly. Lightly salt the zucchini. Then remove the excess water with the help of a paper napkin. Then fry the zucchini in the oven for 2-3 minutes on the front and back, until they turn brown. After taking it out of the oven, take the phase water with the help of a paper napkin. Then bring the oven to 375 degrees. Lightly grease a rectangular baking dish, then place the zucchini first, then the thinly sliced cheddar cheese, then the mince sauce. Add layers to the lasagna in this order. After sorting the zucchini on the top, place the grated cheddar cheese and put it in the oven. After about 20-30 minutes of cooking time, the lasagna is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the apple puree date pudding recipe; After crushing the boiled apple, mix it with milk. For easy peeling, add the dates you have kept in warm water by crushing them beforehand. Grate the ginger. Add all the other ingredients and mix, then let it cook. After cooking, serve the apple puree date pudding cold. Enjoy your meal  :)

For the Emperor's Rice Pudding recipe, after washing the black rice, boil it in 3 glasses of water until it becomes soft. Put the milk in a separate pot and bring it to a boil. Add sugar and boiled rice to the boiling milk and continue to cook by mixing. When the rice pudding thickens, take it off the heat, add cinnamon while it is warm and mix it well. Allow to cool in a cool place, stirring occasionally. Meanwhile, grate your almonds. Distribute your rice pudding evenly in bowls and decorate it with grated almonds. Emperor rice pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For the baked apple recipe; Wash the apple, slice it into 1 finger thick rings without peeling the skin. Remove the seeds from the slices. Place on the baking tray, put half a glass of water in the tray and add the cloves - half a stick of cinnamon. Cook at 175 degrees until all the water has been removed and the apple slices are soft. Your baked apples are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the sugar-free mosaic cake recipe; Heat the milk, then add a teaspoon of cocoa to it, mix it carefully so that it does not clump, and bring it to a boil. Take all the remaining ingredients, except the cocoa milk and biscuits, in a bowl and whisk well. Break the biscuits into the warm mixture without crumbling too much and mix it and spread it on the aluminum foil. Give it the shape of a pyramid or wipe, and wrap it with foil and roll it. Keep the mosaic cake roll in the freezer for 2-3 hours. Then slice evenly according to the number of people. Sugar-free mosaic cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Poppy Bun recipe, leave the yeast and sugar in a bowl with warm water for 5 minutes. Then, add the flour, salt and yeast in the dough bowl and mix with the help of warm water until it reaches a dough consistency. Then cover it and wait for it to ferment. After the dough is fermented, divide it into 4 equal parts and expand these pieces that you rolled with your hands and spread the smashed poppies with oil on top. Stack all the pieces on top of each other in the same way, placing poppy between them. Enlarge the formed 4-layer dough with your hands, with a knife, arrange it in strips of about 4 cm around itself on the nose and side by side on the tray. Before putting it in the oven, cut the buns to the size you want and wait for 20 minutes for the tray yeast to come. Then brush the scrambled egg on it and bake in the oven at 180-200 degrees until the top is golden brown. Your poppy bun is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal

For the asparagus soup recipe; peel and chop the asparagus and chop the onions for edibles. Fry the onion in olive oil in a pan, then add the asparagus to the pan and continue frying. Add hot water and corn to the pot and cook. To season the soup, melt the butter in a small saucepan, then add the flour and mix. Continue processing until the smell of flour is gone. Then pour cold milk and whisk quickly. Pour the seasoning into the pot where the asparagus is cooking, continuing to whisk. Then add the broth and salt. If the consistency is dark, it can be opened with water until it reaches the desired consistency. Asparagus soup is ready to serve Enjoy your meal :)

For the arugula salad recipe with mung beans and curd cheese; Boil the mung beans, which were soaked the night before, for 20 minutes. Chop the arugula and red peppers and put them in a bowl. Add the curd cheese on top. Prepare a sauce with extra virgin olive oil, pomegranate syrup, lemon juice and salt and pour it over. Cut the walnut into small pieces and garnish with walnuts. Arugula salad with mung beans and curd cheese is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the oven baked brussels sprouts recipe; preheat the oven at 200 degrees. Prepare a sauce by mixing olive oil, salt and pepper, and black pepper. Put the prepared sauce and brussels sprouts in the oven bag. Bake for about 30-40 minutes. After taking it out of the bag, grate light cheddar cheese on it.

For the Molasses Cheese Halva recipe; Take the olive oil and semolina in a saucepan, stir fry. Mix molasses and water in a separate bowl. When the smell of the semolina comes out, add the molasses-water mixture you prepared on it. Grate the cheese. When the halva starts to thicken, add the grated cheese. After the cheese melts, the cheese halva with molasses is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the pumpkin mehir soup recipe; Wash the wheat the night before, drain it and put it in a medium saucepan, add water and boil it. 15 minutes after it starts to boil, take it from the stove and keep it closed until morning. The next day, add 2 cups of water and boil again until soft. In another bowl, whisk the strained yogurt, egg yolk and black pepper well. Add this mixture to the boiling wheat, stirring constantly. Next, peel and dice the zucchini and add to the pot and stir. After about 10 minutes, when the zucchini starts to soften, remove from the heat. Sprinkle with salt and serve hot or cold. Mehir soup with pumpkin is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Lebeniye Soup recipe; Soak chickpeas and wheat. Then boil it for a while. Put the boiled chickpeas and wheat in the pot and add it to the water and bring it to a boil. While the chickpeas and wheat are boiling, knead the ground beef, salt and pepper in another bowl and prepare chickpea-sized meatballs and boil them in water. Add the boiled meatballs to the pot where the chickpeas and wheat are boiled. For its dressing, mix the strained yogurt, egg and flour in a bowl, take a ladle of the soup and warm it up, add this mixture to the soup again and stir constantly. For the sauce, heat the olive oil in a small pan, add the chopped onion and fry it until it turns pink. After roasting, add dried mint and mix. Pour the sauce over the cooked soup and serve. Lebeniye soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the yogurt vegetable salad recipe; carrots, zucchini, cucumbers, grate. Fry the grated carrot in a pan with a little olive oil. Then add the zucchini and fry them. Set aside to cool. Prepare garlic yogurt in a separate bowl. Add the grated cucumber and dried mint and mix well. When the zucchini and carrots are cold, add them to the yogurt mixture, mix well and pour it on the serving plate. Vegetable salad with yogurt is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the lentil stew recipe; Take the fine bulgur in a bowl and add enough hot water to cover it very lightly and let it soften. In a bowl, add the pepper and tomato paste, salt, pepper, olive oil, lemon juice, pomegranate syrup and finely chopped garlic and mix. Add cumin, chili pepper and dried mint and mix again. Then finely chop the green onions and parsley and add to the mixture with the bulgur that swells in hot water and mix well. Finally, add the boiled lentils and mix well again. Pour this mixture into the bowl to be served and finally sprinkle some crushed or crushed walnuts on it. Lentil stew is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Göceli tarhana soup recipe, break the egg in a bowl. Beat well. Then add the yoghurt and flour and mix well. When you get a thick consistency, add pre-boiled asurea wheat and mix it well with your hands. Add 1 teaspoon of salt and continue mixing. Put the mixture you prepared in the pot and add cold water to it and mix until it opens well. Heat the olive oil in a pan. When the oil is hot, add the dried mint to the oil and cook a little. Then divide the soup into serving plates and pour the sauce you prepared on it. Goceli tarhana soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the dry cowpea recipe; Soak the kidney beans overnight. Then boil the soaked cowpeas in a pot with enough water to cover them and drain. Boil again for 20 minutes in water with lemon juice added and drain the water. Finely chop the peppers, pickles, dill and parsley. Mix it all with the black-eyed peas. On the other hand, mix olive oil, remaining lemon juice, salt and sumac and add to the salad. Dried cowpea salad is ready. Enjoy your meal :)

For the apple cinnamon sugar-free muffin recipe; First of all, break the eggs into a bowl and add the molasses and oil and whisk well. In another bowl, add the whole wheat flour, baking powder and vanilla. Add cinnamon, allspice and crushed walnuts and mix. On another side, peel and grate the apples. Add the grated apples to the egg mixture and mix well. Combine these two mixtures and mix. Then pour this mixture into greased muffin cups. Bake in a preheated 220 degree oven and reduce to 180 degrees after 5 minutes. Apple cinnamon sugar-free muffins are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for wholemeal rice salad with peas; Put the olive oil in the pot and the whole wheat rice that you have soaked in hot water before and fry it. Then add 2 cups of hot water and close the lid and cook. While the rice is cooking, finely chop the parsley, dill, green onions, and finely chop the pickles and put them in a deep bowl. Drain the peas thoroughly, add them to the bowl and mix. When the cooked rice cools down, add the rice and the juice of the lemon to the bowl and mix well. Pour into serving plate. Whole-grain rice salad with peas is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Balaban Kebab recipe; 750 gr. Knead ground beef, 2 slices of stale bread, 3 cloves of finely chopped garlic, 1 egg, half a teaspoon of black pepper, 1 teaspoon of cumin, 1 teaspoon of thyme, 1 teaspoon of baking soda in a bowl. Cut small pieces of meatball dough, roll them in your hands, shape them and fry them in hot oil. Cut 8 doner pitas (must be stale) squarely. Put tomato paste in it and pour the boiled bone broth over the pita. Pour 1 bowl of whipped yogurt on the pitas and spread the fried meatballs on it. Burn some butter in a pan and drizzle over the meatballs. Balaban kebab is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the vegetable patties recipe; Grate the carrot, potato and zucchini. After adding the other ingredients and mixing, roll them in egg size and bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 30 minutes. Vegetable patties are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the flourless mucver recipe; grate the potatoes and zucchini. Add other ingredients and mix. Pour the mixture onto a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Bake at 180 degrees for 30 minutes. Flourless mucver is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for molasses flour kvass; Melt the butter in a saucepan, add the flour when the butter melts and fry, stirring constantly, until browned. Add crushed walnuts, molasses, milk and water and continue mixing. Continue mixing for 5-6 minutes until it becomes smooth. Shape and serve while hot. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the tuna potato croquette recipe; Grate the boiled potato and mix all the ingredients in a bowl. Give it the shape you want and smear it with oat bran. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 20 minutes. Your potato croquettes are ready to serve, bon appetit.

For the phyllo pastry recipe; Boil the potatoes with their skins in a saucepan. After boiling, peel the skins and mash in a bowl. Add the white cheese, eggs, grated cheddar and spices. Pour your mixture into the greased baking dish. If you wish, apply 1 egg yolk on it, add black cumin seeds and bake in the oven at 170 degrees. The phyllo pastry is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Roll Omelette recipe; First, beat the egg and flour until well mixed, then add the milk and continue beating. Finely chop the tomato, red pepper and parsley. Combine all ingredients in the same bowl and mix. Then pour the mixture on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper and bake at 180 degrees. After it is warm, turn it into a role with the help of greaseproof paper and slice it. Rolled omelet is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal..

Baked Scrambled Eggs, preheat the oven to 180 degrees. Mix all the ingredients in a bowl and transfer to the baking dish. After 10 minutes of cooking in the oven, mix the egg mixture. Then continue cooking in the oven for another 12 minutes. The scrambled eggs in the oven are ready. Enjoy your meal..

For the Egg Paste recipe; Dilute the tomato paste by mixing it with water. After heating the olive oil in the pan, pour the diluted tomato paste into the pan and fry a little. Then add the eggs, fry them and after cooking, take the pan from the ovary. Fried egg is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chickpea Noodle Cold Soup recipe; Fry the noodles in 1 tablespoon of oil. Then add the chickpeas. Add water and salt and boil. Then let it cool. Beat the yogurt in a separate bowl and add the finely chopped mint to the chickpeas. Then add yoghurt on the chickpeas and garnish with the remaining olive oil. Chickpea noodle cold soup is ready. Enjoy your meal..

For the Corn Cold Soup recipe; Boil the corn until it splits slightly. Boil the bulgur in a separate pot until soft. In the meantime, chop the cucumbers to the desired size in the small soup, and finely chop the dill and mint. In a deep bowl, whisk the yogurt, add the water and salt and mix. After straining the boiled corn and wheat and waiting for it to warm up a little, add it to the yogurt with dill and mint. Finally, drizzle with olive oil and garnish. Corn cold soup is ready. Enjoy your meal..

For the Diet Güllaç recipe; 5 glasses of milk and honey are mixed and heated close to boiling. Wet the Güllaç leaves in a deep pyrex and sprinkle the ground walnuts and hazelnuts between the leaves. Arrange the sliced ​​dried figs and peaches on the interlayers and on top. Diet Güllaç is ready. Enjoy your meal..

For the recipe for cold wheat soup with labneh; pre-wet the wheat with plenty of water. The next day, filter it and add enough water to cover it by 1 finger. Boil until soft and strain again. Whisk the flour, egg, olive oil and labneh in a bowl. Add 5 glasses of water little by little. Then pour this mixture over the wheat in the pot. Add the salt and. Stir until it boils. When it boils, turn off the heat and let it cool. Keep it in the fridge when it cools down. When serving, garnish with julienned and baked red peppers. Cold wheat soup with labneh is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Turkey Fresh Peas recipe; In a pan, fry the butter and diced boneless turkey leg until it releases its juice. Add the chopped onion to the pan and stir for a while, then add the green pepper, carrot and potato. Immediately after, we add the peas and the chopped tomatoes with their skins on it, add the salt, add the hot water and chicken broth until the upper limit of the material, and after boiling for a moment, we turn the bottom down and cook until the peas absorb the salt and flavor of the food.

For the recipe for Stuffed Bran Rice with Meat; First of all, add some olive oil and add the chopped onions to the pot, fry them and add the ground beef. The water of the washed wholemeal rice soaked in water is filtered and added to the pot and continue to fry. Add tomato paste or tomato sauce, throw salt. Add 1 glass of hot water and cook on low heat with the lid closed until the water evaporates. When the water is absorbed, close the bottom and add the spices. Let it rest with the lid closed until it cools. On the other hand, wash the green bell peppers, cut off the caps and remove the seeds. Put the meat paste in the green bell peppers with the help of a spoon and fill them in a medium-sized pot by applying the same process to all of them. Add 1 cup of hot water and the remaining olive oil to the pot and cook on low heat until the peppers soften. Enjoy your meal...

For the Meat Bulgur Stuffed Recipe; Peel and core the eggplants. Scrape the zucchini lightly and carve the insides. Season the vegetables you have prepared with a mixture of black pepper and salt. Put the bulgur in a mixing bowl. Finely chop the onions and parsley. Mix all ingredients (except tomatoes) well. After mixing all the ingredients well, stuff them into the zucchini and eggplants. Cover the eggplants and zucchini with tomato slices. Arrange the stuffing upright in the pan. Drizzle some olive oil over the stuffing. Add enough salt on one side, add less than half of the stuffing, add hot water, first boil on high heat, and cook for 45-50 minutes on low heat until the stuffing is soft. Enjoy your meal.

For the Vegetable Salmon Skewer recipe; Chop the salmon into large cubes. Mix with salt and pepper. Finely chop the peppers and onions. Arrange one salmon, one pepper and one onion on wooden skewers that you have soaked in water for 20 minutes. Place tomatoes on the back and front. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 20 minutes. Salmon skewers with vegetables are ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Mantı recipe from Whole Wheat Flour; Turn the flour into a pool on a flat surface. Crack the egg and add milk and 1 teaspoon of salt. Knead the dough until it reaches the consistency of an earlobe. Divide the dough into equal parts, cover with a cloth and let it rest for 15 minutes. Put the ground beef in a bowl. Chop the onion and parsley very finely and add to the ground beef. Add 1 teaspoon of salt, black pepper and ground pepper and knead well. Flour the dough balls and roll them out as thin as you can with a rolling pin. Cut into squares with a knife. Put sufficient amount of minced meat and turn it into a bundle. Boil water in a saucepan and add salt. Cook the ravioli packs in boiling water for 4-6 minutes. Take the ravioli on plates and pour as much yogurt as you want. Manti made of whole wheat flour is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for fried okra with chickpeas, after washing the okra, cut off the tops, cut off the ends and chop them into small pieces. Put the olive oil and mustard in a large skillet, add the butter and melt it. Add the onion and garlic and fry for about 5 minutes until the onions soften. Add the chopped pepper, tomato and ginger and mix well. Then add the okra, cumin and coriander. Cook on low heat by turning for 5 minutes and add the chickpeas and salt. Continue cooking on low heat until the chickpeas are hot. Okra fried with chickpeas is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the oven chicken recipe with yogurt sauce; Whisk yogurt, olive oil, onion, garlic, sweet ground pepper, lemon juice and saffron (soaked in 1 tablespoon of boiling water) in a bowl. Season with salt and pepper. Put the chickens in a shallow bowl and pour the sauce you prepared on it and close the mouth. Leave in the refrigerator for at least 4 hours. Set the oven to 180 degrees. Place the chickens on a baking tray and bake for 30-40 minutes. Oven chicken with yoghurt sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)
For the Baked Lavash Bread recipe; Divide 1 wholemeal lavash bread into 4 equal parts. Dry slowly in an oven at 70 degrees for 2 hours. Baked lavash bread is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Vegetable Wrap recipe; Fry the eggplants in the oven with 1 teaspoon of oil. Saute the mushrooms and peppers in separate pans. Then mix all the vegetables. For tomato sauce, grate the tomato and fry it with tomato paste in 1 teaspoon of oil until it turns into a thick sauce. Then, add the vegetables, the sauce, and then the cheddar cheese in the lavash bread and wrap it. Your veggie wrap is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Vegetable Whole Wheat Rice recipe; Soak the rice with hot water half an hour beforehand. At the end of half an hour, drain the rice and put it in a rice cooker with two and a half glasses of cold water. Boil the rice until most of the water has been absorbed. On the other hand, remove the seeds of the bell pepper and chop it into small pieces. Add the chopped red bell pepper, peas and corn to the rice that is about to absorb the water and mix. Close the lid, cook the rice a little more on low heat. After taking it off the stove, let it brew for a while with the lid closed. Serve while hot. Enjoy your meal.

For the Parsley Minced Meat recipe; First, fry the ground beef in butter. Add the finely chopped onions and continue frying. Then put all the ingredients except the parsley in the pot and continue cooking. Add the last half a glass of water and finely chopped parsley and cook it so that the parsley does not die. Minced meat with parsley is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For herb bread recipe, dissolve dry yeast with 90 g of water. After adding flour and salt to the mixture, knead it to form a dough. Then add the finely chopped dill and parsley to the dough. After resting for 10 minutes, give the desired shape. Then rest for 35 minutes on a tray lined with greaseproof paper. Bake in the oven at 210 degrees for 15 minutes. After cooking, sprinkle a small amount of water on them and let them rest. Your herb bread is ready,. Enjoy your meal.

For the lemon semolina dessert recipe; Mix brown sugar, semolina and lemon zest dry. Then add milk to it. Finally, add turmeric to give it color and cook it on medium heat by stirring until it thickens. Take the boiling semolina from the stove after 2-3 minutes and put it in the mold. After it comes to room temperature, put it in the refrigerator. After 4-5 hours, lemon semolina dessert is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the wholemeal pasta recipe with chicken and tomatoes; Take the boiling water in the pot and add 1 packet of pasta and salt. While the pasta is on the stove, finely chop the chicken breast. Then grate our tomatoes. Cook the chicken breast in a pan, in which you have added about half a tea glass of oil. After the chickens are cooked, add the tomato paste and fry for 1 minute. Then add the grated tomatoes and cook for 1 more minute. Finally, after adding the spices and mixing, the sauce is ready. Add the sauce to the cooked pasta and mix. Whole wheat pasta with chicken and tomatoes is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Cyprus meatball recipe; Grate the potatoes and squeeze the juice into a bowl. Grate the onion, add all the other ingredients and knead. Place the meatballs on the baking tray. Take them out of the oven when they are browned. Cyprus meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for pancakes with dates and bananas; First, soak the dates in hot water and peel them. Then mix all the ingredients well. Cook on both sides by pouring a spoonful of dough into a skillet heated with a teaspoon of oil. Date banana pancake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Potato Dish recipe; First, boil the potatoes, peel and mash them. Finely chop the parsley and add to the mashed potatoes. Squeeze the lemon, mix well and add the salt. Finally, shape the bowl. For the inside, grate the carrot and roast it on the stove with olive oil. Put the carrot inside into the bowls you have prepared. Drizzle yogurt on top. After adding mint and chili pepper on it, the potato dish is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the bat recipe; First of all, boil the lentils in a deep saucepan until soft. Thin bulgur is put on the boiled lentils and mixed. Finely chop the onion and all the greens and add to the pot. Mix the tomato paste in cold water and liquefy it. Add tomato paste to the pot and add salt and spices. Add some more water and mix. Bat is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the wheat purslane salad recipe; Soak the wheat the night before. Boil until soft the next day. Wash and strain again. Put finely chopped scallions, red and green peppers, parsley, dill, and purslane in a deep bowl and mix. Add coarsely chopped walnuts, pickled cucumbers cut into small cubes and boiled corn. After adding the wheat, mix it well again. In a separate bowl, mix olive oil, lemon juice, salt and thyme. Pour it over your prepared salad. After mixing for the last time, purslane salad with wheat is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the cinnamon cocoa chia seed pudding recipe; Put all the ingredients except the cinnamon in a saucepan and cook on low heat, stirring constantly, until it thickens. When it reaches the consistency of pudding, turn off the heat and add cinnamon on it. Cinnamon cocoa chia seed pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the semolina crispy kadayif balls recipe; Put the milk, semolina, starch, sugar in a saucepan and cook until it reaches a thick consistency. Take a deep bowl and mix the vanilla and butter. While the mixture is cooling, put the oil in the pan on the other side and add the crumbled kadayıf and fry it on low heat for 10 minutes. Add powdered sugar and cinnamon, mix and turn off the stove.
