Take a piece of the cooled milky semolina, give it a round shape with your hand and rub it into the kadayıf. Lay on a flat plate and leave in the refrigerator for an hour. Crispy kadayif balls with semolina are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for haddock with vegetables in the oven; Slice the fillet haddock lengthwise. Sprinkle salt on it and leave it for 20 minutes. Clean the stems and seeds of the red and green peppers and chop them lengthwise. Cut the cherry tomatoes into quarters. After chopping the spring onions, put all the ingredients except the spices on the baking tray and bake in the oven preheated to 180 degrees for 20 minutes. Add salt, pepper, thyme and red pepper flakes to taste. The haddock with vegetables in the oven is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for eggplant with chicken in the oven; First of all, cut the aubergines in the middle and hollow out the insides. Take the bitterness away by soaking it in salt water for about 15-20 minutes. Then take it out of the brine, wash and dry it and fry it in oil. Finely chop the onions and fry them in oil. Add the diced chicken breast and continue frying. Peel the skins of the tomatoes, chop them into small pieces and add them to the mixture. After adding the spices and salt, remove from the heat. For the sauce we will pour over it, grate the tomatoes and fry them in oil, add water and a small amount of salt and stir until it boils. Put the chicken mortar in the fried eggplants, pour the tomato sauce on it, add the grated cheddar and put it in the preheated 180-degree oven. When you take it out of the oven, the aubergine with chicken in the oven is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For Homemade Hazelnut Lahmacun recipe; Put water, olive oil, salt, brown sugar and yeast in a bowl and mix. Add flour on it, knead it, cover it and leave it for 1 hour in a warm place. While the dough is fermenting, finely chop the parsley, chop the peppers and put all the remaining ingredients in a large bowl and mix well. Knead the fermented dough again and put it out and break into walnut-sized pieces. Open it in the size of a tea plate on a lightly floured counter. Heat the Teflon pan, set the stove to medium heat, and place the dough in the pan. Put 1 teaspoon of the mortar on the dough and spread it on the dough. Close the lid of the pan and cook for about 4 minutes, checking to ensure that the gold does not burn. Homemade Hazelnut Lahmacun is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

Raisin Gummy Custard, pour the milk into a saucepan. Mix all other ingredients except raisins in a bowl. Cut the raisins in half and boil until soft. Slowly add the other ingredients to the milk. Turn off the bottom when the pudding thickens and does not slip. Sprinkle cinnamon to garnish. Gummy custard with raisins is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the yoghurt spinach recipe, wash the spinach thoroughly and chop finely. Fry the onions in olive oil in a pan until golden brown. After frying, add the tomato paste and water. After 3-4 minutes, add salt and pepper and mix. Add the spinach and fry them until they release their water. After roasting, take the chard on a serving plate and pour the garlic yogurt on it. Chard with yogurt is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the wheat flour pancake recipe; Pass all the ingredients through the blender. Cook the dough, which is ready in 3 minutes, in a Teflon pan with the help of 1 ladle. Wheat Flour Pancake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the gluten-free banana and cranberry crumble recipe; In a deep bowl, mix the banana slices, cranberries and starch. Divide the mixture into 4 baking dishes. To prepare it; In a separate bowl, mix the crumbled cookies, hazelnuts and butter. Spread the mixture over the bananas, press down lightly. Bake in a preheated oven at 180C for 15-20 minutes. Optionally, you can serve it with vanilla ice cream. Enjoy your meal.

For the Vegetarian Cauliflower Gratin recipe; Wash and shred the cauliflower thoroughly. Boil it in water with lemon squeezed in it. Remove the cooked cauliflower immediately by straining it without waiting in the boiling water. Arrange the cauliflower on a baking tray lined with baking paper. Sprinkle 8 teaspoons of grated cheddar cheese and red pepper on top. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven until the cheddar is melted. Vegetarian cauliflower gratin is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the sweetened gummy custard recipe; Put the sweetener and milk in a saucepan and mix. Put water, starch, mastic gum and rice flour in a separate bowl and crush the ingredients. Slowly add the crushed material to the pot. Cook on medium heat until it thickens. When it thickens, turn off the heat and stir occasionally until it cools. Gummy custard with sweetener is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the yufkada pasha kebab recipe; Chop the chicken as a bird's head. Cook in a saucepan for 15-16 minutes, stirring occasionally. Then salt and garnish are added respectively. Cook by closing the lid of the pot. After the meat is cooked, the onions are added. Add black pepper and cayenne pepper, mix well and take it off the fire after 1-2 minutes. Cut the dough into four equal parts. Put a filling in the middle of each piece of dough. Bow well and wrap the phyllo in the form of a roll or a bundle. Brush egg yolk on the phyllo and fry them on the baking tray until they are cooked. Pasha kebab in yufka is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the milk celery soup recipe; Chop the onion for cooking and fry it lightly in oil, then add the carrot, zucchini and potatoes, reduce the heat and peel the celery, chop it and add it to the pot. Turn on the fire, put 7 glasses of hot water, add salt, and when it boils, cook for about 25 more minutes on medium heat. Blend it. Warm a glass of milk first, then add it to the soup by mixing it. Close the bottom of the soup. Celery soup with milk is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the walnut Tulum Cheese Noodles recipe; Boil water in a pot and salt it. Drop the noodles into boiling water and cook for 8-10 minutes until tender. Mix the finely chopped parsley with the crumbled Tulum cheese. Add walnuts and garlic. Mix all the ingredients. Drain the noodles using a colander and set aside. Add olive oil to a medium saucepan. Add the noodles and the cheese walnut mixture to the pot and heat for 1-2 minutes until the cheese melts slightly. Add paprika and mix it. Transfer your walnut and tulum cheese noodles to a serving plate and serve immediately. Walnut Tulum Cheese Noodles is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the orange cake recipe, beat the sugar and egg in a bowl until well mixed. Then add the olive oil, milk and orange juice and continue whisking. After mixing, add the flour gradually, and then add the baking powder. Grate the peel of 1 orange and add it to the cake batter. Pour the mixture into the pre-oiled oven cake mold. Bake at 150 degrees for 50 minutes. Orange cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For buckwheat pilaf with vegetables; olive oil and diced onions are put in the pan, when the color of the onions changes, garlic, grated tomatoes and diced pepper are added. Cook for 5 minutes and add buckwheat. It turns a little. Add 2 glasses of hot water and then add the spices. It is ready to serve when the water is absorbed. Enjoy your meal

For the mock pancake recipe, mix the finely chopped parsley with curd cheese, chili pepper and salt. Spread the dough on the table, divide it into two and spread the prepared dough squarely in the middle of the dough. Cover the dough squarely from right to left, from top to bottom, and fry it in a pan with 1 teaspoon of oil. The fake pancake is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the katmer meatball recipe; Cook the rice in a steel pot with 5 glasses of water on low heat. Boil the carrots and potatoes in another pot. Crush the boiled ingredients and mix them with currants. Add rice, black pepper, red pepper, salt and some flour to this mixture. These ingredients are formed into egg-sized meatballs. It is dipped in previously beaten eggs and fried in hot oil. Fried rice meatballs are placed on a serving plate and garnished with red pepper and parsley. Enjoy your meal.

For the lemon cup recipe, beat the egg well. Add lemon zest, juice of one lemon, milk, oil, vanilla and honey and mix. Add the flour and baking powder to the mixture by sifting, mix. It is poured into a greased cake mold and baked in a preheated oven at 160 degrees until golden brown. The lemon cup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the chocolate roll recipe, melt the yeast by adding the fresh yeast, sugar and warm milk to a bowl. Hold for a couple of minutes. Add the egg white, olive oil and salt to the bowl. Add the flour slowly and sifted into the bowl. Add flour and knead until you get a soft dough that does not stick to the hand. Cover the dough with a cloth and leave it for about half an hour to leaven. Divide the fermented dough into 5 meringues and roll the meringues. Open the meringues to the width of a tea plate with the help of your hand. Add in the chocolate chips. By wrapping it in the form of a roll, holding both ends of the dough and moving both hands in opposite directions, curl it. Combine the ends well and place them on the baking tray on which you have greased paper. Brush with egg yolk and sprinkle with black cumin, if desired. Bake at 200 degrees for 15-20 minutes. Chocolate opening is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal:)

For the cranberry tart recipe; Put 1 tablespoon of sugar and milk in a saucepan and mix. Put 1 glass of water, starch, mastic gum and rice flour in a separate bowl and crush the ingredients. Slowly add the crushed ingredients to the pot. Cook over medium heat until it thickens. When it thickens, turn off the heat and stir occasionally until it cools down. The tart pudding is ready. For the topping, boil 2 cups of cranberries with 1.5 cups of water and thicken. For the batter, mix oat bran, half a teaspoon of brown sugar, 1 teaspoon of salt, an egg, 1 tea glass of cold water and half a tea glass of butter. Spread the dough into the tart mold and put it in the oven. Bake at 180 degrees for 30 minutes. Then, pour the custard into the tart dough you have cooked and the dried fruit that has been boiled on it. Serve after resting in the refrigerator. Enjoy your meal

For the creamy chicken recipe, put olive oil in a Teflon pan and sauté the diced or julienne chicken in hot oil for 2-3 minutes, cover the pot and cook the chickens on low heat until the water they release is absorbed. Pour the liquid cream over the drained chickens. Pour the cream according to the amount of chickens. After adding the cream, you can take it off the stove after the food boils. Creamy chicken is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the pasta salad recipe, boil the pasta. After boiling, drain the water and shock with cold water. In a large bowl, mix the garnish, salt, yogurt and mayonnaise. After adding the pasta and mixing it well, the marakna salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Tuna Pasta recipe, boil the pasta. After boiling, drain the water and shock with cold water. In a large bowl, strain the pasta and oil and mix the tuna fish you added thoroughly. Tuna Pasta is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Sweetened Lemon Pudding recipe; Mix the flour, sweetener and salt. Add lemon juice and grated lemon peel to the mixture. Beat the yolks of the eggs, separating them from the whites and add milk to it. Add the flour mixture to the milk. Beat the egg whites with a mixer and turn them into snow. Gently mix the beaten egg whites and other mixture and bake for 50 minutes in a bain-marie (baking pans are placed in a baking tray filled with water) in a preheated oven at 150°C. Serve pudding garnished with cinnamon powder and lemon zest. Enjoy your meal

For the Lentil Spinach recipe; Chop the onion for food and fry it in olive oil. Finely chop the garlic and add to the onions. Add the tomato paste and cook for 1-2 minutes. Wash the spinach in plenty of water, chop it and add it to the pot. Wash the green lentils and bulgur and add to the spinach. Add the spices and hot water and cook on the stove. Lentil Spinach is ready. Enjoy your meal

For the Cheese Ravioli recipe; Take the flour into a large glass bowl and make a pool in the middle. Add the eggs, salt and olive oil into the pool and mix it gently with the flour. Knead the whole mixture until it becomes a dough. Cover the dough with a cloth and leave it in the refrigerator for 1 hour. Combine grated ricotta, mozzarella and parmesan in a glass bowl and mix well. Take the dough out of the refrigerator, divide it into 4 equal parts and roll it with your hands. Open the rounded meringues thinly with the help of a rolling pin. Put the cheese mixture on the dough at regular intervals and cover the second dough on the dough on which you put the cheeses and cut it to the size you want with the kitchen roulette. Arrange the cut ravioli on a floured tray. Boil 2 liters of water in a deep saucepan and add salt to the boiled water. Boil the ravioli in hot water for 5 minutes. Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese when serving. Enjoy your meal.
For macaroni with cheese, boil the macaroni. After boiling, drain the water and shock with cold water. Mix the macaroni and cheese well in a large bowl. Cheese pasta is ready to serve. Bon appetit :)

For Baked Mushrooms, first the stems are removed, and then they are peeled with the help of a knife. First, butter and then all the spices are added in order. Bake for 10 minutes in a preheated oven at 200 degrees. Add grated cheddar cheese and bake again until golden brown. Oven mushrooms are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)
Put the ingredients in the sandwich bread.

For the blueberry cake recipe; Whisk eggs and sugar in a bowl. Then add all the ingredients except the blueberries and mix. Add the blueberries last and mix by hand. Bake in the oven at 170 degrees for 30 minutes. Your blueberry muffin is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the curd cheese and mint cake recipe; Thoroughly mix all ingredients except curd cheese and dried mint. Finally, add the curd cheese and dried mint. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 45 minutes. Curd cheese and mint cake is ready. Enjoy your meal.

Chicken stuffed with spinach and mushrooms; Put olive oil, mushrooms and spinach in a saucepan and fry. Line the chicken breasts with parchment paper and place them on the baking tray. Cut off the tops diagonally and put the mushroom and spinach roast in the cuts. Bake in an oven at 200 degrees for 1 hour. Chicken stuffed with spinach and mushrooms is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the Pomegranate Jam recipe; Put the butter and pomegranate seeds in the pan and fry them until the water is gone. Add granulated sugar and mix until the sugar dissolves. When the sugar dissolves, add the water and boil it until it thickens. When it thickens, add lemon salt, boil for 1-2 more minutes and turn off the heat. Fill the Pomegranate Jam into jars. Pomegranate jam is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chia seed cookie recipe with dates; Mix the melted butter with the beaten egg in a bowl. Soak dried dates in hot water to soften them and then slice them into small pieces. Then pour all the ingredients on top of the buttered egg mixture and mix. Arrange on the greased paper-lined tray, with or without shaping. Bake in a 180 degree oven for 16 minutes. Your date chia seed cookie is ready. Enjoy your meal.

For the raisin and coconut cookie recipe; Mix the honey and melted butter. Combine other ingredients in the same bowl. Arrange in small pieces on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 24 minutes. Cookie with raisins and coconut is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the roasted eggplant hash recipe, make a few scratches on the eggplants and roast them in the oven. Then peel and crush them lightly. Strain the water and mix it with eggs, crumbled curd cheese, and randomly shredded phyllo. Pour into a baking dish and add grated low-fat cheddar cheese, salt and pepper. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees until the top is browned. Roasted aubergine is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the dried fruit chicken saute recipe; Chop the chicken meat coarsely. After washing the dried apricots and plums, roughly divide them into several pieces. Add olive oil to a large pan with a lid, when the oil is hot, add the shallots and unshelled almonds and fry them until they turn brown. Add the diced chicken meat to the pan. Fry for 5-6 minutes on high heat. Add fresh thyme sprigs whole. Add the honey, continue mixing by shaking. When the honey melts, add the hot chicken stock and cook on low heat for 15 minutes with the lid of the pot closed. Then add the apple cider vinegar and all the dried fruits and mix. Add salt and freshly ground black pepper. Cook for another 10 minutes with the lid of the pot open if there is too much water, and with the lid of the pot closed if the water is low. Then remove the thyme sprig. Dried Fruit Chicken Saute is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For the turkey zucchini shrimp recipe; Scrape and wash the tops of the zucchini, cut them into thin slices from the bottom lengthwise to keep them comfortable on the tray. Play in such a way that they can be filled in the middle. Arrange the zucchini on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper and rub 1 tablespoon of olive oil all over the zucchini. Then fry the zucchini in the oven. On the one hand, turn the cubed turkey meat in a Teflon pan for 3-4 minutes. Put the butter and olive oil in the pan, fry the meat for 1-2 minutes when the oil melts and fry for about 1-2 minutes, then add the onion that you have cut into small cubes by sorting, washing and frying for 3-4 minutes until the onion loses its vitality. Then add the washed and julienne cut red pepper, chopped garlic and sauté in this way for 3-4 minutes. Add the spinach that you have cleaned, washed and chopped in medium thickness to the pan. Add the black pepper and salt and continue to sauté all together for 3-4 minutes until the spinach is slightly dead and turn off the stove. Pull the walnuts from the robot to a medium thickness and mix them by adding them to the mortar. Your heart is ready. Lightly salt the inside of the zucchini you have fried in the oven with the help of a salt shaker and fill the zucchini with the mortar you prepared. Place the baking dish in the oven and bake at 230 degrees for 20-25 minutes. It can be served with yoghurt upon request. Enjoy your meal.

For the apple pie sticks recipe; Spread the baklava phyllo on the table in pairs and apply the sunflower oil to the phyllo with the help of a brush and divide the phyllo in half lengthwise. Then wash the apples, peel and grate them, cook with walnut kernels, sugar and 1 teaspoon cinnamon. Lay the cooked mixture on one side of the phyllo in strips. Roll the dough 1.5 inches thick. Bake in the oven at 180 degrees for about 20 minutes until the rolls are golden brown. Remove from the oven and sprinkle the remaining 1 teaspoon of cinnamon on top. Apple pie sticks are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Yogurt Zucchini Soup Recipe; Wash and dice the zucchini and put them in the pot. Clean the onion and cut it into cubes in the same way and add it to the pot. Wash the dill and cut it into 2-3 pieces and add it to the pot. Finally, let it cook with salt, pepper and 4 glasses of water, turn off the stove after 15-20 minutes when they are all soft. Pass the cooked material through the blender and boil it again. Clean the garlic, crush it and add it to your yogurt. Whisk the yogurt, add it to the soup, bring it to a boil and turn off the stove. Zucchini soup with yogurt is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the puff pastry recipe, divide the puff pastry vertically into five slices. After washing the zucchini, draw lines on the outer surfaces with a fork, slice very thinly and cut into half moons. Drizzle some salt, ground black pepper and olive oil on it and mix. Arrange the zucchini on the strip puff pastry, sprinkle with curd cheese and roll it with your hands. Spread egg yolk around the flower-shaped dough and bake in the oven at 180 degrees for 15-20 minutes. Rose pastry with puff pastry is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)
Clean and slice the acorn. Line the baking tray with greaseproof paper and line the salted bonito. sprinkle thyme on top. Bake in the oven at 200 degrees. Serve with lettuce salad. Bon appetit.

Menengic coffee recipe; For a coffee cup of milk, put a teaspoon of menengiç coffee in the coffee pot and bring it to a boil over low heat. Divide into coffee cups. Menengic Coffee is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

Menengic coffee recipe; For a coffee cup of milk, put a teaspoon of menengiç coffee in the coffee pot and bring it to a boil over low heat. Wait a minute and add the sugar. Divide into coffee cups. Menengic Coffee is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the sugar-free pumpkin pudding recipe, put the sliced zucchini in a large saucepan, add enough water to cover them, and boil them until they soften. Mash the boiled pumpkin thoroughly with water. Add milk, whole wheat flour and egg and mix with a mixer. Cook on medium heat until it boils. Finally, add honey and vanilla and mix once more. Divide the mixture into bowls. After it comes to room temperature, leave it in the refrigerator for 1-2 hours. If desired, you can decorate it with hazelnuts, pistachios and coconut. Sugar-free pumpkin pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the eggplant pizza recipe; Start heating the oven at 200 degrees. Meanwhile, wash the sliced eggplants and dry them with a paper towel. Then brush the eggplants with olive oil and sprinkle with salt and pepper, then bake in the preheated oven for about 20 minutes. Meanwhile, crush 1 clove of garlic and add the tomato sauce. After the eggplants are well cooked and tender, add the tomato mixture, grated cheese, sliced cherry tomatoes and basil in order. Then return it to the oven and bake until the cheese melts. You can serve the eggplant pizza hot without waiting. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken wrap recipe with mozzarella; Cut the chicken into thin pieces and spread on the baking sheet. Arrange the randomly divided mozzarella slices on top. Put the melted butter, cayenne pepper, thyme, a quarter teaspoon of salt, pepper and crushed garlic in a bowl, mix and pour the spicy sauce you prepared on the chicken and roll it. Put the chicken stock and the remaining 1/4 teaspoon of salt in another bowl, mix and drizzle over the chicken rolls that have taken their final shape. Then, cover the rolls with breadcrumbs and bake them in the preheated oven until golden brown and transfer them to the serving plate. Mozzarella chicken wrap is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the dark chocolate orange slice recipe, melt the dark chocolate in a bain-marie. Slice the oranges. Dip the sliced oranges into the melted chocolate. Garnish with nutmeg. Orange slices with dark chocolate are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the olive and mushroom pizza recipe; Add dry yeast to whole wheat flour. Add warm water little by little and knead a soft dough that does not stick to the hand. Close your mouth and let it ferment for 45 minutes. At the end of the time, roll out with a rolling pin or rolling pin the size of a cake plate, apply tomato sauce, sprinkle with olives and mushrooms. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for about 20 minutes, sprinkle the cheddar cheese in the last 5 minutes of the cooking time. Olive and mushroom pizza is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the smoked meat lavash pizza recipe; Open the lavash bread on a greased tray and apply tomato sauce. Spread the smoked meat that you mixed with black pepper on it evenly. Place the finely chopped green peppers. After sprinkling the last of the cheddar cheese, bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for about 10 minutes. Smoked meat lavash pizza is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the cauliflower-based tuna pizza recipe; Wash and separate the cauliflower. Pull until it becomes a grain of rice in the rondoda. In this state, boil it in water for about 15 minutes, then strain it thoroughly. Add salt, pepper, egg and half a cup of cheddar cheese and knead like dough. Spread it with your palm on the baking tray that you have lined with greaseproof paper. Spread tomato sauce on top and sprinkle the tuna. Chop the red onion into rings and add that too. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for about 15-20 minutes. Don't forget to add the remaining cup of cheddar cheese near the end of the cooking time. Cauliflower-based tuna pizza is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the beet and egg toast recipe; Boil the beets and mash them. Add 1 clove of garlic and salt and rub it on the inside of the toast breads. Then put the boiled and sliced ​​eggs on the bread. After heating in the toaster, beetroot and egg toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the honey almond and apple toast recipe; After warming the breads, apply the honey to the bread. Then put the thinly sliced apples on it and sprinkle the powdered almonds on it, then the honey almond and apple toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the avocado and pumpkin seed toast recipe; mash the avocado with a fork and sprinkle with black pepper with the tip of a knife. Spread the mashed avocado on the bread you heated in the toaster and pour the pumpkin seeds on it. Avocado and pumpkin seed toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the tomato basil toast recipe with feta cheese; Add black pepper to the tomatoes. Spread 1 slice of feta cheese on the bread and add fresh basil leaves along with the tomatoes. Toast with white cheese, tomato and basil is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.
For the tropical toast recipe; Heated whole grain breads. Then, after adding the sliced banana, pineapple and coconut, the tropical toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Arabaşı soup recipe, add five glasses of water and a teaspoon of salt to the pot and bring it to a boil. Put 1 glass of flour, 2 glasses of cold water in a bowl and mix well to avoid lumps. Slowly pour the flour-water mixture into the water you boiled. Pour the dough into a shallow tray and wait for it to cool. Cut the rested dough so that it is not very small. Put half of the tomato paste in the pot and dilute it. Add chicken breast, red pepper flakes and a pinch of salt and cook until tender. Cut the cooked chicken breast into small pieces. Fry the oil and flour in the pan. Add the remaining tomato paste and fry for 2-3 minutes. Pour the mixture you made over the chicken breast and cook for another 5 minutes. Take the soup into a serving bowl and add the dough you prepared. Drizzle lemon juice over it and sprinkle with mint. Arabaşı soup is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Kete recipe; Transfer dry yeast and sugar cubes to a bowl with warm water. When the yeast rises, add 1 glass of oil, milk, granulated sugar, salt and flour as much as it takes and knead until it reaches the consistency of an earlobe. Then leave the dough to ferment. Melt the butter, add 1 tea glass of oil to it and let it cool. Meanwhile, grind the walnuts. Make sure it is neither too big nor too small. In the meantime, separate the fermented dough into small balls, roll them and put them on the tray. Cover it and wait for it to ferment a little more. Flour the meringues one by one and open them thinly. Spread about 3 spoons of oil mixture on the dough and spread it with the help of a brush to feed it all over. Roll out a sheet of dough on it again and apply oil. Do the same at the top. Cut the dough into strips, with 3 layers of dough, oiled between and on top, at the level of 4 fingers on top of the knee. Roll the strips you cut by wrapping them with your four fingers without squeezing them. Glue the gold with your hand so that it does not spill out because you are going to put walnuts on it. For each flake, add the walnut kernels with the tip of the tablespoon and cover with a slight puckering. After applying the same process to all the strips one by one, put them on the tray. Cover the tray with a cloth so that it does not dry out and let it rest for 15-20 minutes. Lay the rested flakes on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper, brush with egg yolk, and put them in the preheated 180-degree oven. Cook until browned. Keteler is ready to serve, enjoy your meal.

For the oven-baked ladybudu meatball recipe; First, put 1 bowl of boiled rice or cooked rice in a large bowl. Add half of the ground beef and knead. Then add the chopped parsley and spices and knead well. Then leave the dough you kneaded to rest in the refrigerator. On another side, put the oil in the pan, add the chopped onions and fry until the onions turn pink. Add the remaining raw minced meat at the end and fry it well. Mix the onion mixture you roasted and the rice mixture you kept waiting. Lay greaseproof paper on the tray. Shape the meatballs into large convex shapes, dip them in the two eggs you whisked and then in the breadcrumbs and place them on the tray. Bake in the oven at 190 degrees until golden brown and take it out of the oven. Meatballs in the oven are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the apple pizza recipe; First of all, mix oat paste, oat bran, oat flour, tahini, vanilla and almond milk in a bowl until it becomes a dough. Then bake in the oven heated to 160 degrees for 15 minutes. Take it out of the oven and slice the apples on top. Spread the honey and cinnamon on the sliced ​​apples. Finally, add the walnuts and bake for another 10 minutes. Apple pizza is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the cheddar pumpkin recipe; First, peel the pumpkin and cut it into cubes. Boil for about 15 minutes. Whisk together the mustard and milk. Grate the cheddar. Mix all the prepared ingredients well in a baking dish. Put it in a preheated oven at 175 degrees and bake for 20-30 minutes. Cheddar pumpkin is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the apple banana quinoa muffin recipe; First of all, grate 2 apples and cook them in the pot. Add cinnamon and mix, then let it cool. Boil the quinoa. Mix honey, milk, boiled quinoa, cinnamon, vanilla, diced apple, oat flour, mash 3 bananas and mix the mashed banana and applesauce. Divide the mortar equally into the muffin molds that you have greased beforehand and place banana slices on it and bake at 180 degrees for 30-35 minutes. Apple banana quinoa muffin is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.
For the energy balls cookie recipe; Mix all the ingredients, knead. Bake in the oven at 160 degrees until the top is golden brown. Energy ball cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the peanut butter chia balls recipe; First, mix the peanut butter, honey, and vanilla. Then add the chia and peanuts. Keep in the refrigerator for 15 minutes. After it hardens a little, roll it into a ball. Dip some of it in melted dark chocolate and put it in the refrigerator for another 15 minutes. Peanut butter chia balls are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the quinoa pudding recipe; First, put the milk in a saucepan and start heating it. Add the cinnamon stick, vanilla seeds and stick into the milk. When it starts to boil, add the washed quinoa. Cook, stirring occasionally, until the mixture turns into a pudding. When it reaches the consistency, remove the cinnamon stick and vanilla and add honey. After mixing well, serve in bowls and leave to cool. After it cools, you can add either cinnamon or a fruit. Quinoa pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chia seed pudding; First of all, add chia seeds and honey to the milk you take in a large bowl and start cooking. Stir constantly so that the seeds do not stick together. After cooking for about 1 hour, let the milk mixture rest. While the seed mixture is resting, grate the peaches. Put some pudding, some peaches in the serving bowl. Chia seed pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the chia seed pumpkin cookie recipe; Put the pumpkin in a saucepan and cook it without adding sugar. Make sure there are no lumps left. After the cooking process is finished, add all the remaining ingredients to the pumpkins and mix. Then, with the help of a spoon, lay the mixture on the tray in the form of a cookie. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for about 30 minutes. You can check if it's done by inserting a toothpick into it. When the toothpick comes out clean, your cookies are done. Chia seed pumpkin cookies are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the goji berry cake recipe; Beat all the ingredients in a mixing bowl with the help of a mixer. Bake in a preheated 175 degree oven for 30-40 minutes. Goji berry cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

oat To make Flour Pancakes; Mix oat flour, baking powder, vanillin, honey and salt. In a separate bowl, whisk the milk and eggs. Mix the oat flour mixture with the milk mixture. Finally, add the softened coconut oil. Heat a Teflon pan with oil, pour a ladle of the pancake mix, and fry on both sides. Repeat this process until the mixture is finished. Your pancakes are ready. You can serve.

For the purple pasta salad recipe; Boil half a pack of pasta. Soak in the beet juice that you prepared beforehand to turn purple. After making sure that the pasta gets the color; Mix it with tuna, corn, pickled cucumbers. Finally, sprinkle with fresh basil and the cherry tomatoes cut in half to garnish. Purple pasta salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

Mix 50 grams of coconut oil, 3 tablespoons of honey, 2 eggs, baking powder and vanilla, lemon juice, zest of 1 lemon, gluten-free flour, almond flour, 2 tablespoons of almond milk and poppy seeds until it becomes a homogeneous mixture. It is divided into 10 suitable oven molds and baked in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 35 minutes. Then, in a separate bowl, mix 1 glass of cream and 2 tablespoons of honey to decorate. This mixture is divided into 10 and placed on top of the cupcakes that have come out of the oven and have cooled. Finally, it is made ready for service by giving various shapes from sugar paste in order to decorate it.

Pate Choux Dough Recipe: Melt 1/2 cup of coconut milk, 1/2 cup of wholemeal flour, and 1/4 cup of coconut oil on the stovetop. When the milk boils, add the salt and mix the mixture well with the help of a spatula. Cook the mixture, which has reached the consistency of dough, for 1 more minute by crushing it with a spatula. Cool the dough thoroughly. Set the oven to 190 degrees fanless program. Take the cooled dough into the whisk. Add the eggs one by one. Finally, put the dough in a piping bag. Line a baking tray with greaseproof paper. Cut the mouth of the piping bag with scissors and squeeze into 40 pieces of dough in medium-length strips. Bake for 12-15 minutes until the dough has doubled in size. Cream Recipe: Mix 1 glass of coconut milk, 2 tablespoons of honey and 1 packet of vanilla on medium heat on the stove until it gets a creamy consistency. When the cream starts to boil, take it off the stove and let it cool. Spread a thin layer between the dough you have prepared before. Chocolate Ganache Recipe: 1/2 cup of coconut milk, dark chocolate and 1 tablespoon of honey are melted in a bain-marie and left to warm and then spread over the eclairs.

For toast with basil and red pepper pickles, hard boil the egg. Cut 1 leaf of lettuce. Chop the pickled red pepper into small slices. Divide the disposable cheese into two equal parts. Take 1 slice of toast bread and place the ingredients in order. Cover the 2nd slice of toast bread. Toast with basil, egg and pickled red pepper is ready for the recipe. Enjoy your meal.

For the honey-peach compote recipe; Peel the peaches, remove the seeds and cut into large cubes. Put the water and cloves in a pot. Stir on medium heat. When the water boils, add the chopped peaches and continue boiling for 10-12 minutes. When the peaches are soft, turn off the heat and remove from the stove. Add the honey and mix well. Keep it at room temperature and then put it in the refrigerator to cool. Divide the cooled peach compote into bowls. Peach compote is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the honey strawberry compote recipe; Wash the strawberries thoroughly. Put the water, cinnamon and cloves in a saucepan. Stir on medium heat. When the water boils, add the strawberries and continue boiling for 10-12 minutes. When the strawberries are soft, turn off the heat and remove from the stove. Add the honey and mix well. Keep it at room temperature and then put it in the refrigerator to cool. Divide the cooled strawberry compote into bowls. Honey strawberry compote is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the honey raisin compote recipe; wash the raisins. Put the water, cinnamon and cloves in a saucepan. Stir on medium heat. When the water boils, add the raisins and continue boiling for 10-12 minutes. When the raisins are soft, turn off the heat and remove from the stove. Add the honey and mix well. Keep it at room temperature and then put it in the refrigerator to cool. Divide the cooled raisin compote into bowls. Honey raisin compote is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the honey apple compote recipe; Peel the apple, remove the peel and cut the apple into cubes. Then boil it with 1 glass of water. After the water boils and the apples soften, discard the cloves. After boiling for a while, take it off the stove and add the honey. After cooling, the honey apple compote is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the stuffed artichoke recipe; Cut off the bottoms of the artichokes, tear off two rows of large leaves at the bottom and discard. Then cut off the ends at the top. Boil the artichokes in boiling water with a squeeze of salt and 1 lemon for 15 minutes. With the help of a knife, separate the outer part of the artichoke and discard the hard part. For the Spinach Dip Sauce; Combine the previously boiled spinach with salt, pepper, olive oil, garlic, basil, garlic powder, your pre-melted white and fresh cheddar cheese. Finally, we hollow it out with the help of a spoon. Stuffed artichokes are ready to serve. You can consume the artichoke by dipping it in the dip sauce. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach mincemeat recipe; First, fry the ground beef in butter. Add the finely chopped onions and continue frying. Then put all the ingredients except the spinach in the pot and continue cooking. Add the last half a glass of water and finely chopped parsley and cook the spinach so that it does not die too much. Spinach mince is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the mincemeat recipe; First, fry the ground beef in butter. Then add the finely chopped onions and continue frying. Then add the bacon and continue sautéing. Cook by adding all the remaining ingredients and half a glass of water last. Ground beef with bacon is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the spinach pancake recipe; Finely chop the spinach first. Take the egg in a bowl and whisk, add yoghurt and salt to get a foamy foam and continue beating. Then add the whole wheat flour, baking powder and carbonate that you have foamed by dripping lemon into the mixture and whisk well. Lastly, add the finely chopped spinach and curd cheese to the mixture and flatten it well with the help of a spatula. Heat a pan and spread olive oil with a napkin. Then, take 1 ladle of the mortar you prepared, spread it in a thin layer on the pan and cook both sides. Spinach pancakes are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the fig dessert recipe; First, soak the dried figs in water until they soften. After they soften, cut off their heads and put the ground walnuts in it with the help of a dessert spoon. Place the stuffed figs in a pot and pour them over the figs that mix milk and a quarter of a glass of water with sugar. Add the cinnamon stick last and cook until the milk-water mixture absorbs. Fig dessert is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the flatbread recipe, mix the flour, yeast, salt and sugar. Gradually add 2 cups of warm water. Add in a controlled manner and stop adding when the consistency holds. Then bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees. Base is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the asparagus baked salad, boil the buckwheat and set aside to cool. Then roast the green bell pepper and the red pepper and peel them. Saute the mushrooms in a pan without oil and chop the asparagus into small pieces. Mix all the ingredients in a bowl and add oil and salt. Asparagus baked salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for Hot Salad with Purslane; Boil the quinoa and set aside 1 cup of cooked quinoa. Turn the previously sliced ​​mushrooms and onions in a pan without oil. Wash and sort the purslane. Heat 1 handful of washed purslane with mushrooms and onions in a pan without oil for another 5 minutes. In a clean plate, add the quinoa and fresh curd to the purslane mixture. Hot Salad with Purslane is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For the Red Plum Parfait recipe, finely chop the plums and start cooking them in a hot pan with 50 ml of mustard. When it is well caramelized and the sauce is absorbed, remove from the stove. Spread the granola on the bottom of the mug. Mix yoghurt and labneh in a separate bowl. Spread this mixture over the granola. Drizzle peanuts on it, pour caramelized plums, and finally, pour 1 teaspoon of honey on it. Repeat this sequence. Red Plum Parfait is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chicken Shish and Watermelon Salad recipe; First, mix the chickens with mustard, yogurt and olive oil in a bowl for marination, stretch them and leave them in the fridge for 1 hour. Mix all the remaining ingredients for the salad. For chicken skewers, take your chicken out of the cabinet, line it up in bottles and cook it all over in an oil-free grill pan. Chicken Shish and Watermelon Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Goat Cheese and Red Plum Toast recipe; Toast whole grain breads. Chop the red plums and onion into thin slices. First, start cooking the onions in a hot pan without oil on medium heat, add the plums that are close to pink, and pour 50 grams of mustard on it. After it is thoroughly cooked, first place a slice of thin goat cheese on the toasted bread and drizzle a teaspoon of honey. Spread the caramelized onion and red plum mixture on top. Goat Cheese and Red Plum Toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Quinoa Salad with Soy Sauce; First, boil the quinoa so that it does not remain raw. Mix all the chopped ingredients and quinoa in a bowl, add soy sauce and your spices and mix the salad well. Quinoa Salad with Soy Sauce is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Quinoa Meatballs recipe; Chop the onion into small cubes. Boil the quinoa. Mix all the ingredients in the mixing bowl and add the spices you want. Shape it with your hands and cook it in a low-oil pan.

For the Lentil Salad recipe; First, boil the lentils. Chop the onion and pepper into thin slices and sauté in a preheated pan. Add the tomatoes last and sauté for 2-3 more minutes, then remove from the fire. Mix the ingredients in a salad bowl and add the salt. Lentil Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Strawberry Chocolate Fondue recipe; Melt the chocolates in a bain-marie. Then add the cream to the melted chocolate. Finally, add the vanilla syrup and mix well. Arrange the strawberries next to them. Strawberry Chocolate Fondue is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Banana Chocolate Fondue recipe; Melt the chocolates in a bain-marie in a saucepan. Then add the cream to the melted chocolate. Finally, add the vanilla syrup and mix well. Arrange the bananas next to them. Banana Chocolate Fondue is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe of Kütahya Pie; Knead a dough that will not stick to the hand with flour, water and salt. Let rest for 10 minutes, then divide into 5 meringues. If your tray is small, make 6 meringues. Soak them in a mixture of liquid and margarine. Open the large coffee cup until the saucer and leave it for 1 night. Open one by one the next day. After all the meringues are finished, bake in the oven at 200 degrees, sprinkle a little water on top when you come out of the oven, you can sprinkle powder sugar after chopping if desired. The pastry is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the grilled green apple chicken recipe, chop the chicken breast into small pieces. Add the chickens to the preheated olive oil pan and sauté. Slice the purple onion and apple into small pieces. Place all other ingredients in a bowl and mix with yogurt last. You can choose filet almonds. Grilled Green Apple Chicken is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
For the Mediterranean Pasta Salad recipe; First, boil the pasta for 8 minutes and drain. Add all other ingredients and mix. Spice it up. Mediterranean Pasta Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Chocolate Banana; Peel the bananas and cut them in half. Attach the ice cream tips to the bananas. Melt the chocolate in the microwave and dip the bananas. Dip it in colored sugar last. Chocolate Banana is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
For the Mozzarella Pesto Toast recipe; We apply pesto sauce on the breads. Place the cheese and spinach on it. Toast until cheese melts. Mozzarella Pesto Toast is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Hot Sandwich recipe; Pour oil into the pan and heat it. Add the zucchini first, then the onion, then the carrot and cook. Remove from fire after cooking well. Mix all the ingredients for the sauce. Put the last vegetables on the bread and pour the sauce on it. Hot Sandwich is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Zucchini Pizza recipe; Finely chop the zucchini. Grate the mozzarella. Cut the tomatoes in half. Spread the pesto on the zucchini, top with the cheese and tomatoes. Bake the tray on which you have placed the greaseproof paper in the preheated oven at 200 degrees until the cheese is browned. Zucchini Piiza is ready to be served.

For the Fig Chia Pudding recipe; Boil the milk and add the chia seeds. Mix until it becomes a pudding. When it's cooked, take it into your serving bowls, drizzle honey on it and slice the figs. Fig Chia Pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Quinoa Kisir recipe; Boil until the quinoa is cooked first. Without straining all the boiling water, add the tomato paste and mix. Chop all the ingredients and mix with tomato paste and quinoa. Quinoa Vicious is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Peri's Egg Bread recipe; Crack the egg into the pan and cook. Then spread labneh cheese on the bread and finally place the egg. Garnish with cherry tomatoes. Peri's Egg Bread is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Avocado Breakfast Salad recipe; Boil the egg and divide it into 8 equal parts. Slice the avocado into cubes. Mix all the ingredients. Avocado Breakfast Salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the Classic Breakfast Salad recipe; boil the egg. Slice the feta cheese, cucumber and tomatoes. Wash and sort the parsley and arugula. Mix all the ingredients. Add the olive oil. Classic Breakfast Salad is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Bulgur Vaccine Soup recipe; Finely chop the onions, sauté in butter, add the minced meat that is almost pink. Saute a little and when it gets color, add the pepper paste and continue the roasting process. Add chickpeas and bulgur. After sautéing for 1 minute, add the broth and let it cook. Once it boils, add salt and pepper. Boil for 5 more minutes on low heat, add finely chopped parsley and turn off the stove. Bulgur Vaccine Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Chicken Tantuni recipe; Chop 1 kg of chicken into cubes. Add oil to a large skillet and fry the chicken until the water is gone. Finely dice the onion, tomato and pepper. Add the roasted chicken to the tantuni lavash. Add tomatoes, onions, peppers and spices on top. Chicken Tantuni is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the apple candy recipe, put the granulated sugar in the steel pot and pour the water from the sides of the pot. Let it boil over medium heat without stirring. When it starts to boil, add the lemon juice and boil for another 15 minutes. Add colorant and mix 2-3 times. Boil for another 10-15 minutes to thicken. Cover the apples you stick with the mixture. Candy apple is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Mustard Pistachio Chops recipe, we salt and black pepper the cutlets and first seal them in a pan without oil (no oil was used because it has its own oil). We seal it on high heat for about 1-2 minutes until both sides are browned (by frying the outside of the meat, we ensure that the water inside is trapped). After the sealing process, we apply mustard on one side and sprinkle pistachios on them. We put it on the baking tray and bake for another 5 minutes at 180 degrees. For the salad, we mix all the ingredients and add the lemon and salt. Mustard Pistachio Chops are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Eggplant Mütebbel recipe, we leave the eggplant on the fire on the stove and let the outer shell burn. When the whole crust is burned, we cover it with cling film so that it is not airtight so that it is easy to peel with hot air. After peeling, finely chop the inside with a knife. Add salt, garlic, dill and tahini to the yogurt mixture and mix. Lastly, we add the chopped eggplant and decorate it with chili peppers. Eggplant Mütebbel is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Golden Tea recipe, mix the milk with the powdered turmeric, add the water and mix until there are no lumps. Boil all ingredients except honey. Add the honey last. Golden Tea is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For Onion Bhaji recipe, chop the onions, add all the spices and flour, add the water last and mix well. Arrange on wax paper, spaced one tablespoon each. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for about 25-30 minutes until well browned. Onion Bhaji is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.
For the Fairy's Bread Egg recipe, cook the egg in the skillet. Spread the cheese on the bread, place the egg. Serve with tomatoes. Peri's Toast Egg is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Eggplant Ravioli recipe, add half a tea glass of water and egg to the flour and knead. Let the dough rest covered for half an hour. Divide into small balls and roll out thinly one by one. Add the stuffing little by little, cut and shape. Boil for 10 minutes. For internal mortar; Chop the onions and eggplants into very small squares and cook in the pan. Use as interior mortar. For the sauce; Take the tomato paste in a pan, crush the garlic, add salt and pepper. Finally add some boiling water and cook the sauce. Add the sauce over the ravioli. Eggplant Ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Meatball Ravioli recipe, add half a tea glass of water and an egg to the flour and knead. Let the dough rest covered for half an hour. Divide into small balls and roll out thinly one by one. Add the stuffing little by little, cut and shape. Boil for 10 minutes. For internal mortar; Fry the onions. Then add the minced meat, salt and pepper. For the sauce; Take the tomato paste in a pan, crush the garlic, add salt and pepper. Finally add some boiling water and cook the sauce. Add the sauce over the ravioli. Eggplant Ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Spinach Ravioli recipe, add half a tea glass of water and an egg to the flour and knead. Let the dough rest covered for half an hour. Divide into small balls and roll out thinly one by one. Add the stuffing little by little, cut and shape. Boil for 10 minutes. For internal mortar; First, boil the spinach for 1 minute and then put it in ice water to stop cooking and not lose its nutritional value. For the sauce; Take the tomato paste in a pan, crush the garlic, add salt and pepper. Finally add some boiling water and cook the sauce. Add the sauce over the ravioli. Spinach Ravioli is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

Baked pumpkin dessert; Put the peeled and sliced zucchini in an oven bag and bake on a baking tray at 230 degrees for about 45 minutes. Take it on a serving plate and pour tahini on it. Baked pumpkin dessert is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the recipe for Oven Meatballs with Kashar Cheese; Add ground beef, garlic, parsley, cheddar cheese, salt and pepper, bread crumbs and milk, 2 eggs to the mixing bowl. It is mixed with a wooden spoon and made into a mortar. Then, it is rounded with an ice cream spoon and placed on a wooden surface, one by one, on the greaseproof paper that was previously cut in a rectangular shape. The round patties are fried in vegetable oil. Spread tomato sauce on a flat baking tray. Meatballs are placed on it. Then the remaining tomato sauce is poured over it again and sprinkled with grated mozzarella. It is covered with foil and placed in the oven. The oven is set to 180 degrees for 20 minutes and it is expected to be cooked. Oven Meatballs with Cheese is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Colorful Winter Salad recipe; Cut the green pepper and red pepper julienne. Slice and mix all remaining ingredients. Garnish your salad with the oranges on top. While serving, squeeze the lemon and drizzle with olive oil. Colorful Winter Salad is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Brain Soup recipe; Boil the yoghurt, flour and lemon mixture in a saucepan. Smash the well-cooked brain with a knife, add it to the mixture, boil it one more time, turn off the stove and serve hot. Brain Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Ottoman Soup recipe; Boil the finely chopped meat. Then take 1 tablespoon of butter in a pan and fry the meats in oil a little. Put the remaining butter in another saucepan. Throw in the sliced mushrooms and chopped spinach. Saute vegetables until they release their juices. Pour lukewarm water and crushed hair or grated tomatoes and flour into it. After a while, add the meat and broth and cook for 20 minutes. Serve with chopped green onions on top. Ottoman Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Paradise Date Muffin recipe, peel the shells of the paradise dates and remove the seeds inside. The size of the date of paradise can change the flour size of the dough. The dough should be thick. The dates are crushed with a fork to keep the consistency of the cake. Let's add the other ingredients and mix them. It is baked in the oven at 160°C. The Paradise date muffin is ready to be served. Bon appetit.

For the recipe for sugar-free pumpkin balls, we boil the pumpkin with 1 tea glass of water. We crush the boiled pumpkins with the help of a fork and add honey, walnuts and oat paste into it. We break small balls from the mixture and find them in the coconut. It is enough to wait in the fridge for 1 night. Sugar-free pumpkin balls are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Tahini Cookies recipe, mix the ground mulberry, carob flour, tahini and carbonate in a bowl. Add 1-2 drops of lemon juice to the carbonate. Divide it into 10 equal parts and shape it. Cook for 20-25 minutes at 160 C. The Tahini Cookies is ready to serve. Bon Appetit .

For the Meat Sautee recipe with Cheddar and Mushroom; Add the oil to the pan and fry it until it turns brown. Chopped red and green peppers are lightly roasted. Meat sautéed in a separate place; Add mushrooms and mix. Put 1 spoon of tomato paste and spices in a bowl. It is mixed with 1 glass of water and added to the roasted ingredients. It is boiled for 5 minutes. Finally, it is transferred to the oven dish and grated cheddar is sprinkled on it and given to the oven. When the Cheddar Cheese is melted, Meat Saute with Cheddar and Mushroom is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Roasted Eggplant Meat Recipe; meat is roasted, salt and pepper are thrown. Set aside to rest. Yogurt is crushed and garlic and salt are added to it. The eggplants are chopped and added to the yogurt and mixed. It is taken into the serving plate and the middle is slightly indented. The meat is fully laid out. Poured over the hot butter. Roasted Eggplant Meat Meal is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the carrot-zucchini baked hash browns recipe, grate the carrots and zucchini and squeeze out the juice. Chop the red pepper and parsley. Mix all the ingredients and bake at 200 degrees for 20 minutes. Oven with carrot and zucchini Mücver is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Yogurt Chicken Salad recipe; Chop the green apple into cubes and the red onion into half moons. Saute the chicken breast cut into cubes with 1 tablespoon of oil. After removing it from the stove and transferring it to a clean bowl, add red onion, garlic powder, green apple and strained yogurt and mix. Chicken Salad with Yogurt is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the coconut flour pizza recipe, add the coconut flour, dill cream cheese and 2 eggs to the mozzarella cheese that you have grated 3/4 of and mix well. Roll this mixture on greaseproof paper with the help of a rolling pin, form the base of the pizza, and bake until golden brown. After removing it from the oven, add tomato paste, sausage, tomato, mushroom and remaining mozzarella cheese in order and bake again. Coconut flour pizza is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Whole Wheat Bread recipe; Yeast and sugar are mixed, warm water is added into it and the resulting mixture is left for 5 minutes. The flour and salt are taken into the mixer and the yeast is added and whisked. Water is slowly added to the mixture and when it reaches the consistency of dough, it is kneaded a little more, covered with cling film and left to rest in a warm environment for 40 minutes. The dough that has risen is given its final shape by flouring it and removing its air. It is placed on a baking tray and, after resting for another 20 minutes, it is first baked at 190 degrees for 15 minutes, then at 180 degrees for 15 minutes in the fan option. After the bread is taken out of the oven, it is expected to cool before cutting it so that it does not become doughy. Note: Salt is never added to the yeast because salt kills the yeast and sugar makes the bread rise better. Whole Wheat Bread is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Almond Flour Bread recipe, mix the dry ingredients in a bowl. Beat eggs at room temperature. Add the vinegar in it. Then add the honey. Pour dry ingredients into it and knead. Put the dough you have made into a paper-lined cake mold. Bake at 180 degrees for 20 minutes. Almond Flour Bread is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the tomato paste barley noodle soup recipe; First of all, 2 tablespoons of oil and 1 tablespoon of tomato paste are put in a pan and roasted a little. Add grated tomato on the roasted tomato paste, mix and cook for 1 minute. Then, 6 glasses of water is added to it and left to boil. When the water of the soup starts to boil, barley noodles are added into it. The salt of the soup is adjusted and cooked on low heat until the vermicelli becomes soft. When the vermicelli becomes soft, mint is added to the soup and mixed and removed from the stove. Paste Barley Noodle Soup is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Quinoa Chocolate Chip Cookies; Mash the banana, mix it with cinnamon and cocoa. Add the cooked quinoa, ground flaxseed, almonds and knead. Shape and lay 20 cookies on the baking tray on which you have lined greaseproof paper at intervals. Bake in a preheated 170 degree oven for 15-20 minutes until the tops and bottoms turn a light color. Melt the bitter chocolate benmari style. After dipping the base or sides of the cookies you have taken out of the oven and left to cool in melted dark chocolate, cool them on greaseproof paper. Quinoa Chocolate Chip Cookies is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Quinoa Vegetable Meatballs; Boil the quinoa seeds, which you have washed in plenty of water and drained, in 2 glasses of hot water for about 15-20 minutes until the water is absorbed. Grate the peeled carrots and zucchini with the coarse side of the boiled grater. Finely chop the spring onions. Finely chop the dill and parsley. Put the quinoa boiled in vegetable broth in a glass mixing bowl and keep it aside to cool. Mix grated carrots, zucchini and boiled potatoes with chopped greens. Season with salt, freshly ground black pepper and coriander. Finally, after adding the egg, mix all the ingredients with the help of a spoon until they are combined. Heat the olive oil in a Teflon pan. Take one tablespoon of the quinoa vegetable patties you prepared and leave it in the pan. Fry, pressing lightly on it, until it turns brown on both sides. Transfer the fried meatballs to a paper towel-lined serving plate and leave for 2-3 minutes to release excess oil. Take the seasonal greens that you have washed and dried in plenty of water on a serving plate. Place the meatballs. Quinoa Vegetable Meatballs are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Gluten Free Souffle; Melt the butter and chocolate. Remove from the stove, add rice flour and mix. In a separate bowl, whisk the eggs and sugar quickly to froth. After adding the chocolate and flour mixture to the eggs, pour it into 2 souffle molds that you grease. Bake in the oven heated at 220°C for 7 minutes. Gluten Free Souffle is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Gluten Free Custard; Boil the milk in a saucepan and add the sugar. In a separate bowl, mix rice flour and cornstarch with water. Take a few spoons of boiling milk and add it to the melted flour mixture. Keep stirring while slowly adding the flour mixture to the boiling milk. Mix until there are no lumps in the pudding and remove from the stove. Take it into small bowls while it is hot and let it cool. You can add cinnamon if you wish. Gluten Free Custard is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For Gluten-Free Women's Leg Meatballs; Grate the onion and fry it in oil until golden brown. Meanwhile, boil the rice and drain it. Fry the onion with half of the minced meat for 5 minutes. Strain the excess oil, add the chopped parsley, 5 minutes later the rice and the yolk of an egg, add the desired amount of salt and pepper and knead for 10 minutes. In a bowl, beat the remaining egg white with the last remaining egg. Prepare flat and oval meatballs from the mortar you prepared. Dip these patties in cornmeal, then eggs, then cornmeal again. Fry the prepared meatballs in hot oil. Remove the excess oil by keeping the fried meatballs on a paper towel for a few minutes. Gluten Free Women's Meatballs are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal

For cold detox tea, boil 1 lemon and 1 green apple peel in 1 liter of water for 20 minutes. After taking it from the stove, add 1 stick of cinnamon, 2 pieces of green tea, 7-8 pieces of cherry stalk and 1 teaspoon of grated root ginger and leave it to cool. After it has cooled, strain and add the peeled apple by slicing it. After waiting for 1-2 hours in the ice pack, the cold detox tea is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

Croissants recipe; For the dough, knead the butter, eggs, 1/2 cup milk, powdered sugar, yeast and salt. Add the flour and make a dough in the consistency of an earlobe and leave it to ferment. Pass the cake through the robot. Combine cocoa, walnuts, cinnamon, raisins and 1/2 cup milk. Break off pieces from the fermented dough and roll it out with the help of a rolling pin. Place the stuffing that you have given the shape of a roll in the middle of the dough and roll it. Shape into a moon and place on the baking tray. Brush it with egg yolk and bake at 180 degrees. Croissants are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the almond flour carrot cake; Rinse the dates, which you soaked in hot water and removed the seeds from, with walnuts, carrots, milk and 2 eggs. Add almond flour, cinnamon and baking powder to the mixture. Slowly pour 2 egg whites, which you have whipped into a thick consistency, into the mixture and mix. Bake in a preheated oven at 180 degrees for 30-35 minutes. Almond flour carrot cake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

Cheddar cheese pastry recipe; For the dough, dissolve the yeast with warm milk, water and sugar, add the other ingredients and get a dough that sticks to the hand. Let it ferment for 15 minutes. Break off walnut-sized pieces from the dough, add grated cheddar cheese and cover with the closed side up. Cover with molasses and then sesame seeds, place them on the tray at light intervals and let them rest for another 15 minutes. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven until golden brown. Cheesecake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Fellah meatballs; Take the semolina and fine bulgur in a bowl, add 1.5 cups of boiling water and let it rest for 10-15 minutes. Meanwhile, grate the tomatoes for the sauce and chop the garlic. Fry the garlic in oil for 1-2 minutes and cook until the tomatoes get juiced. Add salt and let the sauce cool. Add flour, egg, tomato paste, salt to the swelling semolina and bulgur mixture and knead. Take some large pieces of hazelnut from the dough you have obtained and make a round and press it in the middle with the tip of your pinky finger. Add the meatballs you have prepared to the boiling water and leave to cook. When the meatballs are above the water, take them in a colander and mix them with the tomato sauce you prepared. Add yogurt and chopped parsley on it. Fellah meatballs are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the cheddar pancake; Lay the dough flat on a flat surface. Spread grated cheddar cheese in the middle and close the opposite edges. Cook in the oiled pan, with the lid of the pan closed, on low heat by turning both sides. When you take it from the pan, lubricate it with oil. Cheesecake is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the spread recipe, melt the yeast by adding the fresh yeast, sugar, and warm milk to a bowl. Hold for a couple of minutes. Add the egg white, olive oil and salt to the bowl. Add the flour slowly and sifted into the bowl. Add flour and knead until you get a soft dough that does not stick to the hand. Cover the dough with a cloth and leave it for about half an hour to leaven. Divide the fermented dough into 5 meringues and roll the meringues. Open the meringues to the width of a tea plate with the help of your hand. By wrapping it in the form of a roll, holding both ends of the dough and moving both hands in opposite directions, curl it. Combine the ends well and place them on the baking tray on which you have greased paper. Brush with egg yolk and sprinkle with black cumin, if desired. Bake at 200 degrees for 15-20 minutes. The opening is ready for service.

For the olive roll recipe, melt the yeast by adding fresh yeast, sugar and warm milk to a bowl. Hold for a couple of minutes. Add the egg white, olive oil and salt to the bowl. Add the flour slowly and sifted into the bowl. Add flour and knead until you get a soft dough that does not stick to the hand. Cover the dough with a cloth and leave it for about half an hour to leaven. Divide the fermented dough into 5 meringues and roll the meringues. Open the meringues to the width of a tea plate with the help of your hand. Add 1 tablespoon of olive paste into it. Wrap it in a roll shape, hold both ends of the dough and curl it by moving both hands in opposite directions. Combine the ends well and place them on the baking tray on which you have greased paper. Brush with egg yolk and sprinkle with black cumin, if desired. Bake at 200 degrees for 15-20 minutes. Opening with olives is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the potato roll recipe, melt the yeast by adding the fresh yeast, sugar and warm milk to a bowl. Hold for a couple of minutes. Add the egg white, olive oil and salt to the bowl. Add the flour slowly and sifted into the bowl. Add flour and knead until you get a soft dough that does not stick to the hand. Cover the dough with a cloth and leave it for about half an hour to leaven. Divide the fermented dough into 5 meringues and roll the meringues. Open the meringues to the width of a tea plate with the help of your hand. Add boiled potatoes into it. By wrapping it in the form of a roll, holding both ends of the dough and moving both hands in opposite directions, curl it. Combine the ends well and place them on the baking tray on which you have greased paper. Brush with egg yolk and sprinkle with black cumin, if desired. Bake at 200 degrees for 15-20 minutes. Potatoes are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the banana oat cookie recipe; mash the bananas with a fork. Add oat paste, cocoa and crushed hazelnuts. Shape the mixture into 12 equal parts with a spoon and place them on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Bake in a preheated 180 degree oven for 12-15 minutes. Banana oat cookies are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal. :)

For a coffee sugar-free cookie recipe, knead whole wheat flour, olive oil, carob molasses, baking powder, walnuts, Turkish coffee and milk until it gets thick. Shape and bake in a preheated oven at 200 degrees for 10 minutes. After taking it out of the oven, dip it in dark chocolate that you melted in a bain-marie and decorate with ground pistachios. Sugar-free cookies with coffee are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)
Heat the pan. Fry the roasted pieces over medium heat. Crack the egg and add salt. Cook covered. Fried egg is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

Beat 3 egg whites and 1 whole egg with a mixer in a microwave-safe glass bowl (30x30 deep bowl). Add baking powder, oat bran flour, milk powder, cinnamon and honey and continue beating. Slowly add the mineral water and continue whisking. You should get a cake-like/fluid mixture. 4) Beat the walnuts and add them. The mixture you get should cover almost half of the container. The container is heated at 180 degrees for 30 minutes. cook until. If it is wet at the end of the time, you can cook it for another 5 minutes.
For the cheddar sausage toast recipe; Arrange the cheddar cheese and sausages on the toasted bread. Press in the toaster. Enjoy your meal.

For the chicken roast recipe; Chop the chicken breasts into cubes. Chop the green pepper, from which you have removed the stems and seeds, into half moons. Chop the tomatoes you peeled into cubes and cut the last onion into small cubes. Pour sunflower oil into the pan and heat it. Add chicken breasts and start frying. Then add onions, green peppers and tomatoes and continue frying. Add salt, pepper and thyme. When the chicken meat is browned and the vegetables have evaporated, take them off the stove. Enjoy your meal.

For the recipe for patisserie mini sandwich breads; Add warm milk and yeast to a bowl and dissolve. Then add warm water, oil, egg white, salt, sugar and mix. Then add the flour little by little and knead until you get a dough that does not stick to the hand. Leave to ferment for 1 hour in a warm place. When the fermentation process is finished, cut off a little bit of walnut from the dough, roll them and place them on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper. Brush egg yolk on it. About 20 minutes in a preheated 180 degree oven. cook until. Patisserie style mini sandwich breads are ready to be served. Enjoy your meal.

For the sugar-free pumpkin mosaic cake recipe; We cut the pumpkin into cubes, add enough water to cover it and cook it until it becomes soft. We grind the oat paste into flour in the rondo. It will be enough to turn the peanuts and the ronda a few turns. Mash the softened pumpkins with a fork. We add the mixture in the ronda and the honey to the pumpkins. It is enough to give it a pyramid shape with foil and leave it in the freezer for 2-3 hours. Sugar-free pumpkin mosaic cake is ready to serve. Optionally, you can garnish with nutmeg.

For Meat Bread; Add warm water to wheat flour, sugar, salt and yeast and knead until it becomes a soft dough, then let it rest. Meanwhile, for the internal mortar; Finely chop the onion, pepper and parsley. Mix the ground beef, tomato sauce, black pepper, cayenne pepper and salt and knead well. Divide the fermented dough into handful-sized balls. Open it longitudinally with a rolling pin and lay the inner mortar in equal parts. Cover the dough and spread butter on it. Leave to bake in a preheated 250 degree oven. Meat Bread is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the oatli walnut bar recipe; Fry the oat paste over low heat. Remove the seeds from the dates and soak them in 6 tablespoons of hot water for half an hour. Crush it with water and add the oat paste. Mash 2 bananas with the help of a fork and add to the mixture. After crushing the walnuts with your hands and adding them to the mixture, add the raisins, chocolate chips and grated orange peel and mix well. Divide into equal parts and bake at 180 degrees for 20 minutes. oatli walnut bar is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the eggplant sitting recipe; Peel the aubergines and cut them into 1 inch thick slices. Deep fry in oil, put it on a paper towel and reduce the oil. Take the olive oil in the pan and fry the onion and garlic. Add the minced meat and cook for another 5 minutes, then add the diced tomatoes, pepper and tomato paste. Take it off the stove and add salt and pepper and mix the mortar thoroughly. Place the bostan eggplants on the baking tray, add the mortar on them and put a slice of tomato on the top layer and bake at 180 degrees for 15-20 minutes. Eggplant sitting is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Cağ Kebab recipe, thinly beat the lamb meat. Grate the onions. Marinate the lamb meat with olive oil, yoghurt, salt, pepper and onion and let it rest in the refrigerator for about 3-4 hours. After marinating, put the lamb meats on top of each other in twos threes and let them rest in the freezer for 3-4 hours. Thread the meat out of the freezer onto skewers and cook in a pan without oil. You can serve it with lavash on the side. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the avocado toast recipe; Mash the ripe avocado with a fork, add lemon and spread it on the toast. Add arugula, cheese and tomatoes. After covering it with the other slice of bread, place it in the toaster. After about 5 minutes, your avocado toast is ready. Enjoy your meal :)

For the cocoa oat pudding; Cook the milk, oat and cocoa until thickened. Remove the thickened pudding from the stove. Add the banana and honey that you mashed with a fork and mix. Transfer to serving bowls and chill in the refrigerator for 2 hours. You can garnish it with nutmeg if you wish. Cocoa oat pudding is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For a healthy burger recipe with eggplant; Slice the garden eggplant and place on the grill. Then fry the halloumi cheese on the grill. Add the fried cheese, tomato and lettuce on top of the eggplant slice. Eggplant healthy burger is ready to be served. Enjoy your meal :)

For the blueberry oat health balls recipe; First, pull the raw almonds and blueberries out of the blender. Take a separate bowl and add oat paste, baking powder, vanilla and cinnamon powder. Crack the egg over this mixture. Finally, mash the banana with a fork and add to the mixture. Knead and break off a little bit larger than the walnut and roll them. Place on a baking tray lined with greaseproof paper or in small cake tins. 15-20 minutes in the oven at 180 degrees. cook until. Health balls with blueberry oat are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the asparagus pasta recipe with pesto sauce; Boil 2 cups of pasta in 4 cups of hot water to which you add salt. In a separate pot, sauté the asparagus, peppers and zucchini with olive oil. For the sauce, put the olive oil, basil, cheese and garlic in a blender. Add the sauce to the boiled pasta and add the sauteed vegetables on it. Pasta with pesto sauce and asparagus is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal :)

For the Pistachio Wire Kadayif recipe; Separate the wire kadayif with your hands. Melt the butter in a saucepan. Grease the tray you will use as much as 3-4 tablespoons of the melted butter. Pour the remaining butter on the wire kadaifs and mix. Spread half of the oiled and separated kadayifs on the greased tray and press them with your hand. Sprinkle the ground pistachios in between. Add the remaining kadayıf to the peanuts and press it with your hands. Put a weight on the dessert and leave it for 10-15 minutes. Bake in a preheated 200 degree oven until golden brown. On the other hand, for the sherbet of kadayif, boil the sugar and water in a saucepan. When it boils, add lemon juice and boil for 5 more minutes and remove from the stove to cool. Pour the cooled sherbet over the hot dessert. After the kadayif sherbet is drawn, the pistachio wire kadayif is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the liquid oil rice pilaf recipe; Heat the oil in a saucepan, add the previously washed rice and fry it on low heat. Add salt and warm water to it. Cook on low heat until the water is absorbed. After resting for 15 minutes, rice pilaf with liquid oil is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the recipe of Potato Stuffed with Avocado Paste with Peas; Make holes in the potatoes and cook them in the microwave for 4-7 minutes. For chickpeas: In a small saucepan over medium heat, add 1 tablespoon of olive oil, 1 clove of minced garlic, 1/4 cup of chopped red onion and 1/2 teaspoon of cumin, 1/4 teaspoon of paprika, a pinch of salt and cayenne pepper, and add about 1 teaspoon of cayenne pepper. Cook for 3 minutes. Then add the chickpeas and keep on the stove for another 5-10 minutes until ready to serve. For avocado paste with peas: Put the peas, avocado, 2 cloves of garlic, 1/4 cup of chopped red onion, 1 tablespoon of olive oil, salt, pepper, and cayenne pepper in a blender or food processor and blend until you get the desired consistency. For the sauce: In a bowl Whisk tahini, maple syrup, lemon juice, 1 clove of garlic, apple cider vinegar, 1 teaspoon of olive oil, salt and pepper until well mixed. Uncover your cooked potatoes, fill them with avocado paste with peas and chickpeas. Then drizzle the maple tahini sauce on it. The Potato Stuffed with Avocado Paste with Peas is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the Spicy Simple Lentil recipe; In a blender or food processor, add the garlic, onion, bell pepper, tomato paste, maple syrup, sea salt, spices, ginger, and lemon juice. Mix well, taste to see if you need to add anything, and add if needed. In a large saucepan over medium-low heat, add the drained lentils, fresh coriander, and sauce. Stir by heating until well mixed. Spicy simple lentils are ready to serve. Enjoy your meal. :)

For the Basil and Cashew Pistachio Pasta recipe; Add the pasta to the salted boiling water and boil until fully cooked. Blend the garlic, 3 tablespoons olive oil, cashews, and black pepper until smooth using a blender or food processor. Add salt to blender, whisk until blended. Add the basil and the rest of the olive oil and mix again. Add the lemon juice. Drain and rinse your cooked pasta, add it back to the pot and mix it with the cashew sauce until smooth. Pasta with Basil and Cashew Pistachio is ready to serve. Enjoy your meal.

For the Goat Cheese and Blueberry Greens Salad recipe; Finely chop the dried cranberries and put them in a bowl, sprinkle some sesame seeds and mix well. Take 2 teaspoons of goat cheese and roll it into a ball. Then roll in the cranberry-sesame mixture, making sure it's well coated on the outside. Repeat this until all the cheese you have is gone and put the balls you have aside. For the dressing of the salad, mix the sesame oil, tahini, honey, balsamic vinegar and olive oil well.
